local a={"I\'m on CatChat now!Complete event missions to receive new exciting messages in CatChat!","The café\'s summer promotion is on!Umu... Since customers are flocking in, there will be three part-time staff helping me out. And Fuyumi\'s custom-made uniforms for the two ladies fit perfectly!","Part-timer No. 1 reporting in!","Mortals don\'t need to know why I\'m working part-time… And no questions!","3","I\'m so glad it fits! Never thought my hobby will come in handy, haha!","Why is the male staff members not in his uniform?! I want to see his uniform!","Mr. A\'s decision to come in as a part-timer was unexpected, so I wasn\'t prepared for him.However, Mr. A might just look good in any uniform. Umu… Do you have a certain style you prefer, {0}?","He is so my type. Heading to the café right away!","Take it easy. I\'ll be waiting for you in the shop.","Since there\'s only one person here, \"buy one get one 50% off\" seems pretty useless...","Secret: {0} may exchange it for a 50% discount voucher at the counter, and it can be used upon your next visit!","Summer promotion: Buy one special brew get one 50% off.","Thanks for the hard work, Mr. A. The café\'s summer promotion has already begun, and we are awaiting everyone\'s patronage with open arms!","Posted while I was making omurice? Cheeky, very cheeky, Mr. A. I better hurry up. Hinata, you can do this!","Hmph, promoting on a homepage with so few followers? Business seems pretty bad for the café.","I almost thought it was some random marketing...","Just a task from the manager.","Why do you work at the café anyway?!","The air conditioner. We need a new one.","A completely different style than Riu\'s? But… Chiori still likes it.","If Miss Chiori wants the same design, just say the word, and I\'ll make one for you!","It\'s fine. After all, Chiori don\'t really like this kind of clothing. No, not one bit.","But it looks really cute on you!","But it looks really cute on you!","But it looks really cute on you!","You don\'t need to be commenting on Chiori\'s cuteness. Keep it to yourself, copycat.","Can I get a \"Welcome back, master!\" from Chiori?","@Riu Kujou","I\'m ready, to punch.","I\'m on my way to your house. You have 23 minutes to prepare for an apology speech.","Takanashi\'s limited-edition Big Three Dragons omurice! There\'s also a \"Red\" version. As for the White version... Pick whatever word you want.","I would like a birdie on my White omurice. A chubby one. Can I get that?","Looks tasty.","What on earth is omurice doing in a café?","Oh, they don\'t sell it in other cafés?","I want you to write \"Hinata is {0}\'s favorite!\"","That\'s too long. Rejected!","However, as a token of gratitude, I will add a piece of complimentary ham to your omurice.","Delicious.","According to the manager, the words on the omurice are some sort of magical condiments. Write it with all your heart, and your omurice will taste better.","Yakuman. Yes.","Oh, the magic of Yakuman? Intriguing.","Making a robot that specializes in writing words on omurice may be easy, but some things are much more meaningful if done manually!","I wonder if I can be as good at mahjong as Yui if I eat the same omurice as her?","Give it a go, maybe?","Is there any chance I could eat omurice made by Yui?","Well, I went through some recipes just now. I\'ll take the challenge if that is what you really want.","I heard that the café which is all the rage right now makes delicious caramel pudding. Wanna go grab some?","President, eyes off your phone during work, please.","!!?","Someone in the team says that the shop has a vacancy for a part-time pastry chef. How about working there during the vacation?","Remember to take the guy above with you.","Vice President: I\'m watching you.","My phone was confiscated. I\'m secretly replying to you with my computer.","Who will you take then?","Judging by your comment, I\'m pretty sure you haven\'t seen my message. I almost thought I\'d been turned down.","Survival confirmed.","Is this why we say that \"a workplace is like a battlefield\"? Looks like I gotta bring in my A-game tomorrow!","(Sticker)","Mr. A, due to your incredible popularity, many customers want you to take their orders. Thanks for your hard work.","√","Survival confirmed +1","I know.","There, there. Is the part-time job really such an uphill battle?","Too many people taking photos. Don\'t want to be in any of them.","Hmph! Told ya, nobody makes better hand drip coffee than Riu. Y\'all better start believing it now!","I\'ve only made them coffee because you told me to, Miss Chiori. After this part-time job is over, I can brew coffee just for you.","Ah—Haruna wants to work with Little Chiori, too!","So that\'s the reason you\'re on duty, but Riu is doing all the work?","Who are you to call her by her name before Chiori?","When can I have the chance to drink some coffee you\'ve made, Chiori?","If you have what it takes to defeat Chiori in the next mahjong game, then maybe you could have a cup.","But you can have only one cup. One cup, you hear?!","The newly-arrived Mandheling coffee beans are definitely some of the finest, but there are just too few of them. Maybe we could try roasting coffee beans ourselves?","Mandheling beans are exorbitant, but their rich texture is beyond compare. That explains why Riu keeps tons of them at her place.","If Miss Chiori doesn\'t like how the beans we bought taste, maybe roasting them myself is a good idea.","You\'re so versatile, Miss Riu. If you don\'t mind, maybe we can try roasting coffee beans together?","Did little Reina brew this batch of coffee beans this morning? I like it.","If that\'s the case, let\'s include them in the crews\' morning tea!","I know very little about coffee beans, but I choose to have faith in Reina.","Well, and Reina have faith in {0} when it comes to Mahjong!","Could I drink it if I swing by now?","Of course you can. Will you come to Éternité today, {0}?","The customers are super friendly. I broke 3 cups of coffee and 2 plates today, but no one blamed me... I\'ll work harder tomorrow and try not to be so clumsy!","In case you didn\'t know, the damages are compensated with your salary.","My little angel Chiori, please tell me you didn\'t post such a ruthless comment yourself!","Reina was once clumsy, but not since I mastered my job. Keep it up, Miss Hinata.","I will work harder to prove my worth, little manager! (Whisper: By the way, can you please not deduct my salary? QAQ)","The damages are unimportant as long as you are safe and sound.","There is a minor gash on my finger, which was why little Chiori took over my job cleaning the kitchen today. She\'s indeed a little angel.","You\'ll be good at the job if you work long enough. Don\'t mind it too much. Your first part-time job is not always fun and games.","All that trouble is still my fault, but I feel much better after hearing your kind words, hehe.","The roast, grind size, coffee-to-water ratio, temperature... As long as you can precisely calculate each step, the process of hand drip coffee is merely solving a math problem with patience.","Um... Is this doable for a newbie?","It shouldn\'t be a problem for newbies, as long as you strictly follow the scientific brewing method.","I\'ve never tried brewing coffee before, but it seems pretty similar to making tea.","I\'ve successfully brewed a good cup of coffee by following the steps you sent me! Can I make you a cup of coffee as a way of saying thanks?","Why not...? I\'ll definitely go for it when I fully recover from this cold. The weather seems to be unpredictable these days, so take care of yourself.","Is there a chance I can drink your hand drip coffee?","Anytime... Let me know if you like a particular kind of coffee bean.","I can feel my age. My heart went bananas after I had a cup of coffee this morning.","Did you go to the café Chiori works at? It\'s cheeky of you to explore the new region without me knowing. The Kitty Legion and I are unhappy about this!","3 ice pops.","I\'ll forgive you this time.","Tsk, you were pretty energetic 2 days before, during our rumble. Take care of yourself before losing to me.","One more comment about taking care of my health, and I\'ll block you...","A cup of coffee after a hangover? If nothing happens except that your heart is racing, I would say your heart is pretty healthy.","Well... I\'ll just avoid having wine and coffee at the same time from now on.","Maybe try a cup of milk to help with your hangover. Age is totally irrelevant. Regardless of their age, everyone should pay attention to their health.","You\'re posting about my health just like that dude above? Give me a break.","Little Reina is very talented at mahjong. At least she\'s much better than some fool.","Umu... But I\'m no match for Chiori, of course.","Oh no! I was just making myself some tea, and I missed the chance to be the first to reply to Miss Chiori\'s post!!!","I wonder if by \"some fool,\" you mean me?","Hmph, at least you\'re self-aware. Chiori will see if your mahjong skills show any sign of improvement after this part-time job ends.","Who is the fool you\'re talking about?","We\'ve only been apart for a few days, and you\'ve already lost your common sense?Since your brain isn\'t working, you better be at the dojo tonight. Your dearest Master Chiori will defeat you \'til your muscle memory reminds you who\'s the dumbest person in One Han City.","Survival confirmed. +1","Survival confirmed. +2","Survival confirmed. +3","Survival confirmed. +... Nope, you almost fooled me. Keep it up, everyone. Work may be hard, but there\'s happiness in it, too.","The same thing again? I thought this was the post from the day before yesterday!","Uncle asked us to post about our working status on the social platform every day to promote the café, haha...","You can share happy things on social media, too, not just your current status!","Nothing feels better than living.","[Éternité Record No.1]Observation time...: {date}Observation object...: Panamanian-made Geisha coffee beanObservation reason...: Reina says that this coffee has a fruity flavorObservation outcome...: The only energizer for KR-976 is strawberry milk","You need to taste the coffee sip by sip. You drank it too fast.","Automatic reply by KR-976: Charging.","Oh my lovely Anju, I\'ll bring you some strawberry milk tomorrow.","Geisha coffee actually has a pleasant taste. Once you\'ve started getting used to the taste, you won\'t be able to get enough of it. Give it a few more tries, and it will grow on you.","What if I just don\'t like it even after drinking plenty of it?","Why do humans torture themselves with horrible drinks like coffee...? (quietly lifting a cup of milk tea)","KR-976 quietly lifts a cup of strawberry milk.","Wow... This café is really one of a kind. There\'s a place in One Han City that can accommodate Shaun after all. Liisa Liisa love this place so much!","Shaun is adorable. Everyone in the shop is looking forward to your next visit.","Liisa Liisa hope to bring Mr. Wolf next time. He\'s pretty cute, too.","I want to be friends with Eliisa, so I can pet Shaun whenever I want.","Liisa Liisa have sent you a friend request. Shaun likes you, too.","Which one do you prefer, the Anca Ranch or the café?","Mmm... Hmm... The Anca Ranch is still on the top of my list. For Liisa Liisa, nothing compares to that place!","Wanna go with me next time?","Sure, of course! The staff ladies are very nice, so don\'t be intimidating, Mr. Wolf.","I don\'t want to get up early for work tomorrow...","Seems like Hinata is facing life\'s hardships pretty early on.","Working as a part-timer is much harder than going to school...","Tomorrow is the last day. Don\'t give up! Your salary awaits! On a side note, the shop has received many comments from customers recently. They like Miss Hinata a lot!","I\'m motivated again.","Sincere sympathy from someone who can sleep in tomorrow.","Are you the devil?","I don\'t want to get up early tomorrow, either... Handshake.jpg","Cry.jpg","His name is Samson, and he\'s one of our customers\' pet. Umu... The shop definitely needs a furry friend.","Little Reina, do you have a favorite animal?","There\'s a bunch on my list, I want to keep a rabbit in the shop. But I wonder if you will like her.","Liisa Liisa like all fluffy animals.","This cat... Looks familiar.","You\'ll get a cup of coffee on the house if you can correctly guess who the cat\'s owner is!","Pet-themed cafés are the best. You have my support!","{0}, you can cast a vote for your favorite pet, too! Uncle said the customers\' opinions are important, too.","The taste is fine. At least it\'s better than the pastry club\'s.","Hiring part-time typists for a salary of 1,000,000 Bronze Coins daily!","Why are you targeted by scammers? Think about it yourself!","Why are you targeted by scammers? Think about it yourself!","Why are you targeted by scammers? Think about it yourself!","To the three students above: Meet me at the Student Council after school next Monday, and I shall reflect on my mistake before you, face to face.","Why are you targeted by scammers? Think about it yourself!","I\'m thinking, why I allowed these bad influences anywhere near you.","Oh, you went to this shop, too. How was the taste?","Not bad. We can go there together next time.","Provided you have time.","Since you have helped the Student Council a lot, I\'ll treat you to a cup of coffee to repay your kindness.","Everyone looks happy working here at the café. I wonder if I should join them next time?","Up to you.","Wow—{0} will join us next time? We\'ll need to work harder on the next event, then.","I\'ll teach you how to write words with ketchup on the omurice next time. I\'m an expert now.","If you\'ll wear a maid uniform next time, Chiori won\'t mind visiting you again. After all, Chiori don\'t really hate this shop.","Fuyumi Shinomiya","Mirai","Natsuhiko Takikawa","Anonymous","Rinko Morikawa","Zechs","Hibiki\'s Fan Club","Hibiki Forever","Hibiki Number One!","Did Hibiki Reply To Me Today","Ciri the Animal Tamer","Yuzu","Riri Kitahara","One Hibiki\'s Fan","User 27589","A little Hibiki","Ordinary Salaryman","Stargazy Pie","Not A Baldy","East {0}","South {0}","West {0}","{0} Repeat Counter","Ichihime defeats {0}!","Ichihime releases extra attack!","Ichihime recovers {0} HP!","Ichihime defeats {0} and gets {1} damage!","Ichihime gains reward: {0}","No deal-in game, Ichihime recovers {0} HP!","Ichihime is fighting {0}…","Ichihime regroups and makes a comeback!","ATK {0}","Next:{0}","Max HP {0}","Next:{0}","Dodge {0}","Critical {0}","Defeat the enemies to advance! You may get limited tablecloth, limited title, and other rich rewards!","Enter a Ranked Match in Silver Room or higher, or enter a match from the event page, then Cat Warrior Ichihime will fight. Click the ? button to see the detailed rules.","Summer Festival Event: Invincible Ichihime \nEvent Time: 8/25 - 9/14 1:59 P.M. (UTC-7)\nCat Warrior Ichihime enters the battle! Defeat the enemies in front of Ichihime to advance! You may get limited tablecloth, limited title, and other rich rewards!\n\nDuring event, after you enter a match in Silver Room or higher in Ranked Match, or use the event page to be allocated in a match, Cat Warrior Ichihime will fight. You will receive rewards after you clear a stage.\n\n*Clear Stage 20 to get Limited Animated Tablecloth - Goldfish Scooping\n*Clear Stage 30 to get Limited Title – Invincible Ichihime\n\nIn the first 20 stages, you will get one Attribute Point for clearing one stage. Use them to increase Cat Warrior Ichihime’s combat stats and become stronger!\nATK: Levels up Cat Warrior Ichihime’s ATK, increasing the damage she causes.\nDEF: Levels up Cat Warrior Ichihime’s Max HP and heals part of HP.\nSPD: Levels up Cat Warrior Ichihime’s Dodge Rate, gives her a chance to avoid damage.\nLUK: Levels up Cat Warrior Ichihime’s Critical Rate, gives her a chance to deliver critical hits\n\n*5 new stages will be unlocked every day during event.\n*The rate of damage caused and received in 3-player matches will be 1/3 of the match points\n\nEvent Match Calculation Details\nMatch Mode: Event Match - 4-Player East\nRank Limit: None\nOrder Bonus: 1st +15, 2nd +5, 3rd -5, 4th -15\nEntry Limit: 5000 Coppers\nExchange Rate: 1000 Points = 50 Coppers\nEntry Fee: 1000 Coppers\nNo Rank Bonus\nCasual Chest Progress: 1st +260, 2nd +130, 3rd +95, 4th +60\nYou will receive Coppers if you finish with positive match points, or lose Coppers if you finish in negativity.","怪物名","Savant Cat","Baker Cat","Serious Cat","Egyptian Cat","Bean Sprout Cat","Phantom Thief Cat","SAMUrai Date Cat","Fisher Cat","Pumpkin Cat","Delinquent Cat","Maid Cat","Fortune Cat","Roadblock Cat","Boss:Muscular White","Boss:Muscular Yellow","Boss:Muscular Grey","Ichihime, ready to attack!","Ichihime attacks {0}!","Critical attack!","","Deals {0} damage!","{0} is defeated!","","Ichihime encounters {0}!","{0} is about to attack!","{0} attacks Ichihime!","Ichihime dodges!","Ichihime is defeated, {0} recovers all HP.","Win! Ichihime attacks!","Deal-in, Ichihime receives damage...","Opponent Tsumo, Ichihime receives damage...","Cat Warrior Ichihime has reached \nthe max limit of enemies defeated today!","Cat Warrior Ichihime \nhas defeated all enemies!","Summer=The Sea=Cold Drinks! I\'m gonna continue my winning streak against master in this year\'s water gun battle. And whoever losses is gonna buy the winner cold drinks for the entire summer, nyaa!","Popsicles! It\'s showtime!","Don\'t tell me this is the reason why I am alone at the Mahjong Soul Shrine!","Hehe, that shortie has something to offer, you don\'t say!","Get lost, you evil hare, nyaa!!!","RIP to my wallet... Well, as long as you behave, you can have all the cold drinks you like.","You\'re the best master in the world, nyaa! Then I guess I\'ll just play a little bit less serious this time, just a little bit!","I\'m going all out this time. So bring it on!","Hmmph, my master, don\'t say I didn\'t warn you, nyaa!","Wanna see me in my bikini? Keep the gifts coming and prove to me that you are worth it! Just a few nice comments are not gonna get me to the beach under that burning sun, alright? So, what are you waiting for? Come to my stream and show me how bad you guys wanna see those bikinis!","Dear fans, only 287 more gifts are needed for Hibiki to become the TOP 1 popular streamer this month. Let\'s make it happen!!","Ahahah... Hibiki posted another chat! She\'s still as vibrant as ever!","Oh no, I\'m late. Going to the stream right now.","Did Hibiki reply to me today?","Nope.","Wow, a bunch of comments just in the blink of an eye. Let\'s see if this post catches her attention.","Be the TOP 1 in Hibiki\'s live stream gift ranking, and you\'ll become Hibiki\'s special following on CatChat. All comments from special followings will be replied to. What do you say? Don\'t tell me you\'re not tickled!","Looks like someone is being replied to by Hibiki. Hibiki\'s fans, let\'s thumb \'em up for everyone to see!","Thumb \'em up!","Thumb \'em up!","Thumb \'em up!","Let\'s play a game. If you lose, you\'ll have to accompany me to the beach this weekend. How about that?","Tsk, you really don\'t know when to quit, don\'t you? Well, since you\'re brave enough to challenge me, how about incorporating this bet into my live stream by the beach on the weekend? Losers will be wearing a bikini. Down for the challenge?","Thumb \'em up!","Thumb \'em up!","Thumb \'em up!","Yes! Holidays are finally here. I\'m coming, beautiful sea! Haruna\'s definitely gonna conquer you this time. Come and follow Haruna, @{0}!","Hmph, Chiori guesses only the likes of you will never get bored with this kid\'s game and play it every single year.","Eh? Isn\'t Chiori a kid too?","UV rays are strong at the beach. You might wanna put on some sunscreen.","Haruna\'s not afraid of that! Well, you better get well soon and join the fun.","Say no more! I\'ll cover you!","So reliable, General {0}, Haruna\'s right about you!","Don\'t fool around, what if you get yourself into the deep waters again?!","Well... I have you looking out for me, right?","I\'ve prepared quite a selection of sunblocks, and I\'m sure there is one that suits you, onesan. I\'ll protect your skin from being charred by the sun! @{0}","Don\'t give {0} a hard time when you\'re out.","Chill out. I am no trouble to onesan since I am pretty obedient myself. Onesan, am I right? @{0}","Oh, Little Ryan is heading to the beach too? Hehe, looking forward to seeing you there!","Get back early. The customers are getting upset after knowing your absence in the upcoming performances.","It seems that someone has made better preparation than me. Looking forward to this seaside trip!","Happiness is knowing that no one other than onesan and I will be at the beach. The same goes for you, right onesan?","So many sunblocks... Why do I have a bad feeling?!","Onesan, are you concerned about the quality of the sunblocks? If that\'s the case, let\'s hang out one day before the trip. You can try the products on me, and I, Ryan, don\'t mind being your guinea pig!","According to today\'s fortune, good luck awaits when bringing this bag along when heading out.","Hmph, you won\'t even budge when I invited you out. And now you\'re saying that you\'re heading to the beach? You\'re acting sus!","Looking forward to your interesting stories by the beach when you returned. Or some funny stories about that kid!","That bag looks great on you. Besides that, is there anything foretold by the fortune regarding this trip?","Fortune says that you have good taste in picking a swimming suit as it matches well with my bag.","The luck doesn\'t get better than having me tagging along.","Do you realize the significance of something that can alter the fortune of a fortune-teller?","It seems that Chiori can still fit in the swimming suit from last year. It\'s just that the design looks kinda outdated already.","Nothing looks outdated on Miss Chiori, but my swimming suit looks kind of small for me now. How about getting a new one together, Miss Chiori?","Not again... Come on...","Let\'s have some watermelon shave ice. Rumor has it that they\'ve launched a new recipe, nyaa!","Chiori, wanna join me and {0}\'s adventure?","This swimming suit looks fine on you.","Hmph, as always, you\'re just brushing me off by saying that. No doubt that Chiori is cute, but it\'s getting old already if the same praises keep coming.","Maybe a change in clothes to alter your mood?","Hmph, Chiori doesn\'t care about your preference. However, Chiori is kind enough to give you a chance to express yourself. Spill the tea.","Mas.. master. I think I\'ve yet to master the art of swimming. Can you please not stray too far from me when I\'m going in the waters?","Hehe, little Aihara is still as cute as ever. Why don\'t you have {0} teach you how to swim. Perhaps you\'ll be surprised with what you\'re capable of!","Based on how much I know about {0}, I think you might be in good hands... perhaps.","Don\'t you fret. I can\'t swim too, so let\'s enjoy ourselves in shallow waters.","Okay, I\'ll stay close to you, master.","Don\'t worry, I\'m a good swimmer. Aihara is safe with me.","Did I just... cause more trouble to master again? I hope I\'m not too cumbersome...","All thanks to sheer good luck, how unexpected that {0} could win us a two-person trip at the beach when we were having our dinner, haha! I\'m so psyched right now. Nature, let me embrace your beauty with my surfboard!","Tsk, {0}, if you really wanna embrace the beauty of nature, you should follow me to the woods for some training.","Hunting may be important, but resting during half-time is equally important. You might not wanna tire {0} out.","Days of Mahjong games without you guys will be pretty mundane. Regardless of that, have fun!","Hmm... Will the tail feel heavy after being soaked in water? And cause imbalance?","Oh yeah! I\'m so hyped!","Well then, let\'s learn some basic moves after dinner. If you can\'t learn, then you can\'t go to sleep!","Uhh, such an extreme activity right away, will it be a problem QAQ?","Relax, leave everything to me and surf all your way up to the top of the waves without a care in the world.","God, everyone is having fun at the beach, while I am all alone at the north enduring the chilling weather. George is almost frozen... Next year\'s program will be... No, the show must be filmed by the beach.","Break a leg, senior.","If this year\'s viewer\'s quota is achieved, this can be considered.","George: Try to look smiley.jpg","Haha, that expression doesn\'t change the fact that George will be all cordial again when seeing you after returning from our shoot.","If your shooting doesn\'t take place at the beach next year, we can still plan our holiday there.","Nice. I\'m already thinking about which unchartered waters we could explore.","It\'s summer again, a season that belongs to youngsters. So bustling!","You\'re already at the beach. I\'ll be right there after finishing my work.","I\'ll be here for a few days. Don\'t rush with your work.","We were supposed to have drinks tonight, but now I can\'t make it because of this last-minute errand, sigh... I wanna have a good drink while enjoying the sea breeze, too.","I got you. Let\'s drink to our heart\'s content after you\'re back.","Can I tag along?","I won\'t be responsible if you are barred from home for returning home too late.","I heard that there is a music festival at that beach during the nighttime. Wanna check it out later?","Let\'s go.","Heading to the beach is an annual event. It\'s just that I was exceptionally psyched this year.","I recommend Limoncello to all employees who cannot be on the beach this summer.","Sandcastle... Let\'s head to the beach during the next summer holiday.","Hmm... I might know who tagged along to the beach with you.","Lemme guess, is it because of your companion?","Well then, my dear companion, were you exhilarated about this beach trip?","Me too.","Let\'s make it happen again next year.","I may not be able to go to the beach, but the fun doesn\'t fade at the school\'s swimming pool.","If you didn\'t have to take those extra lessons, you\'d be at the beach with us already.","Those damn lessons. I\'ll make sure nothing gets in my way next time!","If I\'m not mistaken, you\'re assigned to clean the swimming pool instead of having fun. Make sure you can finish your cleaning by evening.","T.T, forgive me, vice-president. I\'ll finish my task in no time.","Speaking of that, I think we haven\'t gone to the beach together. It\'s time to pick a sexy swimming suit for you, haha.","Will it be... too much for me?","Let me help you with the cleaning.","Now that\'s my favorite junior right there. You\'re just as reliable as ever!","I wanna have fun at the swimming pool, too.","Sure thing, but you must help me with the cleaning before that.","The coconut trees by the beach look pleasant. I wonder if there are any species that I can plant in the school garden.","Best to keep your perplexing yet scary idea to yourself.","Coconut... I am not envying, for real, QAQ","Coconut is delicious.","Hear, hear! Especially those coconut milk puddings. They only sell 50 of those every afternoon. They\'re really awesome!","Planting plants with high esthetical value is a walk in the park in One Han City, but to plant delightful coconuts might not be that easy.","Damn it, never have I imagined that planting is more troublesome than playing Mahjong.","I heard that we\'ll be spending our time at the beach until dusk. Therefore, I\'ve prepared some simple meals. I wonder if it caters to everyone\'s taste.","Fooood... I\'m hungry as heck.","Now that explains the reason Shaun said someone brought something that smells good. Apparently, there is!","Xenia\'s beef veggie wrap tastes really good!","I couldn\'t figure out what you like, so I just make them following my mom\'s recipe. Well, it looks like it turns out pretty fine.","Can I help out the next time you\'re preparing food? I could sense that you\'ll look super cute when preparing them.","Preparing them might just be a breeze, but if you can help out, I believe they will turn out to be even tastier.","Firework Festival is the best, nyaa! Candy apple, grilled squid, watermelon sorbet, takoyaki, chocolate banana... And of course, master by my side, nyaa!","Ichihime looks really adorable when she is eating.","Want some takoyaki, Mai?","I heard someone didn\'t manage to scoop a single goldfish today, uhehe!","That\'s because someone changed my net behind my back! Fess up! Was that your doing?","Every time I see these two, I can\'t help but be touched by their close friendship, hehe!","We\'re not close!","We\'re not close, nyaa!","Hurry up finishing the food, we\'re going to see the fireworks next.","These two candy apples and three boxes of takoyaki are for master, nyaa! Do you want some grilled squid as well?","I\'m ranked after food?","Master is the most important, nyaa! Firework Festival is the best because of master, nyaa! Then comes candy apple, grilled squid, watermelon sorbet, takoyaki, chocolate banana, nyaa!","You asked to see the fireworks, don\'t be late.","Speaking of which, this is the first time I encounter the Firework Festival since I got here, but I won\'t get in the way of your plans, have a great time!","Remember to get in touch with your father, don\'t make him worry.","Boss, should we get the organizer to reserve a viewing spot for you?","No need.","Wait, I haven\'t decided what to wear yet!","Alright, I\'ll make an exception for you again. But no complaint if we don\'t get the ideal spot.","By the way, the ones from last time suited you well, you looked wonderful.","If I arrive early, is there a reward?","Then do you have any rewards for me, considering I\'ve been waiting here for 15 minutes already?","Soul\'s Autumn Tour is about to start and everyone has prepared new programs for this tour. Please stay tuned!","I finally get a chance to show my magic to onesan! I\'m really excited! Oh, I need to send onesan an invitation first!","I\'ve already sent out the invitation, hehe!","New tour?! I can\'t have anyone not knowing this!","Thank you for your support!","Won\'t you reconsider teaching your kitty a trick or two?","Being cute is enough!","Has Sara prepared a new dance as well?","Two new dances, one of them is special and for your eyes only. Will come to see it?","Autumn Tour... Let me check when I have time.","Soul will reserve a VIP seat for you every day, so you have to come~","Question: Will there be... masks that {0} likes?\nKR-976 invites {0}: Do you want to attend the Firework Festival with KR-976?\nOptions: YES   NO","Oni mask... I like it.","Automatic reply from KR-976: Battery Charging.","Yes, {0} wants to attend the Firework Festival with KR-976.","Data record: {0} promises to attend the Firework Festival with KR-976.","Speaking of masks, how about Anju choosing one for me?","Question: Does {0} want the same kind of mask as KR-976? From a human perspective, it should look cool.","A rare holiday, should I go find some big news or take a good rest?","Me and Ayane are going to the seaside and have a drinking party. Wanna come?","*Sob* Chief, please take a day off... There\'s enough work we need to catch up on, please don\'t add to our workload...","Since it\'s a rare holiday, why don\'t we go out and walk around?","Considering what a trouble maker you are, walking around with you is no relaxing feat, hehe~ But since you\'ve invited me, don\'t even think about running away. So set a time.","I\'ve heard there are many events recently, there must be stuff that\'s newsworthy.","Those kinds of crowded places are very accident-prone, hehe~ In that case, come help me find a big scoop!","OK, go.","x","You are still so taciturn... Talk a bit more to me.","OK, I\'ll accompany you.","If you talk on Catchat like that, no one else can understand what you mean.","That\'s not important. I only need you understanding my words.","I have put a spell on this image yesterday, those blessed by the gods will see white and gold stripes, and those not blessed will only see blue and black stripes, uhehe!","White and gold.","Do white and gold, blue and black look different? Aren\'t they the same-woof?","Loading failed, nyaa!","Arere, the picture is uploaded with no loss, could it be that only you can\'t see it, uhehe? What an incompetent priestess~","White and gold!","Yes, not bad, a human blessed by me.","Loading failed.","You are an honest one, uhehe! It seems I need to pay more attention to you in the future so that you won\'t get swindled by others.","{0}, you are really not coming to the Firework Festival with us? It\'s super lively here.","If I knew in advance, I would have returned from the seaside in time for the Firework Festival.","It\'s not too late to get back now. It\'s gonna continue a long time, hehe","I found a good spot, come quickly.","I\'ve got takoyaki and marshmallow, coming now.","Takanashi\'s yukata is very cute!","I\'m a little embarrassed to be complimented all of a sudden, ehehe! I want to see {0} in yukata as well!","I won\'t be able to make it today, but the next time I will!","Really? But when is the next time?","If anyone saw {0}, please let me know the location!","I just saw {0} go the opposite direction of where you are.","Thanks!","Didn\'t you go see the fireworks with {0}? You got... separated?","If I knew there are so many people, I won\'t have gone to buy the drinks alone...","Tell me your location and don\'t move, I\'ll go find you.","?! I am at the yakisoba stand, can you find it? Or I can go find you, my stamina is better.","I got caught up in the crowd and am at the goldfish scoop now...","Stay there, don\'t be afraid, I\'ll get to you soon!","Actually the rooftop of Mahjong Soul Shrine is the best viewing spot.","You are just too lazy to squeeze in the crowds like the young ones.","I had no idea the view was so good from there, next time you won\'t have it for yourself, hehe.","Wanjirou, you sly dog, why didn\'t you take me with you if the view is so great?","Now I have told you, it\'s a secret between us. The roof won\'t hold up if too many people were here.","As someone responsible for the Mahjong Soul Shrine, you set a bad example by climbing the roof! I reserved a spot for you!","Since you are inviting me so sincerely... Well, it\'s not like I can\'t squeeze in with y\'all.","Kana Is Best Girl","Light Chaser","noticeME_Kana","ID What ID","Kana Love","Dojo Owner At Large","Suuankou Quest","Ryo","Preparations for Asaha High School\'s costume party, \"Witching Hour\", have begun!\nThis time around, we also received a sponsorship from a special guest. Everybody, make sure to follow the rules while you\'re having fun, or else... Hmm, let me think of a scary punishment. Maybe I\'ll put you on the vice president\'s troubled teen list. What do you think? Hehe...","Whether it\'s during the party or not, I have my eyes on any slackers. BTW, dear president, you\'ve been late 3 times in this month alone. The clock is ticking. You\'ve got 23 minutes to give me a reason for your chronic tardiness.","About that... I apologize. It will never happen again.","Why does Liisa Liisa get the feeling the president means, \"I\'m sorry, but I\'ll do it again!\" Shaun\'s in the same boat.","LOL... Shh, don\'t expose me.","Requesting a day off.","Declined.","Why are you hating on a school activity lol? You\'re a vital member of this place, too.","Isn\'t this the cake I helped bake this afternoon? Looks like it turned out pretty good. I wonder if that person will like it.","Come on, even if you don\'t believe in yourself, you gotta believe in the cake!","I wonder... How does the cake taste?","There are a thousand tastes in a thousand Hamlets\' mouths. You can only know the actual taste by eating it yourself. I will allow you to have a bite beforehand, I\'m sure you\'ll like it.","What are you going to dress up for the party?","Now that\'s a secret. Let\'s see if you can find me behind those masks. A test of our bond lol!","I might be a bit sad if you can\'t find me. But it\'s fine because I can always find you.","Yahoo!!! This time, I\'m dressing as Kana-chan from the woods. Behold the charm of my LOVELOVE magic.\nHehe. I put this witch outfit together specially for the Witching Hour costume party. How is it? Does it fit okay?","That\'s not half bad. It suits you. So cute!","Senpai! Hehe. You\'re so sweet. I\'m flattered! I\'ll keep doing my best!","Am I the first one to see Kana the Witch?!!! I\'m gonna carry Kana the Witch and run!!!","UwU Why on earth does Kana look so good? She would make wearing a sack look good! (I\'m not saying that her outfit isn\'t nice, but it definitely looks as good as it does because she\'s wearing it)","Why does that witch outfit suit Kana-chan so well? Dang it, why don\'t I go to Asaha High School?!!!","Why does that witch outfit suit Kana-chan so well? Dang it, why don\'t I go to Asaha High School?!!!","Why does that witch outfit suit Kana-chan so well? Dang it, why don\'t I go to Asaha High School?!!!","Indeed, why does the witch outfit suit Kana-chan so well? It\'s a good thing that I\'m going to the party, too, hehe.","I\'m an idol, so I have to be able to look good in anything! I see that you\'re a big fan of my new costume. That\'s good!","Holy moly! Let\'s fight fair and square, my rival in love!","Holy moly! Let\'s fight fair and square, my rival in love!","I won\'t fight you! Just hand me your party invite!!!","I\'m gonna get rid of the costume I have right now and make an adventurer outfit instead. No witch would ditch an unconscious adventurer in the forest, right?","Getting rescued by a witch comes at a price, you know. Pathetic adventurer, prepare to accept your fate!","I hereby declare myself Adventurer #1. Take your number tag and wait in line!","I\'m Adventurer #2. You stay in the back!","I\'m late. Any adventurer tags left?","Oh no, I forgot to prepare an outfit... Can I still make it on time?","If it isn\'t careless, it isn\'t Nana, lol. But there is still plenty of time. I\'m just a call away if you need any help!","Where should I start...?","I\'ve told the drama club to provide outfits to all attendees during the dance. Register for one and then take good care of it.","QAQ Vice President, hands down, you\'re the best.","There\'s still plenty of time before the party starts. If you have any ideas, I don\'t mind helping you out.","Actually... I couldn\'t think of anything because I wanna try everything. How about a werewolf? It looks strong and sharp!","I\'m looking forward to your makeover, whether it\'s a vampire, a witch, a mad scientist, a damsel in disguise... A mermaid seems like a good choice, too.","M-Mermaid?! Then wouldn\'t I be soaking in a pool the entire night?! Well... I suppose it\'s not actually a bad idea, since swimming is my forte.","Alright, I\'m all dressed up, but there\'s no way I\'ll recite the spells. If all of you really want me to do that, I wouldn\'t mind reading the school motto out loud.","That\'s cold, Ren!","Dear President, as I\'ve mentioned before, please kindly abstain yourself from scrolling through CatChat during work.","Did you just share a post to bait me?!!!","It worked pretty well, wouldn\'t you say?","Look on the bright side. At least the vice president is willing to make a compromise. Looks like our next party might be a good one.","I prefer to call it a \"Student Council responsibility\" instead of \"making a compromise\".","Judging by the looks of the outfit, it doesn\'t take a genius to guess who picked it, lol!","Keep your opinion to yourself.","If you\'re too shy to say the spell, whisper it to me. I promise to not tell anybody above.","I refuse.","But... If you can somehow become more obedient after I say the spell, I might just think about it.","That outfit looks perfect on you. Mimi is also slaying it with that mask.","Are you bragging about your own taste?","But I have to say, you do have good taste in many ways.","I heard that dressing up as a fearsome villain would really spice up the party. Perhaps Liisa Liisa should attend the party as Mr. Wolf?","You must be a cute werewolf then, Eliisa. But I\'ll train you, so you\'ll look stronger!","No way! Liisa Liisa and Shaun don\'t need any training!","If that Mr. Wolf looks like what I think it does, that doesn\'t really count as dressing up!","Yeah? You city slickers\' rules are overwhelming, and Liisa Liisa doesn\'t understand a thing... QAQ","I\'m the scary villain?","Isn\'t Mr. Wolf the most charming villain in One Han City?! But Liisa Liisa knows that deep down, you\'re a good wolf!","Then it\'s decided. See these furry wolf ears and tail? Wear them, and you\'ll transform into a wolf.","Wow, these feel nice. Speaking of which, why does Mr. Wolf not have furry ears or a furry tail? Liisa Liisa wants to touch Mr. Wolf\'s ears, too!","I received a lot of guidance from Asaha High School during my visit to One Han City, which is why I am also attending the Witching Hour costume party as a special guest.\nI\'m the little succubus at the reception. Let\'s dance!","This grown-up outfit looks great on you, Xenia.","I bet it will look just as good on you, too, Chiori.","I prefer something cute. Grown-up outfits... aren\'t my style!","Lady succubus, please take my soul.","Offering your soul to a demon isn\'t very safe, you know. But since I\'m a kind succubus, I\'ll spare you and return your soul after the party.","Shout out like a madman to Xenia. I\'m applying to be a receptionist right away.","You might need to ask the president for the arrangement. But I think he\'ll probably agree since it\'s you. Looking forward to working with you tonight!","Costume parties are all about attracting the limelight, so everyone will be trying to become the center of attention by dressing up in gorgeous outfits.\nSo I think whoever has the most low-key outfit might be the real center of the attention since they\'ll stick out... That\'s why I\'ve come up with a ballsy idea.","That\'s the devil inside of you talking. You need a chill pill.","No, it\'s very calculated! It\'s just as likely to succeed as it is to get All Simples.","Huh? Hey, I wanna know what the ballsy idea is!","Any good Jyanshi does not simply expose her trump card.","Are you gonna go to the dance without any makeup?","I know I\'m just a regular high schooler, but that\'s kinda rude! I\'m gonna knock your socks off, just you wait!","Wearing the most low-key outfit... All I can think of is a tree in the background.","Were you always cast as a tree in primary school plays, too? But this time, I\'m trying something bolder. Stay tuned.","Let me see which pretty, charming, pathetic creature will trespass on this forbidden land on a forbidden night. Don\'t be shy, you\'ll have the time of your life, KUKUKUKU!","You\'re going to scare the students if you keep talking like that!","KUKUKU—— The Dark Chief does not utter any words without purpose. They will surely experience a night they won\'t forget.","Are you by any chance the special guest the president mentioned? The cup thingy you\'re holding looks pretty dangerous.","Rest assured, there won\'t be anything prohibited in Lullaby\'s Bloody Mary for all of you at the party. It will just make you so happy, you\'ll get lost in ecstasy.","QAQ I\'m the poor little thing who got lost and accidentally trespassed into the castle. Mr. Natsuki, can you take me in?","Of course. Since you are unable to find your way back, you\'re welcome to continue to lose your way here.","I know. Someone from the Student Council said that you will be the bartender at the party!","Being too honest during the costume party might lead you to become an offering of the night. Since you know so much, how about you stay and be my assistant.","Who says that witches have to wear a conventional long dress. All you need is to raise the hemline, pair it with a chain belt, leave the fabric by the chest, then alter the back of the dress with sheer black panelling. Finally, put on rotten tomato red lipstick as the icing on the cake. Perfection!","Sounds sexy.","Yup, being stylish is all about having the right amount of sexiness!","I was about to vote for the conventional witch, but the reinvented version ain\'t half bad.","Hehe, think about it, Hana. Maybe I could tailor a stylish costume for you?","A suggestion: white pearl accessories would probably go very well with a black dress.","Sound advice. That\'ll add more elegance. It\'s not sexy enough, but still worth a try!","Kirara, I can\'t wait to see your new clothes!","Since you\'re so eager, let\'s meet up and have some dessert before the party.","Yay, I\'m finally done with my part. The party can officially start now. Can I go to sleep now...?","Nana did just as much work as you, and look at her, you weakling.","I don\'t know why, Hana, but that doesn\'t sound like a compliment... QAQ","I\'m exhausted due to mental and physical stress.","According to the plan, you still have three tasks to do tonight.","Ren, you\'re a monster...","Ten, nine, eight, seven...","What are you counting?","I\'m counting down a certain someone\'s arrival. You could use some motivation you know, lol!","Don\'t you dare falter before the party. I\'m looking forward to seeing your outfit tonight!","Rest assured, this is nothing. I still have the strength to carry you around the field three times!","How about taking a short break in the lounge after the party starts?","A gentleman does not simply leave his partner in the middle of the dance floor alone. Don\'t worry, I can even take you home after the dance ends.","Expand","Rewards","Training","Missions","Current Stage","Battle Log","Claim Rewards","All","Summer Festival Event: Peerless Ichihime \nEvent Time: 8/9 - 9/2 1:59 P.M. (UTC-7)\n\nCat Warrior Ichihime is back! This summer, Ichihime will show her god-blessed might and defeat them all!\n\nDuring event, after you enter a match in Ranked Match, Tournament Match or Friendly Match with no AI, Cat Warrior Ichihime will fight the enemies. When the stages are cleared, you will receive an abundance of rewards including Limited Call Tile Indicator, Limited Animated Tablecloth, Summon Scroll, and more!\n*Conversion rate of winning points: 4-Player 100:1; 3-Player and matches with special rules (e.g. DoraDorara) 300:1.\n*Battle of Asura and Bloodshed Skirmish are excluded from this event.\n\nDuring the event, 3 stages will be unlocked daily.\nClear Stage 30 to get Limited Call Tile Indicator - Gurgling Stream.\nClear Stage 45 to get Limited Animated Tablecloth - Seaside Purple Glow.\n\nComplete event missions to get Skill Pts.\nEvery skill can reach Lv3 at maximum, train Ichihime to make her stronger!\n\nBasic Training: Increases DMG of all attacks.\nRhythm Master: Win before a certain turn to increase DMG dealt.\nInstant Kill: Win with a certain Han or above to increase DMG dealt.\nJack of All Trades: Win with a certain number (or more) of Yakus to increase DMG dealt.\nGreat Tactician: Win when waiting for a certain number (or more) winning tiles to increase DMG dealt.\n*Please check the details of the skills on the \"Training\" page.","Basic Training","Rhythm Master","Instant Kill","Jack of All Trades","Great Tactician","Lv","Activate!","Cat Warrior Ichihime attacks {0}! Deals {1} DMG!","Cat Warrior Ichihime attacks {0}! Critical hit! Deals {1} DMG!","Cat Warrior Ichihime has reached the max limit of enemies defeated today!","Cat Warrior Ichihime has defeated all enemies!","{0} is defeated!","Lv1: Increases DMG of all attacks by 5%.","Lv2: Increases DMG of all attacks by 10%.","Lv3: Increases DMG of all attacks by 15%.","Lv1: Win before Turn 9 to increase DMG dealt by 10%.","Lv2: Win before Turn 12 to increase DMG dealt by 20%.","Lv3: Win before Turn 15 to increase DMG dealt by 30%.","Lv1: Win with Baiman or above to in