! Do you know what this means?\nMooncakes! Mooncakes, nyaa!\nThey have all sorts of filling, like red bean paste, coconut paste, five kernels, jujube puree, pineapple, lotus seed paste with salted egg yolk, runny egg custard, rose ham, and... Oh, I almost forgot, nyaa! There\'s also a limited-edition ume and crab roe mooncake jointly released by Mahjong Soul Shrine and Asaha High School, nyaa!","Somehow I can\'t tell who\'s the winner here, you or the president?","Ishihara said this is called win-win, nyaa!","Vice president, it sounds like there\'s an inside story! Putting my ears here.jpg","Fujita, your attendance rate is getting dangerously close to being too low because of your frequent idol performances this year... I hope you can make up for it at Asaha\'s Mid-Autumn Festival celebration.","QAQ, I got careless...","I just played at Luck and Fortune for a few days, and now you are releasing limited-edition mooncakes? Of such an unconventional flavor, too, woof...","When we were playing Mahjong last week, Ishihara and Ichihime made a bet, that the loser would be responsible for Mahjong Soul Shrine\'s mid-autumn mooncake this year. Unexpectedly, the win was intercepted with Four Concealed Triplets, hehe!","Wanjirou! COME BACK NOW! Nyaa! There\'s still a pile of mooncakes that haven\'t been packed yet, nyaa! If you don\'t help, you\'ll only get to eat five-kernel mooncake this year, nyaa!","Damn... The holy Mahjong Soul Shrine has been corrupted... Even mooncakes are limited-edition now? And they look so damn sweet and delicious, too! Ahhh!","...The CatChat server clearly was under maintenance for too long earlier, and everyone must be itching to post. I feel like I\'m watching a TV drama here...","Ume and... crab roe? Will those two combined really taste good?","Nyaa? Ume is delicious, and crab roe is delicious, nyaa. So shouldn\'t they taste super delicious together, nyaa?","It looks like you haven\'t tried it yet...","Of course I haven\'t! I have to save the most delicious mooncake and eat it with Master on the day of the festival, nyaa! But both Master and the Mid-Autumn Festival are taking so long to arrive, nyaa...","Why does it seem like Ichihime is always saying food names when I view her CatChat? I must say, she\'s as good at this as she is at announcing the Yaku list after a game.","Nyaa? It\'s okay if Master wants Ichihime to add the things from Master\'s daily itinerary, such as eating an extra bowl of rice at noon or dealing into Big Three Dragons at Mahjong in the afternoon, to her CatChat, nyaa! After all, like what Miki said, CatChat is for showing everyone her favorite things. Ichihime likes both Master and food, nyaa!","So it\'s almost the Mid-Autumn Festival. I was wondering why there are fewer and fewer people at the dojo. They must be busy going home to reunite with their families...\nMaybe I should close the dojo and celebrate the festival somewhere since this is such a big day.","The second floor of Magical Dream is a rare moon-viewing spot of One Han City, and we can make a reservation for you at any time.","After so many years, you won\'t fool me again this time. Every time I go there, all I can do is drink tea. Tea! TEA! It\'s not a good Mid-Autumn Festival if you can\'t admire the moon with a bottle of good wine...","Be careful, it\'s easy to put on weight during the Mid-Autumn Festival, woof.","Wanjirou, I mean... I think YOU should be more concerned about that given your current figure.","I received some good tea a few days ago, and I was actually thinking about inviting Fu Ji to celebrate the festival with me...","What a coincidence, haha! I recently got a few bottles of good wine as well, and we aren\'t like Fei Ming. How can you do business if you don\'t drink at all? I\'ll come find you tomorrow.","Luck and Fortune—Can you not close for the day? I want to play Mahjong, maam!","Oh? {0}, are you inviting me to play Mahjong with you? Let me think about it since it\'s rare for you to be so proactive. How about this? If you win, I\'ll give you a 30% discount for next year.","Fu Ji, you seem to really like the Mid-Autumn Festival. If you don\'t have plans, we can celebrate it together.","Everyone in One Han City loves this festival where people reunite with their families. After all, in the past... Oh, {0}, are you trying to make me have a slip of the tongue? But since you made such a good suggestion, I won\'t mind telling you about the origin of the Mid-Autumn Festival when we view the moon together.","NYAA!!!\nWho switched out the cat paw-shaped ume crab roe mooncakes that Ichihime painstakingly made with bunny head-shaped mooncakes, nyaa!\nWho did this, nyaa!","Um... I didn\'t expect the mooncakes at the shrine to be tampered with too. Actually, it\'s not just the appearance—even the filling has been changed to a mixture of matcha and wasabi...","You didn\'t eat it, right?","I thought it was a new product created by someone in the pastry club...","Does this mean there won\'t be any limited-edition mooncakes this year, nyaa?","That might really be the case if we can\'t find them before tomorrow... Hahahaha...","How can this be, nyaa! I haven\'t given any to Master yet, nyaa...","The Temple of Moons also received this type of mooncake this morning... It was placed on top of the altar.","Mai, did you see the culprit, nyaa?","Sorry... It was here when I got up in the morning. If only I got up a little earlier...","Based on this shape... Oho! Once we eliminate the impossible, whatever remains, however unreasonable, can only be the truth.","Nyaa?","Relax, according to my deduction, the culprit will soon expose themself!","This looks kind of familiar...","Master actually knows the culprit, nyaa!","Ichihime, look at the shape of this mooncake. Don\'t you find it a bit familiar?","Nyaa? Ichihime has eaten lots of cookies that come in this shape recently... Which brand is Master talking about, nyaa?","......","If there really aren\'t any clues, it\'s better to make a new batch instead of looking for them. I\'ll help out too this time.","Master is so nice, nyaa... It\'s really nice to have Master by my side whenever I encounter a problem, nyaa... Other than the ume crab roe mooncake, Ichihime also wants to eat mooncakes with chocolate, runny egg custard, or rose ham fillings made by Master, nyaa!","I had a gentle and romantic manicure done for the Mid-Autumn Festival. Haha, what do you think? Does anyone want to challenge it with me? I have an extra set of rhinestone nail stickers.","Wow, something is making you give off a different vibe to your usual hottie vibe, but I can\'t quite say what it is.","Maybe it\'s because I rarely adopt this pink girly style, haha. But following the trend is what a gal should do. Even if I\'m adopting a pink fairy style, I\'ll still be a \"gentle hottie\".","I don\'t know anything about how to be a hottie, but I know you. Haha, just do what you think is right!","Bingo! Nana, you definitely have the talent for being a hottie!","Me, me! I thought this pink color would only go with pale skin, but it goes surprisingly well with various styles.","OK! I\'ll bring it to school after the festival!","Sure enough, Kirara\'s designs are way better than the nail salon\'s! If I knew earlier, I would have asked you to do my nails for me... By the way, with such shiny nails, try not to get caught by Ren when you get to school!","Haha, if I do your manicure, you gonna have to keep this a secret for me, okay? Oh yea, Ms. Ayane, I\'m really curious, who are you going on a date with this time?","That\'s a secret! As your teacher, I don\'t have to answer questions unrelated to health care knowledge!","I want all the data of this design within five minutes... No, I mean, please do my nails with the exact same design!","Haha, {0}, I\'ve prepared a different set for you. I was just waiting to meet you tonight to start our \"Mid-Autumn Festival couple nail\" plan!","This way of celebrating the festival really matches your style. It suits you!","What about you, {0}? Do you celebrate the festival in any particular way...? I suddenly really want to know. {0}, are you the traditional type, or are you the trendy type?","Mortals, today is the day! Worship me to your heart\'s content and dedicate yourselves to me fully, Hee-hee!\nOh, by the way, do you like the Mid-Autumn Festival gift I gave you all recently?","Nyaa! I knew it was you, bad rabbit! Return the mooncakes of Mahjong Soul Shrine, nyaa!","Hehe, midget, I\'ve hidden them somewhere you\'ll never think of!","That\'s right, I\'ll let you in on another secret. This is just the first step in my plan to take over Mahjong Soul Shrine! Hahahaha!","So, a few days ago...","Shush! I don\'t understand what you\'re saying!","Understood.","T-T I announce that the wasabi matcha mooncake developed by Kaguyahime is the best mooncake this year. My nose had been blocked for one week due to a cold, and I recovered immediately after eating one! Kaguyahime is a true deity! Sob sob...","Praise to Kaguyahime!","If I make a wish to you during the Mid-Autumn Festival, will you make my wish come true?","You\'re provoking me, aren\'t you, mortal! Go on, tell me your wish!","Well... Will you be a good bunny and return the mooncakes so we can celebrate this festival happily...?","Hmph!","I knew it was you. So, you\'ve finally decided to make your move to Mahjong Soul Shrine? Hold on... Haven\'t you been saying that you\'ll take over Mahjong Soul Shrine for a long time now?","He-he, this is the wisdom of a deity. Something as important as taking over a shrine should be done on an important day!","Mortal, become my follower! This very day next year will be the anniversary celebration of my occupation of Mahjong Soul Shrine, hahahaha!","Everyone seems to treat the osmanthus tree in the Temple of Moons as a tree of romantic fate... But on a special day like this, I believe the god of this tree will bless everyone with a happy relationship.","The osmanthus tree looks good and smells even better... The only problem is it\'s too unfriendly to the nose, damn it!","No wonder someone new is delivering goods to the shrine these days. Mr. Ein, please take care of your health.","Sure enough, compared to the traditional and complex celebration rituals of Mahjong Soul Shrine, the Temple of Moons is more popular with young couples.","When grandpa was still around, the Temple of Moons would also have traditional celebrations... But I think it is great like this, and the osmanthus tree is running out of space for everyone\'s wishing plaques.","What do you think, Mai? Do you want a perfect relationship?","I... Master, why ask me this all of a sudden? I\'m kinda embarrassed to answer this question...","Actually, Mai has prepared a wishing plaque too... Master, will you hang it on the osmanthus tree with me?","This is the first time I\'ve seen you in such traditional clothing, Mai!","Master... Do I look good? Does it look weird on Mai?","No, it\'s perfect. Mai, you need to be more confident. You look good in everything!","It seems that every legend related to the Mid-Autumn Festival is about people\'s longing for a \"reunion\". Maybe that\'s one of the reasons why the Mid-Autumn Festival is celebrated when the moon is full.\nBut the ancients also said that the moon is rounder on the 16th and not the 15th in the lunar calendar, which means that today is a better day for viewing the moon.","Are you really not considering an editorial position in our magazine? With your experience and talent, you\'ll surely shine in this industry!","Compared to sitting in those office buildings that are lined up in rows, I prefer to have my freedom.","I didn\'t expect Mr. Sammir to know so much about religious and traditional culture, haha. It seems that I really must study more.","I\'ve just seen and heard many things during my travels around the world over the years. I naturally have more experience from meeting more people and experiencing more things. Isn\'t that the same for you, Mr. Saturne?","I\'m curious about these legends. Sammir, you must know a lot of folklore that I haven\'t heard of.","Yes, there\'s a lot indeed, but it\'ll take a long time to tell you. Are you sure you want to listen? It might take an entire night.","Sammir, is there anyone you want to celebrate the festival with? I get the feeling that you\'re always alone in One Han City.","Although I want to say something to make myself look less lonely, unfortunately, I no longer have a family to reunite with... But if you are willing, I\'ll have someone to celebrate the Mid-Autumn Festival with every year in the future.","Um... Nyaa... Does anyone feel like the atmosphere has been strange in One Han City recently, nyaa?","What kind of strange do you mean? Could it be... some impurity?","Nyaa... I don\'t think so. If it was, Mai would be the first to notice, nyaa!","I’m not that amazing... I make mistakes sometimes too...","Are you all lonely because I haven\'t had time to shower you with my attention, Midget?","Why are you everywhere, nyaa! You stupid rabbit, stop appearing whenever people are confused!","Hehe! But you\'re no longer confused now that I\'ve appeared.","That\'s true, she\'s just angry now, woof.","I remember now! It\'s almost time for that festival! I almost forgot to prepare for the store event.","Which event... nyaa?","Halloween! Halloween!!!","Nyaa! No wonder there\'s been such a short supply of pumpkin and candy, nyaa!","So, that atmosphere even Ichihime found to be strange... What would it be?","Nyaa?! Why are you making it sound like I\'m very strange too, nyaa... Hmph! Since you said something bad about Ichihime, I\'ll let you experience my poison-coated claws! Nyaahahahaha!","If it\'s recent, it should be because of Halloween. Everyone is busy preparing to celebrate it.","Master, master, trick or treat!","Don\'t worry, I\'ve prepared your candy a long time ago.","Master, you\'re the best! Nyaa!","A reversed tarot card... Holidays are often accompanied by accidents. If you have any concerns, you are welcome to consult me online.","I caught you in the act! You sly fortune teller, tell me what you\'re really up to!","Did drinking papaya milk have any effect? PS: Drinking papaya milk does not improve one\'s figure.","Provocative words cannot anger the Witch of Justice! Yuzu isn\'t angry at all! Not at all! Hmph!","Miss Kaavi\'s divination has always been very popular among housewives. Based on past experiences, they might really be true.","Eh... Isn\'t it normal for some small accidents to happen occasionally over a period of time? Besides, there are still a few more days before Halloween.","No! The new album is being released this week!","Reschedule it? Find a lucky time?","Good idea! Senpai, please help me convince the president.","Don\'t you usually call Joseph directly by his name?","Shush! We have to save some face for our senpai in public and watch out for scandals and gossip!","Could it be... Could this be because you\'re about to release an album, Kana?","Online divination... How do you see the result?","A photo will be provided. You need to pay extra if you wish to consult via a video call.","Reversed? What card?","The card isn\'t important. What\'s important is the result.","I watched an immersive theater performance with Master today. I didn\'t expect there to be a dress-up photo session... Although I was quite embarrassed, I promised the store to help them with the promotion... If you\'re interested, you can go and have some fun too. I think... it\'s quite interesting.","Whoa! It\'s actually the \"Heart of SAMUel\" theme that Liisa Liisa wants to experience the most! You actually managed to grab a ticket! So impressive!","Actually... Master got the ticket. I only got to watch it because of Master.","Mmmm! {0} didn\'t bring me! That\'s so unfair! If I went, I would get to see Mai wear this set of clothing in person!","Immersive theater... I\'ve been hearing about that a lot at mahjong tables recently. Is it really that fun?","Yeah! But I\'m a little slow and not good at interacting with the NPCs. Master helped me clear all the stages.","Hehe, as I expected, {0} is very skilled at these games!","Mai is perfect for this theme. It looks great! Let\'s try to clear another main story next time.","Yes! I\'ll do my best to help Master complete the missions!","Hey! {0}, you better bring Liisa Liisa and Shaun next time too!","Actually, I\'m not good at this type of game. I only managed to clear it because of Mai.","I think you\'re the best, Master! I... I want to become just like you in the future...","Fly, butterflies, fly!","Has Yui gone to experience the immersive theater as well?!","Yeah, I went to work as a part-time NPC.","You actually started a part-time job behind my back!","By the way, Akechi and Shinomiya were there too.","Damn it! Why does it feel like I\'ve been ostracized...","Good work, Yagi! So many people came to have fun today! Haha, although we had to work overtime, the good vibe just makes me so happy!","You\'ve been working hard too, president. Good thing my character doesn\'t have a lot of lines.","Haha, I\'m here to give Yui a like on behalf of my brother. He is lying down at home and doesn\'t want to say anything.","Shinomiya\'s character... does have a lot to say.","I thought I saw someone familiar in the theater. It really was you!","I saw you too, senpai, but a lot of people have been trying to clear my storyline... It\'s such a shame we couldn\'t meet.","Which character are you dressing as? It\'s a perfect fit for you.","Flora. Senpai, will you experience this main story next time? I can\'t wait to see your performance!","Ichihime has been yammering on about how the Mahjong Soul Shrine needs some holiday vibe during Halloween, and this is all she could come up with?","Haha, isn\'t this the pumpkin I moved to the shrine for the priestess? So it was prepared for you.","It\'s a long story, woof... But it\'s been too noisy on the streets these few days, so I\'ll just meditate and cultivate here in the shrine, woof.","After a priestess with car ears is a pumpkin with cat ears, huh...","Haha, kiddo, you must know that anything is possible in the Mahjong Soul Shrine, woof!","Speaking of which, I just realized that the cat ears on this pumpkin aren\'t carved...","Wow! This scarecrow outfit is perfect for Mr. Wanjirou! Liisa Liisa can sit on Shaun and cosplay as another scarecrow!","Shaun: Where are your manners?","Don\'t underestimate Shaun. Shaun is very strong! Hana, do you want to give it a try?","Thanks for the invite. I\'m in the classroom, and the vice president is outside the window.","Does the cat-headed jack-o-lantern represent Ichihime?","Bingo, {0}! Ichihime said this pumpkin would watch over Mahjong Soul Shrine in her place. I was just too lazy to expose her, woof!","This pumpkin is too solid.","Hmph, ignorant young one, when I was in my prime, I could stand on one leg on top of a tomato, let alone a pumpkin, woof!","I can testify to that. Wanjirou really was strong and healthy back then... But it\'s like what he said, that was way back then...","Mastema is really restless tonight... Maybe it\'s because it can sense others of its own kind...\nAfter all, humans can\'t tell true demons from false ones on this occasion, which makes it the best time to blend in...","Ehhhhh? Are you just saying that to match today\'s atmosphere? Otherwise, that\'s just too terrifying!!!","Sorry...","Question: Can Mastema tell real and fake demons apart?","I think it... can. Mastema is good at this type of thing...","So you\'re saying that many real demons are hiding among us tonight?","It\'s Halloween, after all... {0}, are you carrying the protection amulet I gave you?","Ayako, what character are you dressing up as today?","A witch... Ehehe, I hope I\'ll be an outstanding witch by next year.","I\'m a real witch, not a pretend one!\nThe number one rule of the Law of Witches (reiterated): Humans who underestimate witches will pay a painful price!","How strange, no one seems to have ever doubted my identity as a fortune teller. Why is that?","Damn... One day, humans will understand that clever words are useless! It\'s just a matter of time!","Maybe it\'s because a real witch wouldn\'t skip class to celebrate Halloween.","I\'m not doing this to celebrate Halloween...","So you admit that you\'ve skipped class?","I-I\'m sorry, vice president... QAQ","I can prove that Yuzu is a real witch. The Red Panda Squad found my lost phone for me, and it\'s only because of them that I\'m able to keep scrolling CatChat now! So grateful...","We were just doing our job. Just don\'t fall asleep while playing on your phone on the subway next time. It\'s too dangerous...","I heard I can come here to ask for help... Oh great witch, is there a way to make my ex come back to me?","Huh? My teacher does have a potion that can do that, but I don\'t recommend using it. Your ex... shouldn\'t he be dead to you from the moment you break up?","D-dead? Is he already...?","I mean he is just dead to you mentally... Don\'t worry, witches don\'t kill people for no reason.","I heard that the Witch of Justice will help me if I come here to ask for it. Is that true?","You\'re missing a keyword. I provide help that is \"just\"! Although I help everyone, I won\'t do anything bad! Not even for you, {0}!","I can testify that the witch temperament of Yuzu is unique, and no one can copy it!","Hehe! {0}, as expected of someone who has paid a painful price. It looks like you now have a basic understanding of witches. Congratulations!","Halloween... When I was on the subway last year, I remember someone asking me what I was dressing up as. I was just reading on the subway... Why did someone think I was a monster?","Ehhh... Someone mistakenly thought I was dressing up as a witch a few days ago too! On some level, Halloween truly is fearsome because it can make humans lose the ability to tell true from false...","You... You aren\'t dressed up?","Ehhh?","You\'re still reading a physical book nowadays? Don\'t you think it is heavy?","Only the ignorant would make a fuss out of nothing.","Won\'t you get distracted if you read on the subway...?","I do miss my stop sometimes.","Why don\'t I dress up as something next year too?","...How about Frankenstein?","I can\'t believe you were actually able to read while on the subway when it was so crowded on Halloween night...","It\'s always like that.","This immersive theater experience... I walked out of there half an hour ago, and my head is still buzzing... All I can say is that the things you young people do for entertainment these days are getting more and more demanding, both physically and mentally.","I knew you were only pretending to be weak. That fire in your eyes wasn\'t something you can pretend just by putting on a costume! Let\'s have a showdown!","How many showdowns have you had this month... Geez, can\'t you let my old bones get a rest...?","Did you go with Wanjirou?","No.","I\'m sorry! I mistook the person behind you for Wanjirou.","Woof?","Kukuku! Foolish and ignorant werewolf, it\'s almost the full moon. Prepare for your ugliest moment!","Insolent vampire, I\'ll kill you when the moon is full... Haha, I remember my lines very well.","Are you still not done with playing your character?","Well, this is the most amazing werewolf player we\'ve had in dozens of games!","This outfit is really cool!","To win so much praise from {0} makes it worth it to wear this outfit for half an hour, haha.","But I want to go and play with you again next time.","Well, if you say it like that I guess I\'ll have to keep you company next time, {0}, but can we choose a theme that lets us sit down without moving?","Ha... The days when anyone could challenge and provoke me under the pretense of Halloween are finally over! I thought that only the peasants on the islands would celebrate Halloween... I didn\'t expect the people of One Han City to like it so much too... It\'s so noisy...","Hehe, I was also shocked too when I first arrived. I didn\'t expect to experience such a familiar holiday atmosphere. One Han City is such a wonderful place.","In that case, we will need to make the people of One Han City fall in love with hunting too.","Yeah... but where would the people of One Han City hunt? You\'re not allowed to hurt the animals in the zoo...","Can\'t we make a wish at that Mahjong Soul Shrine? Let them come up with a solution.","Calm down. I know Mr. Zechs is actually a very gentle person. I saw {0} petting your tail, and you didn\'t get angry at all, ehehe!","Damn... That sneak attack was only successful because I wasn\'t paying attention! It wasn\'t voluntary!","Zechs, do the people of your hometown also celebrate Halloween?","We don\'t really celebrate Halloween. This is just a custom of those people on the nearby islands. It\'s really unsightly to see a bunch of demons dancing everywhere... That being said, the people of my clan would hold a large event around the same time since it is the time of the autumn bumper harvest. I\'ll show you next year!","It makes me wanna laugh whenever I think of all those people who were asking where you got such a high-quality tail from!","Damn, stop laughing! If you didn\'t pet it all the time, they wouldn\'t think that I\'m so easy to bully!","The presents of autumn have become the gifts of winter.\nWith some effort, even inconspicuous fallen leaves can become something eye-catching.","I never realized you are so good at handicrafts, Ninomiya. This looks as exquisite as the things they sell in stores. Why don\'t we put you in charge of the Christmas tree in the student council\'s office this year?","President, please don\'t exploit student labor so brazenly under the guise of being open-minded.","Haha, you saw right through me. But this type of Christmas tree seems to be better and more meaningful. Hmm... I\'ve made my decision. We\'ll get Ren to help you make it!","...On second thought, I think I\'ll be able to finish it by myself. Don\'t worry, president, I promise I\'ll finish it before Christmas!","In that case, I can\'t wait to see the finished product. Thanks!","QAQ","The vice president arranged me to sweep the fallen leaves you know. While you\'re having fun, I have to deal with dust, sweat, and scars... *sobs*","If you weren\'t so fixated on the fruit hanging on those high branches, you wouldn\'t have scraped your elbow while climbing the tree.","Aren\'t you curious though, Hana? Like how can there still be fruit as red as that in this season? The vitality of plants is really amazing.","Plants have always had very tenacious vitality. Why don\'t you join the gardening club with me next year to experience it for yourself?","Hmmm... The woolen star at the top of the tree looks kinda familiar. Is that... Shaun?!","I\'m surprised you noticed that. Maybe I should call you E. Hawkeye Liisa instead.","It easily stands out among all the green plants. Can you teach me how to make something like that?","I need to make a bigger one for the student council anyway, so you can come and help me to have some practice.","Not even a single plant has been hurt during the making of this Christmas tree! So this is the strength of the members of the gardening club!","The gardening club is capable of much more than this! Keep your eyes out for more amazing things! What\'s more, these leaves have shaded us all summer, so it would be a pity to just sweep them away like this.","Since they are born, heroes are responsible for saving the world, enduring hunger and cold and working hard in the process. They endured all the hardships alone only to pick up a snowflake—the only harvest this winter.","Haha, what my brother is saying is that the 24th of this month is his birthday, and he wants to get everyone\'s blessings. Of course, it\'ll be even better if there are gifts.","Kukuku, how can a gift bestowed upon a hero by the Heavens be described with a word as simple as \"gift!\"","Okay, whatever... The gift bestowed upon you by the Heavens has been placed at home in advance. Remember to go home early after work on your birthday. Mom and I chose this gift together, and she said you\'ll like it.","Happy birthday!","There is a trace of perfunctoriness in your unpretentious blessing. You didn\'t even realize that today isn\'t the day.","Haha, I\'m just doing it to meet the occasion! Actually, we\'ve prepared a surprise for you.","A surprise? Care for a little spoiler?","It won\'t be a surprise if I tell you. Of course I have to keep it a secret.","Happy birthday.","Sigh... Couldn\'t you at least add an exclamation mark like the president to express your excitement?","!","Hahaha! See? Plenty of people still remember your birthday. Just look at this lively comment section!","I won\'t admit that I\'m actually quite moved. By the way, do you want to come to Lullaby for a drink? They have that special drink you like today.","I was going to play some mahjong tonight, but if you say it like that, how can I not come?","I wish you a happy birthday in advance too!","Thanks, but instead of an early \"happy birthday\", what I want more is to see you on my birthday. How about spending Christmas Eve with me?","I was so busy preparing for Christmas that I forgot such an important thing. Mr. Phantom Thief, is there anything you want for your gift?","Gift, you say? Well... I want something that I can\'t get by using my skills alone, such as someone\'s heart.","The Christmas stocking that Riu knitted by herself has been hung up! Hehe, let\'s teach Santa that not every Christmas stocking in this world can be filled up!","The Christmas stockings sold in the stores are all way too small. I think Chiori deserves to receive all the wonderful gifts in the world.","I get the same gifts every year... It\'s sooooo boring! None of them is as good as your Christmas stocking, Riu.","It can\'t be filled up... How large is this stocking really, nyaa?","You can\'t tell how big it really is from the photo. It\'s big enough that I can fit both my legs into it.","This is the biggest Christmas stocking I\'ve ever seen. You will probably receive lots of gifts.","Riu knitted this for me after all! But since you\'ve worked so hard this year, I\'ll let you choose an extra Christmas gift.","By the way, you don\'t need to thank me because I\'ve heard that too many times. Remember to say something novel when the day comes, hmph.","What a lovely pattern. If I was Santa, I would definitely take this stocking.","Between me and a stocking, you actually chose a stocking? How dare you, peasant! You\'re not getting a Christmas gift this year!!","Hee-hee, it doesn\'t matter even if I don\'t draw a \"great blessing!\" Haruna already knows how to writing it like this. So, what do you think? Great, isn\'t it?\nEveryone should have a \"great blessing\" in such a joyful time, so I\'ll finish making them before the New Year!","People draw lots at the shrine to pray for a good omen in the new year, nothing more. As long as you work hard in the New Year, you\'ll definitely reap good results.","Then the \"great blessings\" I drew will definitely bring good omens too, right?","Theoretically, yes.","A great blessing... Is that good luck or bad luck for Mastema...?","Mastema... should be happy, right? How can he not be happy when he receives a gift?","You\'ll need to ask Mastema after he wakes up. But... I know I will be happy.","I feel that the dignity of the shrine has been severely tested.","Isn\'t it because you\'re all too stingy? Mom said the Mahjong Soul Shrine is a place that brings happiness to people. Shouldn\'t most of the lots say \"great blessing?\" It\'s terrible to draw \"great misfortune!\"","Haruna, you\'re calligraphy is amazing.","I know, right? I practiced writing these two words for a whole day!","I was even writing these words in my dream last night, and I felt like I couldn\'t recognize them anymore. It was terrifying!","I want a \"great blessing\" too!","This one is for you, {0}. Are you moved? Hehe, the Kitty Warriors are already searching for {0}\'s location. Haruna\'s great blessing is ready to deliver!","Finally got some days off, so I invited Nadeshiko to go to the hot spring with me, hehe!\nSenpai looks so beautiful in the yukata, but I\'m keeping her beauty all to myself! I\'m not sharing with you guys!","Actually, I took many photos of Kana, too. Hmm, should I post them for everyone to see? How about the one where you\'re drooling while sleeping on my lap?","No!!! I usually pay great attention to my image, you know? But it\'s not often that I get to hang out and have fun with you, so might have... indulged myself a bit. Please don\'t post that one QAQ","You\'re as gullible as ever. I was just teasing you, hehe.","You\'re the best!","Am I here too early? The first comment somehow isn\'t made by Kana\'s fan club?","Private messages can only be seen by those who are important to Kana!","Haha, it seems I haven\'t taken care of you in vain. I don\'t think I saw the boss\' reply. What a shame. Anyway, I guess it\'s normal for corporate slaves to block their bosses.","Good point.","I want to go to the hot springs too.","Senpai recommended this hidden gem of a place. Since it\'s you, {0}, I\'ll share the address with you. Remember to save it.","Oh, by the way, I just got the tickets to the New Year\'s live show from my manager and have sent one to you. Don\'t be late for my New Year\'s performance, okay? Your seats are so close you can see me winking at you.","The New Year is coming, and so is the time to give back!\nTo thank all my fans for supporting me this year, we\'ll be holding a CatChat lucky draw event. Without further ado, here are the rules.\nDraw Rules:\nFollow Hibiki Himekawa\'s live stream account and repost this message with your New Year\'s wish. 20 lucky fans will be drawn from the live stream, and Hibiki Himekawa will help you make your New Year\'s wishes come true. The lucky fans will also receive a New Year\'s red envelope and a set of photos signed by Hibiki Himekawa.\nEvent Time:\nFrom now until 23:59:59 on December 31, 2022.","This event will be supervised by representatives selected by the Hibiki Fan Club to ensure fairness and confidentiality, so feel free to participate, Hibiki fans!","I\'m willing to have my ex be single for 10 years to get a set signed by Hibiki!","I\'m willing to have my ex be single for 20 years to get a set signed by Hibiki!","I\'m willing to have my ex be single for 30 years to get a set signed by Hibiki!","Move aside, I\'m willing to have my ex be single forever to get a set signed by Hibiki!","I\'m... Hold on, why do all of you have an ex... Damn, then I have no choice but to have the pair I ship now break up tomorrow to get a set signed by Hibiki!","That\'s coooold! You win.","Something bad happened today, and I\'ve been feeling so low all day. Hibiki\'s CatChat event is probably the only good news I\'ve received today... I don\'t know if I\'ll be drawn, but this news alone is already enough to cheer me up.","Now for the second piece of good news.","Oh, this girl... I want to cry...","I hope the fan club can manage the messages to keep strange wishes from being mixed among them. Hibiki must have spent a lot on this luckydraw... The more I think about it, the more worried I am. Gotta send her more donations tonight!","My New Year\'s wish is to see Hibiki act cute in a live stream!","That sound familiar... But I\'ll do it if I draw your message.","Me too! I want to see that too!","My two favorite game streamers are interacting? I\'m so excited!","Can I really wish for anything? Then I won\'t hold back. Smirk.jpg","Anything as long as it\'s legal, except for going easy on you in games.","Haha, I knew it! Nothing is more important than winning in mahjong to Hibiki!","I bet the person above me loves winning too!","There\'s Only One Kana","No. 1 Fan","On the Way to Kana","Deformed by Jealousy","Eat, Sleep, Love Kana","Hibiki Fan Club","Hibiki Number One","Ciri","Kutsuji","Repeat after me loudly: Éternité\'s summer sale is back and better than ever! We have new summer specials! We have gorgeous staff uniforms! We have three lovely young waitresses! Come visit us now!","Pfft! You actually chose this version for the post.","Yes! Because this version is so cute. It\'s definitely not because Catchat messages are difficult to write(?).","The result is pretty good judging from the number of shares and forwards you\'ve got. I\'ve learned something from this...","It\'s great that you can help out, Miss Ninomiya! We\'ll be relying on you this summer.","That\'s right! Come and have a wonderful summer with our youthful and energetic waitresses (me and the two ladies above me)!","I can\'t wait to go already (to see the wonderful waitresses)!","Aha! Now I know exactly what you want to do, {name}. I\'ll be protecting all my staff, hehe!","I get all that, but what\'s with the bold tone all of the sudden...?","Oh, {name}, you noticed. Hehe, actually, this is the handiwork of a new part-time employee. Everyone wants the marketing text to have the energy of summer.","{name}, what do you think about the marketing text?","The first day of business was a great success! If you ignore my messy hair and the mop in my hand, I think this look deserves at least 90 points!","90 points is an injustice to Nana\'s beauty! As the owner, I give you 100 points.","The way how you\'re making the V pose at the camera so confidently... You\'re so dazzling that I feel embarrassed for you...","There\'s nothing to be embarrassed about. You\'re the one who looks a little stiff, Hana.","Smile! I know what I\'ll do. I\'ll take a dazzling photo for you tomorrow too!","Boss, I want to take tomorrow off. You can see this message, right?","Is the hem of the sleeves too wide and causing problems? Please let me know if it needs to be adjusted.","(hug) I haven\'t had any problems yet!","You look so good I thought this was taken just after you opened in the morning! This is amazing! How did you do this?","Hehe! Talent! You\'re jealous, aren\'t you? Start training with me tomorrow, and you\'ll be able to be like me too!","The first day of the promotion is usually the busiest. Good job!","Well, it seems okay to me, but since that\'s what our junior is saying, it feels wrong to not get some benefits while I can. Why don\'t you come and take a group photo for us tomorrow? I mean, we don\'t always wear such cute uniforms!","What I think I look like at work VS What I really look like with no filters.\nI need to try harder.","It was great today! I never realized a member of the gardening club can be so tough. I\'m so amazed.","Yea, I noticed that a lot of people ordered the mulberry special drink today. I almost couldn\'t respond to their orders in time.","I heard the customers all ordered it because it\'s being recommended on the Internet. Um... We\'re going to need to prepare more materials tomorrow.","OMG, how can you enlarge your own photo like that? I mean, I want to see the original HD photo!","My skirt was a little messy in the original... Let me see... Oh, my break is over. I better get back to serving customers. Chat later.","Haha, but the design of this uniform suits you well. You look great.","I just knew you would like this uniform, {name}. It also indirectly explains why so many people were staring at me today. You\'ve got a good eye I can trust, {name}.","O night that hides behind day, I summon thee to be my garment of destiny, so that on weekday afternoons when that deadly force need not be unsealed, ye can guard the order of the world alone and eternally.","?","Reply to all: A cat with \"chunibyo\" accidentally pressed my phone. Please ignore that.","...It sounds like a cat with quite a personality.","Yes, and it has two faces.","Really? I don\'t believe you.","Um... What do you want me to do before you\'ll \"believe\" me, {name}?","In this world where we must keep walking, my sister and I ultimately chose different paths. What will you choose?","The cocktail-style cold-brew special drinks you provided yesterday were really popular, Mr. Shinomiya. You should come over more often when you\'re free.","I\'m glad everyone liked them. Speaking of which, these drinks are all non-alcoholic, so everyone can enjoy them.","I couldn\'t find you anywhere, Shinomiya! So you were at Éternité. I upgraded the last one. You\'ll be satisfied this time!","...Thank you for your hard work. Please contact my manager in the future.","???","Since when did you have a manager?","@{name}","Oh? So you came by the café today?","I came in the afternoon but didn\'t bother you because you were busy. I need to shoot off right now, but I\'ll come back to pick you up when you get off work.","Coffee in the morning and alcohol at night—only children need to make choices.","I didn\'t expect that from you, {name}. It looks like I\'ll need to mix some special flavors tonight so you\'ll really be forced to make a real choice.","I look up at the writer of the post, and I know the answer. I choose 2.","Why do I get the feeling of a conspiracy from this answer? Don\'t worry though, a good man knows when to pretend to be stupid and enjoy the happiness of being chosen.","Who stole my sleep? Oh, I know... It\'s because I didn\'t want to waste anything and drank all the coffee I made to practice latte art.","Ah! I woke up in the middle of the night and looked at the time... Nana, you should sleep in tomorrow morning. You can come in later —I won\'t dock your pay.","Thanks, boss!!! But you don\'t need to worry about me. I can make it!","There\'s only so much caffeine a person can take. Don\'t do this again. Drink some warm milk to relax.","I don\'t have any warm milk at home. Can I have yogurt instead? Speaking of which, why is our junior still awake?","Junior? Are you still there?","Don\'t tell me you fell asleep after replying to my message! Damn... Will I have to 