ter reading someone\'s statement in the comments.","As expected of the owner.","It looks like this year\'s promotion event is quite stressful.","The shop manager said that everyone was a lot more relaxed when our junior here helped out last year. Say, do you think it\'s possible that...","The one I want to drink the most has a buy one get one 50% off deal. Do you understand what I\'m saying? @{name}","It looks great.","But there aren\'t many days left until the promotion ends. When will you return from your trip?","I got it!","See you there then.","I want to get it, but I\'m stuck at the dojo. It feels like this game is especially long and slow...","I\'m shocked! Mahjong is more important to {name} than me...","It\'s onee-sama\'s limited edition. Now onee-sama can gobble up this Ryan rabbit one bite at a time.","It\'s surprisingly good. In that case, Can you provide some coffee to the customers who come to watch our performance?","No! Latte art is like some special magic tricks. Only onee-sama can get it.","I can\'t bear to drink such a cute rabbit.","The rabbit is saying: \"I really want to become a drink that makes onee-sama happy, so please drink me! Later on, the magician Ryan will make more rabbits that onee-sama loves appear.\"","I suddenly feel like watching Ryan\'s magic tricks after drinking this coffee.","Ah, what a greedy adult. But if it\'s you, onee-sama, greed is just another way to express your love. I\'m going to give you a surprising magic trick. Let\'s start counting down ten minutes from now.","Time\'s up! Onee-sama, you can open the doors to welcome your lovely Ryan now.","I have to deal with twice as many takeout delivery orders now because staff A suddenly quit.\nSigh... I\'ve even started to lose hair... Oh well, I might as well focus on working hard for now!","Ah! (Liisa Liisa makes a high-pitched scream) The Furry Conservation Association reminds everyone to love all furry things. Liisa Liisa can\'t accept Ein losing hair!","...I thought you