bout me. I finally understand why Natsuhiko is nowhere to be seen today.","I have a question. What if there\'s a real emergency?","Ask the nearest staff member for help or call me.","Sure, the vice president is synonymous with a sense of security.","Come join the party?","There are still some details to be finalized for the friendly mahjong competition with St. Tina\'s Girls\' School.","But I\'ll do my best.","Where\'s the president? Capture the president and make him work! We can\'t let him get away with this!","??? Things aren\'t as serious as if the law has been broken!!!","Don\'t worry. He\'s working hard right now, and he won\'t be able to go to the amusement park until he\'s done.","It isn\'t necessary to go to the amusement park. When you two are around, the whispers of the devil can be heard throughout the office... Geez, why don\'t I resign already...?","According to the information gathered by the Red Panda Squad, the line Yuzu chose is the slowest. Um... Why is Yuzu always in the slowest line? Could this be the curse of an evil spirit?!","Whenever there are more than three lines, the probability of selecting the fastest one is only 1/3. This probability will continue to decrease as the number of lines increases, so from a probability perspective, it\'s very normal to choose a slower line.","...Hey! That\'s not scientific at all. Since when did you start being this scientific?","Oh, that\'s just a paragraph I randomly copied from the Internet when I was bored while in a line... I didn\'t expect you to believe it, haha.","Hmph! Who said I believed it? I didn\'t believe it. Not even one tiny little bit!","Do you think it\'s possible that Yuzu thinks the line next to her always moves faster and that your name will always be called whenever you skip class are both wrong stereotypes because our brains always remember bad things more deeply than good things?","It\'s the magic of science!","If you put it that way, then the situation of there being a spot check whenever you skip class doesn\'t exist. The reason you kept getting found out whenever you skipped class isn\'t bad luck. It\'s because you skip way too many classes. Isn\'t that right, our student with zero attendance this week?","How did you manage to notice me even when I\'m using my alternate account!!!","There\'s still a long time to go. Yuzu, do you want to go to another attraction instead?","Argh! If I give up now, my efforts in the last hour and a half will be wasted... I can\'t give up now. The witch of justice never gives up easily!","We should have paid for the fast pass... We shouldn\'t have left things to chance.","No, that\'s not the fast pass—that\'s a pass that grants happiness... Argh, another group of happy people are passing us and joyfully arriving at their destination. Can you see them?","Yes, I think they looked even happier when they saw how long our line is...","There are more people at the amusement park today than expected. The children\'s set menu in the amusement park\'s restaurant sold out early too. Luckily, I prepared some rice balls in advance, so all I need to do is find a place to enjoy lunch with the children.","Nyaa! That looks so delicious! I want to have some too, but I\'m still lining up for an attraction, nyaa...","Priestess, are you also here at the amusement park today?","I\'m here with Wanjirou, nyaa!","I was just thinking of taking a break here. If you don\'t mind, you can come here and have some after you finish the attraction you\'re playing.","That\'s great, nyaa! I\'m so hungry that I\'m about to pass out, nyaa.","As expected of Sawako. You\'re always able to arrange things in a thoughtful and orderly manner.","{name}, you\'re also a very considerate person to me.","These rice balls are so cute! Was it a lot of work to make them?","It looks like you like these rice balls, {name}. I\'ll make some for you when we meet again next time.","Whoa! I never knew this fake blood that\'s used as a prop is made from honey!","Honey, nyaa? How does it taste, nyaa?","If the person in charge of running the attraction next door hadn\'t taken her back, maybe you would see a peaceful and serene Bloodless Castle tonight instead...","Ehehe, I didn\'t mean to...","It\'s that delicious? Then I won\'t hold back, nyaa!","Do you even remember that the main mission of this year\'s haunted house is to avoid being captured by the NPCs?","Does Liisa Liisa have anything else that can be eaten?","I have some red mushrooms that have white stalks, but... they don\'t look very edible, hmm.","I can\'t wait to see you in your Halloween costume, Eliisa.","Ehehe, I bet you\'ll jump up and scream in fright when you see me, Mr. Wolf. You have to look for me as soon as possible after the activity starts.","[tag]#CloseYourEyesAtNight[/tag] The hunting grounds are ready. Who will be the first prey to enter the grounds?","Whoa, everything looks super realistic. It\'s a good thing that my night vision is decent, woof.","I knew it. Someone as dense as Wanjirou is oblivious to the horror of a haunted house, nyaa...","I heard that it\'ll become completely dark when the hunters go out to catch the players. Having good eyesight will come in handy at that time, don\'t you think, woof? [tag]@Ein[/tag]","I won\'t give any spoilers even if you\'re the one asking me, Wanjirou. But I\'ll never admit defeat in a battle of night vision. I guess we\'ll find out who\'s better when the time comes.","[tag]@Hana Ninomiya @Kirara Fujimoto @Yuzu[/tag] About the cemetery theme... Maybe we should forget about it? I recall how fast Ein moves when making food deliveries from the café. We won\'t have any chance of escaping alive...","We unanimously vote in favor of that.","Surprisingly, the signal seems especially good here.","But both you and I will need to hand over all our communication devices after the activity starts, so you shouldn\'t even bother to try to call for help, {name}, because I won\'t let you escape.","Can you give me a spoiler and tell me if it really will be very dark?","To a normal person, it should be very dark... but a layer of protection has been applied to the floors, walls, and corners to protect people from injuries. I\'ll take care of you, don\'t worry.","A dark and windy night is when the hundred demons arise! Tonight is when I\'ll get my greatest chance to learn the art of transformation. I\'ll do my best!","...Ransei, you\'re here too?","Yes! Vice president, is there anything you need me to do for you?","I need you to voluntarily hand over all the concealed weapons you\'re carrying during the security check when you enter the amusement park.","It\'s useless to pretend you didn\'t see my message.","Do you think it\'s possible that our classmate Ransei, who never does things conventionally, might not go through the security check at all?","Ransei, why didn\'t you tell me you would be coming today?","Master, I couldn\'t report this to you in time because I only just received this information. Are you also here? Will an event related to secret mahjong techniques be taking place here tonight?","I\'m not the type of person who is always playing mahjong...","I understand! I understand exactly what you\'re saying!","What do you understand? I didn\'t say anything!","At the very least, you should reply to my message before disappearing...","I saw you at the entrance of the haunted house.","What?! Master, how did you notice me?","It\'s because a group of people around me are chatting about a girl at the entrance who is cosplaying as a ninja and looks just like a real ninja...","The process of creating a good article is also very interesting in itself.","Haha, what article is bringing you so much joy?","It\'s an exclusive article on One Han City Amusement Park\'s Halloween haunted house attraction.","No wonder. After finishing off the work at hand, come out and relax over a glass of mulled wine.","You\'re still working overtime? When will you be done? I\'ll come and pick you up when you finish work.","Ahaha... I\'m afraid I\'ll be spending the night here in the office. You should just enjoy your night out at the amusement park. Don\'t worry about me.","You\'re still working overtime? Should I come over and accompany you while you work?","Aren\'t you at the amusement park? Since you have time to look at your mobile phone, I bet you\'re lining up for something right now.","You\'re right. This is the consequence of not buying the fast pass... I\'ll come to you after we finish up here.","Be careful on your way here then.","I want to thank the operators of the amusement park for giving me this reward. The haunted house is so fun, and it would be even better if I could play it again during the day next time... I apologize if I scared any of the staff...","Amazing!!! From now on, I can tell people that I\'m the MVP Hana Ninomiya\'s classmate!","Amazing!!! From now on, I can tell people that I\'m the MVP Hana Ninomiya\'s teacher!","Amazing!!! From now on, I can tell people that I\'m the MVP Hana Ninomiya\'s friend!","Amazing!!! From now on, I can tell people that I\'m the MVP Hana Ninomiya\'s...?","...important person.","Amazing! Can you share your experience of the game?","To put it simply... you need to immerse yourself in it.","I had so much fun tonight! I\'m tired and happy at the same time! However, the thing I remember most deeply is seeing a cosplayer who looked like the vice president! When I saw him, I couldn\'t lift the chainsaw in my hands at all! ...If it wasn\'t for that incident, I would definitely be able to catch more players!","Hahahahahahaha...[tag]@Ren Kisaragi[/tag] So Eliisa didn\'t let you off the hook at that time because she knew you.","Ah! No way! Are you telling me... that person was really the vice president?!","I can personally guarantee that the vice president experienced the haunted house and didn\'t get so scared to the point of making expressions that I took precious photos of to convert into emotes.","That\'s so exciting! Can you share them with me in a private chat?","[tag]@Ren Kisaragi[/tag] Haha! You actually went there in your usual clothes? That\'s such a shame. Is the Sleeping Beauty princess dress I gave you not pretty enough? I remember you really liked princess dresses when you were little.","Since you\'re a teacher, you should know that a child under the age of five doesn\'t have the correct clothing awareness... Don\'t bring this up again.","It\'s not shameful for boys to wear skirts. Ren, you\'re getting less cute as you grow older, sigh...","...I have the feeling I saw something I shouldn\'t see. I can\'t be the only person to bear this burden.[tag]@Kirara Fujimoto @Ling @Hana Ninomiya @Kana Fujita @Natsuhiko Takigawa @Ransei @Yuzu @{name}[/tag]","Hehe, I just received the shocked expression emotes from the president.","Good sisters should share all images they receive. By the way, why have you only been using your alternate account today?","My mobile phone that has my main account has been confiscated by my manager. I\'m sure you understand QAQ.","The comments section is so exciting.","...Mr. Wolf, I\'m not brave enough to reply to any of the messages now. You\'re so much braver than me after all QAQ.","What happened? I just woke up.","Yes, that\'s right. Liisa Liisa and Mr. Wolf just got up. We don\'t know what happened at all!","Mr. Wolf is so smart. Now we won\'t be implicated.","Other than the fact that some players couldn\'t tell the difference between a fallen angel and a vampire, I guess you can say that I had a good time tonight.","This problem wouldn\'t exist if I didn\'t make the wings smaller.","You can\'t blame yourself for other people\'s mistakes! The improvement you made for the escape feature of the attraction is praiseworthy.","Haha, whether you\'re a vampire or a fallen angel, you\'re still cute either way, Chiori!","Since you said that, manager, I\'ll forgive those people... but only by a little bit.","How can people mistake you for something else when you\'re obviously a vampire! That\'s unacceptable!","???","[tag]System notification: The user only allows friends to comment on their CatChat.[/tag]","You\'re so beautiful tonight, Chiori. You\'re the most beautiful angel to me.","Hmph...! I\'m only beautiful tonight? I\'ll give you a chance to reflect on your mistake!","Remember to THINK CAREFULLY about what you should be saying to me!","The aura of revelry and desire still fills the streets this morning. It\'s so pleasant to live in a free city without restraints where you don\'t need an excuse to enjoy yourself. However, the events of last night seem to be just a prelude to things to come.","God, may Sister Kitahara\'s will guide me, just like how your will guides me.","God, I follow your will and am willing to remember the true love and desire that should be remembered.","God, may I follow your will with a pious heart and be loyal to your incarnation.","God, I wish to be your most loyal believer for all eternity, just like Sister Kitahara.","What did you do yesterday, Lily?","While you were having fun in the amusement park, {name}, I also played some happy games with the children. That\'s all though.","By the way, you\'ll be coming to the church today, right?","Can I spend some time with you today, Lily?","At the church? At the West Wind dojo? Or... do you want to go to another place? All of those options are okay. I\'ll fulfill all your wishes, haha.","I went to the amusement park with Hinata yesterday. By the way, the special effects of haunted houses are so amazing now! I feel like I\'ve got a lot of inspiration for new inventions!","The aura of an evil spirit seems to be trapped in this photo... Was a powerful magical circle with sealing powers used?","Hmm? Sorry, I don\'t understand what you\'re saying. If you\'re talking about the photo, I just used an ordinary photo-editing software to alter the skin color and strange background, and then I applied a filter to it.","Huh? Isn\'t this the photo you took with that strange thing in it?","After spending a lot of time going through the photos, I still thought this one looked the best, so I just removed that thing. What do you think? You can\'t see it at all, right?","Using scientific means to solve supernatural events is such a futuristic thing!","Let\'s make an automatic photo-editing software. The instant beautification features that are on the market right now aren\'t that useful.","No way! That takes the fun out of photo editing! I won\'t let that happen!","What do you want to do? Can you tell me anything specific?","After considering the funds we have, I\'m thinking of developing contact lenses that give people night vision. After all, not all the NPCs have powerful night vision, and their performance is greatly affected by dark environments.","So this is the terrifying stamina of a woman who can carry Bex everywhere with her. You actually think the NPCs aren\'t chasing hard enough...","...I missed the Halloween event.","Did the sun rise from the west today? Ling is actually expressing interest in Halloween activities?!","Ling, will you consider joining the pastry club? One important activity of the pastry club is the research of festive foods. You\'ll never miss a festive event again after you join the club.","Wow! As expected of our scheming president. He has such devious ways to promote clubs to students!","What a refreshing compliment. It seems that we\'ll need to arrange for Eliisa to attend extra language classes in addition to mathematics classes.","The Halloween haunted house attraction will be ending soon, but the Halloween themed decorations won\'t be removed until three days later. Ling, do you still want to go to the amusement park?","I read the comments and think you\'ve all misunderstood something... What I mean is that I missed the Halloween discount event for the gaming platform.","Do you want to go to the amusement park? If you do... let\'s meet at the entrance of the amusement park in a moment.","What have you been up to recently? It\'s been a few days since I\'ve seen you.","All kinds of bugs have been appearing with the festival, and I\'ve been working on them for days now.","Doesn\'t that mean you\'ve missed out on this Halloween then?!","If you\'re willing to go on a date with me now, then I won\'t have missed out. I can treat today as Halloween.","Warning: Since the Halloween haunted house virus hasn\'t been fully removed, KR-976 is prone to lagging in night mode. It is currently protected by a quilt.","So the secret technique \"haunted creature stay away from the person in bed\" is a ninjutsu that eveLingne knows?!","Translating the above question into something processable.","Answer: Yes, KR-976 has been equipped with this protective program before leaving the factory.","Give me one too. The chase just now was too exciting, and I\'m in urgent need of a protective shield.","Answer: After calculation, the protective shield can provide just enough protection for KR-976 and its companion {name}. Please enter the protective range of the shield in time.","Did you actually go to the haunted house by yourself this time? Anju, you\'re getting braver and braver!","Answer: KR-976 wants to become a perfect artificial intelligence that can protect {name} in the haunted house.","Answer: KR-976 wants to perform... better when faced with the same problem as last time.","Okay, Anju, you\'ve worked hard and done a great job. Shall we play together next time?","Answer: Okay.","[tag]#HalloweenIdolAdventure[/tag] Kana\'s Halloween trip will be released later! This year, Kana secretly went to [tag]@One Han City Amusement Park[/tag] to experience the haunted house. I even participated in the Float Parade of One Hundred Demons. Can you guess... which tile I\'ll play this time?","Oh my! I knew that Kana would never do things conventionally. I\'m firmly caught in Kana\'s grasp.","My wife... Where did my wife Kana go?!","Noooo! Not mahjong again. Kana-chan, you really love mahjong recently! You actually celebrated Halloween by playing mahjong!","Kana-chan will play the red Dora of course!","Wow, really? That makes so much sense to me!","Since Kana is the top idol, of course she\'ll play a 1 Pin!","Kana-fans, I\'ve received all of your expectations for me!","Kana-fans... Kana\'s reply is so official and polite today. Could this be her manager instead?","No way, I really am Kana.","Ahem.","Ananke","Lin Lang","Best Fullback","Liberated Libero","The Trophy is Beckoning","No Buttering","Go Practice","Say Good Morning to Me","Prince of Salted Fish","Ordinary Salaryman","Levine","Xi Xi","Kai","I only realized that it\'s almost Christmas when I heard a familiar song playing on the radio. No wonder the children have been pestering me to tell them bedtime stories about Santa recently. Just then, one of them asked me a very important question. Now that we no longer have a chimney, how will Santa come in to deliver our presents?","Now that you mention it, I don\'t think Santa has ever come to the Mahjong Soul Shrine. Is it because we don\'t have a chimney, nyaa?","Haha, the priestess is still a child after all.","Argh... I really wanted to say that Santa can use magic, but it\'s not right to tell lies. A stumbling block has appeared on the road to justice...!","You know what? Maybe it\'s another form of justice to tell a white lie, hehe.","Argh! So that\'s possible too...","In that case, I don\'t need to feel bad about skipping today\'s classes. After all, I just maintained the peace of One Han City! I was telling a white lie when I requested a day off school due to sickness... Um.","Santa can knock on the door.","Oh! I can\'t believe I actually forgot this most normal way of turning up. {name}, thanks for reminding me.","Burst their bubble, of course, and tell them that Santa doesn\'t really exist!","Argh, {name}, I never expected that you would have such a mischievous idea... Children\'s dreams are just as important as our pursuit of Yakuman.","I heard that Christmas is known as another Valentine\'s Day in some places. In that case, the gift selection is especially important!","Whoa! The food in that image looks so delicious! Fuyumi, you\'re not only a talented fashion designer, but also an amazing cook.","Hehe.","Although it\'s been a while since I\'ve delivered food at the café, the hair on my tail stood up when I saw these images. I could even hear the notifications received when people placed orders...","Haha! You\'ve been working so hard, Mr. Ein. Has the hair on your tail grown back? This is very important!","Why is it known as another Valentine\'s Day?","Haha, it\'s because all the couples are out on dates on this day. The streets are filled with a lovey-dovey atmosphere. Hehe, {name}, I bet there\'s someone you would like to go out on a date with on this day, right?","Fuyumi, do I have the honor of inviting you to celebrate Christmas with me?","Wow! Are you inviting me to go on a date with you? You are, right? Hehe.","I took a short nap and woke up to find everyone wrapping apples together in the student council\'s office. I hear that they will be given out as gifts on Christmas Eve. I thought I might as well try wrapping one too. What do you think?","It\'s great. I\'ve got ten boxes of apples here. Are you interested in wrapping them up too?","There\'s absolutely no way I\'ll wrap any more of them for you. I only need to experience something this boring once!","Miss Kisaragi, instead of taking a short nap, it\'s more accurate to say you were in a deep sleep for two and a half hours.","Two and a half hours is just enough to play two Hanchan. If you look at it like that, it really is just a short time.","I\'m starting to understand everything.","It\'s beautiful! I give it five stars!","In that case, you can have it tonight. Don\'t say no to me.","The bow looks a little loose.","{name}, you\'re so strict. Will you also critique my appearance so strictly when we go on a date next time?","I accidentally broke the wrapping of a gift I\'m about to give to someone. What should I do?! This is an emergency. Save me!","Has this already escalated into an emergency?","I put a lot of thought into preparing this Christmas present. Stop making sarcastic remarks already and help me think of a solution.","Seeing this has reminded me that I still haven\'t prepared a Christmas present for my little sister. Thanks for reminding me, captain.","That\'s not why I posted this on CatChat!","Hahahahahaha!","Hahahahahahahahahahaha!","Hahahahahahahahahahaha!","Hahahahahahahahahahaha!","Et tu, Coach...? Won\'t anyone consider my feelings?","Maybe you can fix it with some glue.","Ninomiya is as reliable as ever. I\'ll try that now.","Did I make a mistake? The wrapping paper looks more torn than ever...","How bad is it? Show us a picture!","The wrapping is damaged so badly... that you\'ll find out what my gift is if I send a picture. You won\'t be surprised when you get it then.","Why don\'t you tear off the wrapping completely? Maybe the person you\'re giving it to doesn\'t care whether it\'s wrapped or not.","Really? You won\'t mind receiving an unwrapped Christmas present?","Soul\'s Special Christmas Eve Project—\nNew song and dance performances, mysterious magic tricks, and a Christmas costume party! Come and join us tonight!","First comment!","Can\'t believe I\'m the first one to comment! Damn, why aren\'t I this lucky when I\'m trying to get tickets for the show!","Mojito seems really interested in costume parties recently. Why don\'t we dress Mojito up in a costume with a headpiece?","It\'s a good idea, but don\'t even think of doing this next time.","What a shame that I\'m uneducated and can only scream wherever I go. What I mean is, let\'s do more activities like this!","See you there!","Haha, in that case, let\'s see if we can find each other in the crowd that night and be each other\'s dance partner.","I only just realized, Sara, your CatChat seems to only have posts about Soul.","Are you trying to imply that I should share more things from my daily life? Haha, I understand now.","The prizes for this year\'s year-end party are ready. They were voted on and decided internally by the company. We\'ll see you all at the party.","Boss, you\'re a legend!","Oh my god! Why am I always recording a show on the other side of the world whenever the company gives out benefits?!","{name} can draw your prize for you.","Boss, you\'re a legend!","Boss, you\'re a legend!","I can\'t believe it! I, Kana, an 8G surfer of the Internet, actually replied after Akane! Impossible! But... you\'re a legend, boss!","Boss, you\'re the best! Wait, do I get a gift too?","What do you think? I don\'t think I\'ve forgotten your gift in past years.","What activities will we be doing at the year-end party?","A mahjong competition. The final winner will get a grand prize. Well, are you interested?","Do the people in wonderland celebrate Christmas? Will Santa also give them gifts?\nHmm... I couldn\'t fall asleep because I kept thinking about this. In the end, I found out that mom was about to sneak into my room and leave a Christmas present. Would it be better if I pretend that I\'m still sleeping?","What? Momo Hina, your gift is from your mother? Shouldn\'t it be from Santa?","Maybe I\'m getting one from mom because Santa hasn\'t arrived yet... I\'ll find out tomorrow.","According to my experience, you should pretend to be sleeping.","Oh? What experience are you referring to?","Come on! I want to know the answer too.","When I was only a little older than you are now, I suddenly sat up when my teacher came to give me a gift in the middle of the night and gave him a fright.","Although he didn\'t tell me off, I never received a Christmas present again from the next year onwards.","Oh my, that sounds like a really painful experience.","I raise my hand in support. I also prepared a gift for Momo Hina.","I\'ve also prepared a gift for Mr. Rabbit. We can exchange them at Mr. Mad Hatter\'s tea party.","Let me see when this was posted... Children who stay up late at night will be captured by the Red Queen\'s guards.","I\'ll never stay up late again. Mr. Rabbit, please don\'t tell people about this.","The Christmas dinner party will have sumptuous food this year thanks to Mai, nyaa!\nThere\'s a Christmas chocolate cake, French crème brûlée, vegetable and bacon pizza, mushroom and potato soup... They\'re all my favorite foods! But can someone tell me why there\'s an apple in the roasted suckling pig\'s mouth, nyaa?","The mouth of the suckling pig will be wide open because I use a special steel fork during the roasting process. So I put an apple in it for aesthetic purposes...","Nyaa?! That\'s why? Not because you want the roast suckling pig to have the aroma of an apple, nyaa?!","Oh? I never expected that you would be celebrating Christmas here at the Mahjong Soul Shrine and that you would even prepare such a grand dinner. However, a Christmas dinner party is incomplete without a roast turkey.","Nyaa, hehe! Actually, Mai is already preparing a turkey soup, nyaa.","A turkey... soup?! Angry.jpg","Nyaa?","Hahaha! For a noble young lady, turkey soup is just like a pineapple and mango pizza, taro and salmon maki sushi, or strawberry mapo tofu... It\'s an absolutely unacceptable act of heresy.","Those foods sound quite delicious, nyaa.","In the future, let\'s not eat Miki\'s cooking so often. It\'s not good for our taste buds, woof.","Hehe, the Mahjong Soul Shrine is looking really lively today. I just happen to have made some snacks today. I\'ll come over to the shrine a little later to share them with you so you can have them for dessert.","No! That won\'t be necessary, nyaa!","Uncontrollable drool is flowing from the corner of my mouth. I\'ll definitely buy a mobile phone that can view images in the future!","Nyaa? Nyaa, nyaa, nyaa?! What happened to my picture, nyaa?!","It would be great if I can have a feast like this every day!","That\'s what I think too, nyaa! I want to have a big feast every day with you, Master, nyaa!","[tag]#Annual Christmas Lantern Show! One Han City Never Sleeps!#[/tag]\nThe organizer said that I can get a 10% discount on the ticket price if I get 30 Likes. Please help me!\nDon\'t miss out on this winter\'s Christmas lantern show! Why are you hesitating? Bring your family and friends and have some fun together!","As one of the partners of this lantern show event, Éternité will be providing visitors with delicious hot chocolates. Fuyumi, you should be able to see the sign of our café\'s stall if you walk down the first street. I\'ve already sent a message about you being at the lantern show to my uncle.","Wow! Does that mean I\'ll be able to drink a hot chocolate personally made by the owner? That\'s amazing!","Oh! My right hand is out of control! Argh, listen to me and press that \"Like\" button!","Brother, you, mom, and dad will also need to post on CatChat to get Likes. Don\'t stand there like this has nothing to do with you.","When Fuyumi posts something, I always give it a Like first before reading it.","With the Like from you, {name}, I have all 30 Likes I need. You really are my superhero! You\'re always there to help me when I need help!","The youth of today are always posting pretty event images to request Likes. What happened to ethics? Where is their dignity? Where is the address?","The Jyanshi of today are always asking a series of questions to hide their true purpose for joining the event. What happened to ethics? Where is their dignity? The address has been sent to you in a private message!","I\'ve bought the tickets.","It\'s rare for Yui to actively participate in an event like this. Well... the power of a certain emotion that can only be understood but not expressed in words sure is powerful.","Mirai, you can come with us too.","Haha, I like wheels, but I don\'t like being a third wheel.","I\'ll only be returning from my family home on the day after tomorrow. Will the lantern show already be over?","The event will run until New Year\'s Day.","I\'m falling deep in thought while looking at the ticket I just bought for tomorrow...","Don\'t worry, I can go with you twice, senpai.","I\'ve already bought snacks and drinks. Let\'s go!","I\'ll be waiting for you at the ticket office, senpai.","It\'s been so hard to schedule this afternoon tea date, and we even missed Christmas. Fortunately, there weren\'t many people here in the restaurant today, so the service was more attentive than usual. I had a wonderful afternoon with [tag]@{name}[/tag], and it was a perfect date.","[tag]@Chihori Terasaki[/tag] I win!","Ah... Why do I feel like I\'m watching my daughter getting married after growing up?","Huh?","Chihori and I had made a bet on whether the dress you chose earlier is for today\'s date.","Shush! Don\'t talk about that in the comments.","Haha, it doesn\'t matter. I bet {name} likes how you\'re dressed today.","The weather forecast says that it\'ll be -10°C today, hehe.","I wonder which cute hot girl told me in the school infirmary yesterday that it\'s necessary to dress as beautifully as possible regardless of how cold it is when going on a date with the person she likes? I can\'t seem to remember her name right now.","My only regret is that I was late. Damn, I even made sure to set out one hour in advance.","I don\'t think it\'s a pity. The wait sometimes makes the encounter more exciting.","That\'s not accurate. Every second spent together with Ayane is a wonderful time.","Low EQ: We had a wonderful afternoon together. High EQ: Every second we spent together was a wonderful time.","??? You really are my sister!!!","When I went out, the convenience store downstairs was closed, and the store manager was busy instructing the employees to take anti-freeze measures for the equipment. Although everything is also white in One Han City on a snowy day, the snow is still much lighter here than in the Northland.","It\'s been a while, Eve.","Lily...","While 