se you didn\'t build a snowman with me!","I\'ve made up my mind, nyaa. I\'m going to write a book called \"100 Ways to Make My Master Buy Large Snack Giftpacks for Ichihime\"!","Are you sure {name} won\'t block you after seeing it, woof?","Nyaa! That\'s impossible, nyaa! Master loves me the most in the whole wide world, nyaa!","Large snack giftpacks!","What do you think? Are you excited about my new book, nyaa?","I want to preorder it! I want {name} to buy twice as many large snack giftpacks for me!","You\'ll get fat if you eat too many snacks. I\'m sure you don\'t need me to remind you about what usually happens to orange cats.","Nyaa! Beautiful girls can never get fat, nyaa. I only gained 5 kg this month, nyaa.","You\'ve even started to teach others how to trick me. I feel bad for my poor thin wallet...","Just dote on her.jpg","But she calls me master.jpg","Master! Master! You\'re my favorite, master, nyaa. When you buy me snacks, Master, you\'re the wisest and most heroic person in the world, nyaa!","Miki said that those who see the first sunrise of the new year will be lucky throughout the coming year, nyaa, so I\'ve specially prepared a mahjong table this year. Nyaa, nyaa. We\'ll battle intensely throughout the night and then watch the sunrise when it\'s time. I\'m such a genius for coming up with this idea, nyaa!","I still think it\'s more reliable to pray directly to the Mahjong Soul Shrine, woof.","You asked for this, shorty. Don\'t go crying to {name} after you lose, hehehe.","Hey, that\'s my line. Don\'t complain to Master after you lose, nyaa!","Well... in that case, please take care of me tonight. For the sake of everyone\'s good luck in the new year, I\'ll also try my best to play mahjong passionately!","I won\'t go easy on you, nyaa.","Can I join you for the New Year\'s Eve game? How\'s it going so far?","I order you to come to the Mahjong Soul Shrine immediately to take the shorty\'s place. She fell asleep while playing.","So did Ichihime\'s New Year\'s Eve challenge succeed this year?","No, woof. She fell asleep while listening to the fireworks.","Happy New Year! This year\'s blessing is on time as usual.","Wow! This New Year\'s greeting card is so beautiful. I bet a certain someone gave it to you.","Haha, yes, I did get it from that person. Takanashi, someone told me that your greeting card comes with some pressed dried flowers and is really beautiful.","Haha, don\'t worry! I made lots, and there\'s plenty to go around, so there\'s naturally one for you, president.","Happy New Year, president! Let\'s meet again at school after the vacation!","Yes, Happy New Year!","Happy New Year!","Happy New Year! I still haven\'t congratulated you on finishing in second place in the FEI World Equestrian Games.","Hey, you don\'t have to emphasize the ranking!","Happy New Year!","Happy New Year, Yagi!","Argh!!! The morning is over, and I\'ve yet to send even one greeting card!","Oh, do you need any help?","I\'m currently inspecting the research society\'s automatic delivery machine to find out why it brought back all the greeting cards without delivering them after it left with them.","How\'s the inspection going? Is there something wrong with the machine?","I was about to take it apart when I saw a label on the back marking it as defective! Why on earth would my senpai put a defective product in the front row of the shelf?","New Year\'s greeting cards are just used to exchange greetings. As long as you convey your blessings accurately, it doesn\'t matter whether people receive the card itself.","President, you\'re still so good at comforting people, haha. I wish my senpai in the research society could learn to be more like you. Anyway, Happy New Year!","Hideki, Happy New Year! My father won\'t let me rush you, but everything he\'s cooked is already on the table, and even the chopsticks have been set. Come downstairs and eat with us.","I\'m sorry for making Mr. Ayame and you wait. I\'ll be right there.","Happy New Year!","Haha, Happy New Year! {name}, I wish you great health in the New Year! May all your wishes come true, and may everything go your way.","A certain person is feeling really relieved at the moment because their blessings have been delivered in time.","Haha, in that case, I wonder if a certain someone has received my gift yet? I prepared that with all my heart.","Happy New Year! Congratulations! During the holiday, all customers of Luck and Fortune will get a 20% discount on games played. We wish all our customers every success, smooth sailing, good luck, peace, serendipity, good fortune, and perfection in all your endeavors. May everything go your way!","I just saw an ad with exactly the same content, except the name of the mahjong dojo is different. Did you just copy and paste the contents, woof?","Don\'t focus on the details. Isn\'t the 20% discount good enough to shut you up?","Fu Ji, Happy New Year!","Happy New Year. By the way, when will you pick up that lost three-legged bird? She is a little confused and has been freeloading here for several days already.","So Jin Wu is with you, Fu Ji. I apologize for the trouble she must have given you these last few days. I\'ll come over to pick her up in a moment.","A 20% discount on games played. That\'s the same as last year, and it isn\'t competitive enough. What other benefits are there?","You\'re not happy with a 20% discount? We can hear the sound of you making calculations all the way here in Luck and Fortune.","I highly suspect that you\'re trying to brainwash me, but I don\'t have any evidence yet.","But it\'s not like I can\'t consider your suggestion if you spend enough today.","You call it a blessing when it\'s really an ad. The schemes of Fu Ji are some of the most complicated ones I\'ve seen.","That\'s not very fair to me. I sincerely wish our guests the best. If you don\'t believe me, come to the dojo and let me give you our blessings in person. I guarantee that nothing will be said incorrectly.","I went to visit 