u while you focus on finishing the assignment.","Wow! {name}, you really are the most reliable person ever!","Holiday syndrome is kicking in on my first day back at work.","I find this difficult to believe. You\'re already back to work today?","What? Today\'s only your first day back at work?","I was doing interviews on New Year\'s Day, writing articles on the second day, and printing on the third day... I\'m starting to wonder if I really did go on holiday.","It\'s not very civilized to work overtime during the holidays. Leave your evil boss as soon as possible.","Sigh, where can you find a boss who isn\'t evil nowadays?","Hmm, so there are things that even you find troublesome, senpai.","Haha, you think I\'m far more omnipotent than I really am, Kana.","Life is short, but work takes forever... I really empathize with you.","Let\'s do something interesting after work today. I\'ll pick you up in the evening.","[tag]#forwarded CatChat: [What\'s the correct thing to do when you have holiday syndrome?]#[/tag]","I thought that was my dad sending me a message. You\'re more... widely read than I expected.","I wish you all the best in the New Year and hope that everything goes your way in the festive season.","I\'ve been using the pestle and mortar all morning. This is as physically draining as a soccer match.","Haha, thanks for your hard work. Next time, I\'ll remember to get a few other members of the soccer club to come help out.","There\'s going to be another time?","Argh! This is such a serious conversation. President, have you been possessed by something strange?","???","Yesterday\'s bribe was very delicious. Liisa Liisa will keep that thing secret for you!","Shush—","That\'s all?","???","Sure enough, people respond seriously to serious messages on social media... Hey, I prefer it when your replies fill up my comments section.","Here are some New Year\'s greetings for your reference: In the new year, I wish you endless joy and happiness. May your dreams illuminate your way forward, and may everything go well in your career! I wish you a happy New Year, good health, and happiness for you and your family! May your life get better and may your smile become brighter! The New Year is upon us, may you...","Seriously, I\'m crying really hard here. You didn\'t even delete that sentence about the paragraph being a reference when you copied and pasted it.","I\'ve checked the time. Today isn\'t any festival, is it?","You\'re right, but instead of admitting that I made a mistake when pre-setting the post time, why don\'t we celebrate a new holiday today? It\'s okay even if we\'re the only ones celebrating it.","If the Witch of Justice inadvertently does something wrong, please let the almighty God of Justice directly punish me with magic instead of a toothache...","I heard that you can still eat food that falls on the ground if you pick it up within three seconds, nyaa...","S-Still eat it? Argh, I don\'t recommend doing that.","Yuzu, do you need to go to the hospital? I\'ll help you submit a request to take the day off to the teacher and the vice president.","Argh... It won\'t be necessary to go to the hospital. It\'s not that serious...","Gargling with warm salt water is an effective way to relieve toothache pain.","I just tried that. I guess it\'s effective.","Argh, the Witch of Justice repays her debts of gratitude and resentment. Thanks a lot.","Haha, I\'m just worried that the little red panda who is suffering from illness won\'t put on a good show when resisting. Anyway, get better soon, or else Teacher will keep saying that I\'m bullying others who are weaker than me.","Argh... I\'m so angry that my teeth are starting to hurt again after just feeling better!!! I knew it! Big-breasted women who have bunny ears are all evil. I\'ll definitely punish you and dish out justice, argh!!!","This is strange. I remember that I put away all the rice cakes because I was worried Yuzu would eat too many of them.","Argh... I was thinking of giving 