g things? Hmm... I\'m shivering in this freezing temperature even though I\'m wrapped up tightly in my coat with Shaun.","Although the essence of hunting training is overcoming difficulties, this sub-zero temperature is really unfriendly to those who need to work part-time.","Ein, do you need a pair of gloves? Shaun lost enough fur to knit several pairs of gloves this year.","Lost enough fur... This cold winter feels even colder after hearing that.","I don\'t think you\'re imagining things...","Ninomiya, how\'s your cold? Are you feeling better? Liisa Liisa is worried about you.","My fever has subsided, but I\'ll stay at home for a while before I go back to school so I won\'t infect the other students.","It really is cold. I\'m shivering so much.","It must really be cold if even Mr. Wolf is feeling cold. Liisa Liisa\'s new coat is really big. I think you\'ll fit under it too, Mr. Wolf.","Is it cold? I think it\'s just right.","Mmm, the teacher was right. The feeling of being cold or warm really isn\'t the same for all people. But Mr. Wolf\'s embrace must be very warm. I want to hug you to keep warm. Is that okay?","Ta-da! I dug out a small backpack I bought three years ago from my closet and was surprised to find that it\'s still trendy. I saved a lot of money, so I can buy some new head accessories now.","This bag... I think I bought one too when it was trendy three years ago, but I haven\'t seen it ever again after I took it home.","You can never find something when you\'re looking for it specifically. And when you give up, that thing will suddenly appear where you least expect it. You can try this method.","Hmm... let me rephrase that. You\'re telling me to forget about it if I can\'t find it.","Senpai, did yesterday\'s photo shoot go well?","It went very smoothly. Please contact me as soon as possible if you have another easy and high-paying job with such a good-tempered photographer.","Everyone except me is paying attention to your backpack. What I\'m paying at