d merch?! H-how did you manage to get that...","Haha! This channel is always so hyped!","Oh my grandpa, what did I just see?","The stupid rabbit always says I\'m a scrooge, let me prove her wrong, nyaa!","All Simples is Justice, nyaa!","Calm down, why are the young ones always so hot-headed, woof...","Friendly sponsor for the table, woof.","Hehehe, nice show!","This is the reward for entertaining me, receive it with gratitude.","I learned that!","Cheers, Hibiki! Don\'t lose to those bad-mouthers!","Thanks for the good laugh","I\'m touched, really...","Take this, my worthy rival!","I admit defeat to your grind!","Bravo！","CoooooooooooooooooL","LiisaLiisa","I Call All Simples","Ordinary Salaryman","A Wind of Red","KR-976net","WitchOfJustice","Hibiki For Life","Colourful Darkness","Kiwi Reader","CafeLatte","Hibiki\'s Table","Deep Hate Deep Love","Gimme Oranges","This Nickname is Unavailable","WarOfMaid","Guest (Really)","Friends Keep Promises","One Han Night Walker","Jade Room Philanthropist","Deal-In is Unavoidable","Attention! Attention!","That\'s too easy, my granny could win.","I don\'t understand","XD XD XD","Don\'t panic, it\'s just a technical adjustment","How flashy! My eyes!","Have you ordered the table for this month already, hehehe?","Leaving satisfied","Tile gains work in mysterious ways","Don\'t, don\'t do THAT!!!","Thinking will only slow down your path to deal-in","No choice but go for it","?","???!","Nice move!","Damn, she pulled it off","Humans who don\'t have dreams are just sardines.","How greedy","She\'s so gentle, I\'m tearing up","How ordinary","One must face reality","Is this POV for real?","Still unyielding, huh","BIG CRISIS","INCOMING","Awed","So this is the confidence of the strong","The tile dealer: gimme money","Stop scolding","Scold her more!","A hero never chickens out!","Hibiki, my superwoman","Continue speaking, I\'m noting everything down","I was too shallow","Sorry for the interruption","Investigate the left player","Continue next time, tomorrow will be a better day","Who gave you the courage?","She\'s like a war goddess","Don\'t take the haters seriously","Wanjirou","Ramen Stall Marketing Strategy","Wanjirou wants to open a ramen stall and doesn\'t know what price to set. He values your opinion as his partner.","Price low for high volume sales","Wanjirou put up a banner at the stall with the words \"Make ramen cheap again\" written on it. Although many bowls of ramen were sold in the end, they were priced too cheaply to recover the original investment...","As Wanjirou\'s ramen was delicious and cheap, people lined up all the way from the stall to the gates of Asaha High School. The student council even had to arrange for more people to maintain order. In the end, Wanjirou made a lot of money.","Sell premium ramen at a premium price","The diners wondered why it was necessary to garnish a perfectly fine bowl of ramen with some strange-smelling herbs, making it disgusting and expensive. As a result, they started telling everyone to avoid this ramen stall.","Each bowl of ramen was garnished with two cute cat paws. Upon taking a bite, the diners realized that these cat paws were mangosteens! The sweetness and deliciousness of fresh mangosteens gave the ramen a unique taste, instantly making the ramen stall famous and filling it with diners.","Riu Kujou","Café Marketing Strategy","Riu Kujou wants to open a café during the festival, but the competition among food stores is fierce. What theme could be used as the core selling point of the café to attract customers?","Cat Café","The idea of playing with cats while enjoying coffee is too comfortable, and Riu Kujou strongly agrees with your suggestion. Everything is ready, but where can we find the cats? You couldn\'t help but turn to Ichihime, but this cat-eared guest firmly claimed to be human and declined your request.","Riu Kujou temporarily borrowed some very happy-to-serve cats from Éternité. They are very friendly, allowing people to touch and hold them freely, and even cling to customers demanding to perform tricks. The cat café quickly attracted a large number of loyal cat worshipers, becoming immensely popular and generating astonishing revenue.","Maid Café","The maid staff were so cute that customers coming in for photos soon caused congestion inside the café, making meal delivery extremely difficult. Riu Kujou sighed and started to consider the feasibility of diverting customers to other food stores.","So this is the coffee handcrafted by specially trained high-level professional maids! The rich aroma, mellow taste, and lingering aftertaste all attest to the top-notch quality of this maid café. Its reputation skyrocketed, and sales grew exponentially.","Miki Nikaidou","Food Sharing Gathering","Distressed that no one was interested in the food she put so much effort into making, Miki Nikaidou decided to hold a food sharing gathering at the festival and invite everyone to taste her creations. She wants to ask your opinion on what she should make for the food party.","Nikaidou\'s secret dish","Miki Nikaidou made the cherry tomato and strawberry mapo tofu that she has always been proud of. She believed that the tartness of the cherry tomatoes and the sweetness of the strawberries would perfectly offset the spiciness of mapo tofu. However, after the tasting session, a lot of complaints were received... They complained that the world started spinning after they tasted this dish and that the school infirmary was now overcrowded. Miki Nikaidou also received a note criticizing her bad cooking skills, saying: \"Spiciness is not a taste but a pain signal!!!\"","Miki Nikaidou made the chocolate squid ink roasted eggplant that she had painstakingly developed over a few days. She believed that eating black-colored foods would improve hair quality, slow down aging, and enhance mahjong luck. To her surprise, this \"delicacy\" caused a craze. Her plan was a great success, even though she probably owed her success to people\'s curiosity and their desire to take revenge against others...","Normal home cooking","Miki Nikaidou decided to make a classic dish that would be least likely to go wrong: egg fried rice. However, for some reason, the egg fried rice she made was shrouded in a dark aura, and none of the people who came to her stall had the courage to try it. The entire day passed without any sharing of food at the stall.","Miki Nikaidou made a curry chicken rice bowl. Although she kept telling everyone that she bought the curry chicken from the supermarket and had only heated it up, no one was interested in trying it. Eventually, by chance, a group of delinquents sneaked inside the school and came to the stall. When they saw the free food, they started gobbling it up without saying anything... \"Th-The food has been poisoned!\" These were their last words before they were taken to the hospital.","Siesta Party","Ayane Kisaragi, who is forced to work overtime at the school during the festival, decides to organize a siesta party for the benefit of all workers who want to enjoy paid naptimes, and she wants to ask your advice on how she can put the partygoers to sleep.","Perform ASMR for them","Listeners heard the sound of Ayane Kisaragi saying \"go to sleep, go to sleep...\" in a soft and melodious tone of voice. They didn\'t hear anything else after that. An observant person discovered that she had already put herself to sleep.","Unexpectedly, Ayane Kisaragi was very talented in ASMR and gave listeners an audio experience of the sounds of a pillow being kneaded, liquid being squeezed inside a syringe, and her own heartbeat amplified with a stethoscope... The listeners all felt at peace, like they were being embraced by their mothers, and slept soundly, filling the venue with snoring sounds.","Play a recording of one of Ren Kisaragi\'s meetings","Unexpectedly, this recording was of a monthly problem children criticism meeting, so everyone listened with interest as Ren Kisaragi elaborated on the most recent mistakes made by the most famous problem children of the school and how many subjects they had failed. Everyone started clamoring for more recordings like this and enjoyed listening to it, so no one fell asleep.","\"I\'ll go over three points briefly...\" Something about this sentence seemed to trigger something in the DNA of the listeners, and they fell asleep on the nap mats that had been prepared in advance by force of habit. Everyone slept soundly, filling the venue with snoring sounds.","Yuzu","The Punishment of Justice","Yuzu, the Witch of Justice, has volunteered to maintain security at the festival. When she encounters a suspicious person, what kind of attitude should Yuzu adopt?","Strict","Upholding the spirit of being strict to oneself and others, Yuzu and the Red Panda Squad did not condone anybody who made a mistake. As a result, she knocked over six stalls, two floats, and one old man while chasing wrongdoers... She was currently being scolded in the student council\'s office.","Yuzu and the Red Panda Squad struck down the naughty students who tried to ruin the festival one after another with their iron fists of judgment, leaving only justice and absolute order.","Kind","Under Yuzu\'s leadership, the Red Panda Squad ran everywhere through the festival, but managed to attract countless tourists to take photos with them due to their friendliness, causing a commotion at the venue.","Yuzu and the Red Panda Squad intended to make the naughty students see the error of their ways with tolerance and kindness. They managed to succeed and recruited new blood, bolstering the ranks of the justice patrol.","Kaguyahime","This Is a Command, Not a Proposal","Kaguyahime requests you to arrange a place with good feng shui for her because she wants to give the tourists who visit the festival a chance to serve a god.","Okay","Unexpectedly, Kaguyahime was surprisingly picky about the offerings and didn\'t like anything except gems. At the end of the day, Kaguyahime didn\'t receive any offerings at all and claimed that this was because the place you found had bad feng shui. To punish you, she replaced all the cheese in the cheese bun you just bought with wasabi.","As the first person to present an offering, you were given the right to touch her bunny ears. To your surprise, the curse really took effect, and you actually grew a pair of bunny ears. After seeing this, some other people got very envious and wanted the same bunny ears, and a long line formed in front of Kaguyahime. However, the favor of the gods has always belonged to one person, and you unexpectedly became the center of attention in the festival as the only bunny-eared envoy.","Extremely willing","You start waiting for her after finding a place with good feng shui. In the end, you waited the entire day without Kaguyahime appearing. It wasn\'t until Ichihime came over to complain to you that you found out that Kaguyahime was busy making trouble for Ichihime at the next stall and forgot about her agreement with you.","The people who came to present their offerings formed a long line. Apparently, everyone was willing to pay tribute to her for the chance to catch a glimpse of this cute bunny-eared goddess.","Eliisa","Farm Knowledge Seminar","Eliisa wants to introduce her hometown to everyone at the festival, but she only has a limited amount of time for her speech. What should she focus on?","Beautiful pastures","When Eliisa started the second part of her speech, which was about the beautiful pastures of her home, Shaun ripped the wig off a teacher\'s head in the front row and started chewing on it, causing the seminar to be suspended.","Eliisa\'s speech made the audience feel like they were there. As the tenor sang \"I have a pair of invisible wings\" rhythmically in the background music, the atmosphere reached its climax, and everyone yearned more and more for the beautiful farm life depicted by Eliisa.","Pure white sheep","When Eliisa started the third part of her speech, which was about some newborn lambs in the pasture, the audience started to get drowsy because she got too serious and enumerated the names of all the lambs.","Shaun stayed on stage to help Eliisa with her speech, and its clever and cute appearance attracted everyone\'s attention, making them all say that the best pet in modern society is actually a lamb. A popular saying started circulating at the festival: \"the three things in life are eating, sleeping, and petting Shaun.\"","Kaavi","Omen of Failure","Kaavi is a little distressed because a star athlete came to her stall to ask for the result of the nationals. With how expectant the onlookers are, Kaavi finds it hard to tell the athlete that she will lose in the first round.","Conceal the truth","Kaavi didn\'t want to affect the athlete\'s performance so she concealed the truth. The athlete was happy about the divination and thought victory was in her hands. However, she underestimated her opponents in the competition and met defeat after defeat. Afterwards, she cried out that should have never trusted a fortune teller.","Kaavi didn\'t tell the athlete that she saw an omen of failure. In the nationals, the athlete performed with no mental burden and the competition was fierce. Although the athlete did lose in the end, her excellent performance made it to the sports highlight. In the end, a number of sports clubs reached out to her.","Tell the truth","Kaavi decided to tell the truth and the athlete\'s enthusiasm was dampened. Later, in training, the athlete couldn\'t help but think about failing the competition and disappointing her supporters. In the end, she pulled out of the competition due to mental pressure.","Kaavi decided to tell the truth and the onlookers were all speechless. However, the athlete thanked Kaavi for her reminder and assuaged the audience that she would not give up. During the competition, the athlete gave her best but still lost in the first round, but with her perseverance, she fought her way out of the repechage and managed to enter the next round.","Kana Fujita","Sing and Dance or Play Games","Kana Fujita has been invited to perform at the school festival gala and is wondering if she should do a sing and dance performance, which she is good at, or try to show everyone another side of herself.","Sing and dance","Kana Fujita shined on the stage like always, creating great economic benefits for the stalls that sold fluorescent sticks, cheering items, etc., during the festival. However, since her performance was no different from her usual sing and dance performances, she didn\'t create any special memories for everyone.","There was an unknown problem with the equipment on the festival stage. The background music stopped abruptly, and the lights suddenly went out. However, Kana Fujita\'s light didn\'t go out. With her leading them, the audience raised their mobile phones in the air with the flashlights on and sang along with her. Everyone had a special and unforgettable night.","Stream a game on stage","The game Kana Fujita played on the stage was cast onto the big screen of the festival stage. After her game character suddenly died, she burst out a loud roar on the stage, and it was so loud that it stunned the fans in the audience for a few seconds. Although Kana Fujita immediately spoke in her normal voice again and smiled, she became the trending topic of the day with the keywords \"Kana Fujita\" and \"manly voice.\"","The game Kana Fujita played on the stage was cast onto the big screen of the festival stage. With skilled moves and quick thinking, she interacted with the audience from time to time, giving everyone a wonderful performance. The fans exclaimed that this was their first time participating in such a novel meet-and-greet event. Most importantly, they learned that their idol was also an expert gamer!","Ayako Morikawa","Friends From the Old School Building","Ayako Morikawa wants to invite friends from the old school building to participate in the festival with her and wants your support.","Support her","The student council received many complaints about things disappearing, people falling down for no reason, people choking while eating fried rice and even while drinking water... Everyone agreed that these were pranks played by the ghosts of the old school building and requested an exorcism ceremony to seal the ghosts.","Ayako Morikawa who has always been troubled by social anxiety, seemed to be a lot more relaxed with these friends by her side. She also showed a rare and sweet smile despite being surrounded by people at the crowded festival, which was quickly captured on camera and posted on the school forum. Many people left messages asking about her identity. All of a sudden, the school festival of Asaha High School had a spontaneous activity—search for the mysterious beauty.","Don\'t support her","Ayako Morikawa who has always been troubled by social anxiety, sat alone in a corner during the festival, and not even the company of Hanako, Reiko, and Sadako could make her calm down. During the festival, a strange story about a ghost girl became popular. According to the story, anyone who touches the left hand of the ghost girl will receive a curse that makes them deal into their opponents\' hands for a whole month.","You knew that the reason Ayako Morikawa wanted to invite some \"friends\" from the old school building to accompany her was that she felt uneasy about coming to the festival alone, so you kept her company at the school festival instead. You created lots of miracles at all the game stalls with luck-based games. Ayako Morikawa said this was because you brought good luck with you. You both gain a lot on this day.","Kirara Fujimoto","Makeup Style for the Festival","Kirara Fujimoto is in a dilemma about which style of makeup she should choose for the festival, so she decides to just send you a sample photo of herself with both styles of makeup. Which do you prefer?","Natural style","Kirara Fujimoto came to the festival wearing light makeup for a natural look, only to find that every girl here was well dressed and full of personality. After looking at the girls around her, to protect her dignity as a gal, Kirara Fujimoto redid her makeup urgently and missed some wonderful performances of the festival as a result.","Many people marveled at Kirara Fujimoto\'s natural look at the festival. Her face glowed with the youthful aura of a high school girl, and her light makeup highlighted her superb makeup skills. Thanks to you, she was the focus of the school on that day.","Glamorous style","Kirara Fujimoto was a member of the honor guard on the day of the festival. She didn\'t fit in with the other members because she had heavy makeup even though she was wearing a simple school uniform. Some people even started questioning whether she had done that intentionally to attract people\'s attention. Although she\'s always carefree and doesn\'t take things to heart, she couldn\'t help but feel sad and hid in the lounge alone.","To showcase the vibrant and diverse side of Asaha High School\'s students, a runway was specially arranged at the festival. After being spotted by the organizer, Kirara Fujimoto became the main star of the show and perfectly demonstrated the style of a hot girl to everyone.","Ichihime","Big Eater Challenge, Nyaa","Due to Ichihime\'s dominance in this competition, the rules of the big eater challenge have been specially modified for her, and the top five will challenge her as a team, in a relay manner. Ichihime is so nervous that she has already eaten several portions of takoyaki. If you don\'t help her find a solution, the takoyaki stall will soon run out of stock.","Believe in her","The top five challengers each chose a type of food that they excel at eating, which included spicy hot pot, watermelon that has been chilled for eight hours, and an equal mix of male and female steamed hairy crabs... To everyone\'s surprise, Ichihime started suffering from unbearable abdominal pain and was sent to the hospital soon after taking on the third challenger. Eating that combination of foods could wreak havoc on anyone\'s stomach no matter how tough it is!","It\'s no secret that Ichihime\'s stomach is connected to a black hole, but to be safe, you checked the food that would be eaten in the competition in advance to make sure they would be safe. In the end, Ichihime lived up to everyone\'s expectations and won the competition. The first thing she said to you after the competition was: \"Master, can I eat a large snack giftpack, nyaa? I\'m really hungry, nyaa.\"","Tell her she doesn\'t have to compete","You didn\'t realize that Ichihime had stopped eating three days in advance in anticipation of the competition. After learning that she wouldn\'t be participating in the competition, she ate everything at the takoyaki stall, and you had no choice but to pay the crying stall owner for everything... As for how much you paid? You downplayed the situation and said: \"I\'ll be starving for the next three months.\"","The judges sat at their table. After you persuaded Ichihime not to compete, she decided to become a judge instead. The five evenly matched contestants and Ichihime, who only wanted to taste all the food in the competition, all have a bright future ahead of them.","Yui Yagi","Science Lecture Topic","You were entrusted by the student council to invite Yui Yagi to give a science lecture during the festival, but she has trouble deciding on a good topic. She hopes you will help her come up with a lecture topic.","\"Which Tile to Discard? - Fes Edition\"","Yui Yagi started the lecture with the intention to present a very novel theme. She prepared many questions for demonstration, which sparked lively discussions among the audience. However, her voice was too soft and was quickly drowned out by the noise of the audience\'s debates, leading to chaos at the scene.","Although Yui Yagi didn\'t feel her mahjong skills were strong enough to give a science lecture, she trusted your judgment and managed to secure the top spot multiple times in live demonstrations, igniting the audience\'s enthusiasm and earning thunderous applause. You couldn\'t be sure if it was your imagination, but her calm face seemed slightly flushed.","\"The Observer Effect\"","Theoretical science proved to be a bit too profound for high school students, and only a few came to the lecture. Minutes later, the lecture room turned into a new haven for a nap party. From Yui Yagi\'s calm gaze towards you, you sensed a silent reprimand.","The lecture was a great success. Yui Yagi\'s concise and accurate explanations combined scientific theoretical knowledge with competitive mahjong, attracting many earnestly learning students. The school leadership was very satisfied and plans to hold ten more sessions on this topic at Asaha High School.","Robot Battle","A robot battle would be held at the festival, and Mirai was specially invited to compete in it. However, her scientific research and practical abilities are far superior to those of the other students, so she is troubled about whether she should go easy on them.","Use 10% of her abilities","As Mirai only charged her robot to 10%, the battle ended soon after it started. The other contestants thought that Mirai\'s actions were a sign of disrespect for them and the competition, so they demanded that she be disqualified.","Mirai thought it was more important for the other students to enjoy a taste of victory than winning the competition herself, so she brought a robot that had many social functions, having the ability to tell jokes and answer some professional questions. The competition was extremely fierce, and the ring was surrounded by onlookers. Everyone became good friends after the competition.","Go all out","Mirai wanted to show off her abilities in the robot battle, so she brought \"Slayer,\" the war machine she was most proud of, to the competition. However, \"Slayer\" had a peculiar feature... While explaining this feature, Mirai smiled and randomly selected a person from the crowd. \"Slayer\" leaned over and carried this person in its arms, then in a voice so loud that everyone could hear it clearly, it said: \"BMI 28.9. You are overweight!\" This robot really was a slayer in every sense of the word.","Mirai wanted to show off her abilities in the robot battle, so she brought \"Love & Peace,\" the war machine she was most proud of, to the competition. \"Love & Peace\" was two meters tall. It was equipped with homing missiles for long-range engagement, as well as a powerful magnet and flamethrower for close-quarters combat, preventing any escape. After \"Love & Peace\" entered the ring, nobody dared to challenge it, and everyone forfeited. However, the beautiful wish conveyed by the name of this robot came true, and public order improved at the festival.","Ninjutsu Training","As there are a lot of people at the festival, this is a rare opportunity for Ransei to practice her ninjutsu, and she decides to reward herself with a bowl of super luxurious ramen with ten slices of beef if she is successful. Therefore, she wants to ask her master where she should train to get the best training results.","Under Kaavi\'s fortune telling stall","After receiving strict ninja training Ransei is able to restrain the urge to laugh while concealed unless she really can\'t help it... \"Do superheroes wear another pair of underwear under their tights?\" \"A live wire and a neutral wire fall into the water at the same time. Which wire should I save first?\" ...The people who came to ask Kaavi to tell their fortunes asked some really strange questions, and Ransei, who was hiding under the table, couldn\'t stop herself from laughing... As a result, her training was unsuccessful.","The most dangerous place is often the safest place. As the fortune telling stall was the most popular stall, the constant flow of people meant that Ransei had no chance to relax. She hid under the table with her concealment technique and breathed carefully, fully focused on whether she should eat the beef in the ramen first or last. The entire day passed, and nobody knew she was there except you.","Among Yuzu\'s Red Panda Squad","Using a transformation technique, Ransei successfully sneaked into Yuzu\'s Red Panda Squad. As they walked around, lots of people looked at the Red Panda Squad due to how cute they were, but she was lucky that nobody noticed her. Absolutely delighted, Ransei was just about to reward herself with a bowl of super luxurious ramen when she suddenly saw a photo on CatChat... Apparently, Ransei was used to transforming into a beautiful girl, so she had transformed into a red panda wearing a hip-hugging skirt this time out of habit.","Ransei believed that at the highest level, the transformation technique was equivalent to a top concealment technique capable of keeping a person hidden in a bustling city. In the past, Ransei mostly transformed into other humans, so she wanted to transform into an animal this time. After using her ninjutsu, she transformed into a red panda with a boom sound, then she whizzed her way into Yuzu\'s patrol squad. Although she wasn\'t familiar with the butt-twisting and tail-swishing movements, she was successful, and nobody noticed that there were four red pandas following Yuzu during this time.","Hana Ninomiya","Book Exchange Event","Hana Ninomiya wants to organize a book sharing event and is conflicted over whether she should require people to provide their real names or an anonymous name.","Real name","For some reason, everyone brought books such as, \"Three Assessments and Five Practice Tests,\" \"100 Super Difficult Math Questions,\" or \"Welcoming Literature Bravely,\" which were extremely common at school for the book exchange, and very few people participated in the event. Hana Ninomiya was very troubled by this.","Since everyone who submits or receives a book in the book exchange must provide their real name, the number of participants and their enthusiasm might have been affected to a certain extent. However, some people still managed to meet others who had the same hobbies as them through this event. After all, there\'s nothing happier than getting positive feedback from others about things you have sincerely recommended.","Anonymous name","Although the anonymity made students more enthusiastic, it also brought more chaos. People submitted all sorts of books, as if they were eager to show off their special preferences to others. Some readers said these books opened doors to new worlds for them, but some people couldn\'t accept this, and the student council intervened urgently to end this event.","Forcing people to provide their real names would make things too transparent when sharing books, and Hana Ninomiya also believed that retaining some privacy would encourage students like herself, who wanted to share books but were introverted, to share. Through this book exchange, many students temporarily put down their own hobbies and opened up to more unpopular and unique books. Upon seeing that the event made everyone happy, Hana Ninomiya also felt an unprecedented sense of satisfaction.","Lin Lang","Cooking Competition Judge","Lin Lang says that the only thing she wants to do at this festival is to be a tasting judge in the cooking competition, and she hopes you will give her this chance.","Say yes","Lin Lang got her wish and became a judge in the cooking competition, but she wasn\'t as fair as she imagined. \"American steak, 10 points! Army Stew, 10 points! Omurice, 10 points! Twice-cooked pork, 10 points! Mushroom rice bowl, disqualification with negative points! Although the scores Lin Lang gave out were ultimately invalidated, the contestants felt that this competition was unprofessional.","Although the scores Lin Lang gave out weren\'t as valuable as expected, and she wasn\'t professional enough, her intoxicated expression when tasting the food, the amazing speed at which she consumed the food, and her generous praise gave the participants of this competition a different kind of psychological satisfaction that was even comparable to the sense of accomplishment gained from winning a prize from the competition.","Say no","Lin Lang sat as close to the tasting table as she could in the stands. Whenever she saw the judges putting food into their mouths with chopsticks, she would ask what it tasted like and whether it was delicious. The judges couldn\'t bear to eat the food with Lin Lang\'s innocent and lovely eyes on them, so Lin Lang ended up eating everything, and the judges guessed the scores of the foods based on the expression she made when eating them.","The competition announced its cooking theme for this year. As the One Han City Shiitake Mushroom Farm sponsored the competition, all contestants must use the shiitake mushrooms produced by the farm in the competition. After hearing about the theme, in addition to expressing her disdain for shiitake mushrooms, Lin Lang also expressed her understanding and approval of your decision. She then turned around and spent all the money she had saved over the previous weeks on food at the other food stalls.","Chihori Terasaki","News Topic Selection","Chihori Terasaki wants to do a special report on the school festival, but she hasn\'t been able to decide on one of the section topics and has decided to ask for your opinion.","The Most Popular Event","You received an unusually thick envelope, and upon opening it, you found a handwritten letter from Chihori Terasaki along with eighty survey questionnaires examining various aspects of the festival activities. She sincerely invited you to be her special reporter to distribute the questionnaires at Asaha High School. After a whole day of running around, you belatedly realized that you might have been used by the editor-in-chief as free labor.","Chihori Terasaki sent you a survey report that analyzed the festival\'s most popular events, taking into account various demographics and dimensions. The number one ranking went to Kana Fujita\'s evening performance. The second place was Riu Kujou\'s café... This report is of great value for optimizing future festival planning and event preparations.","The Event with the Most Beautiful Girls","Chihori Terasaki sent you a detailed survey report, listing the number of beautiful girls in each festival event and pie charts of the data. She also quietly added a note to your data — \"Fond of beautiful women,\" and unknowingly, you seem to have become potential news material for Chihori Terasaki.","Chihori Terasaki sent you a detailed survey report. After receiving the report, you personally conducted fieldwork at the events starting from the most popular event with beautiful girls and pragmatically analyzed the data for hidden information and messages. In the end, by improving publicity methods and designing events that were more in line with user preferences, you obtained a large amount of festival funds.","Student Council Member","We\'re running low on funds for science-related activities and we lack chairs for the audience. Your generosity will decide if we get to enjoy the president\'s snacks.","Give a regular amount","Give a little extra","No Classes Today","The entertainment booth is crazy popular! The students can have a better time if you can increase our funding!","Call Me the Warrior of Justice","The festival is extremely exciting, having one climax after another, but the influx of people is impossible to manage anymore. Please send more security personnel immediately!","Increase security slightly","Increase security drastically","Deal In Isn\'t the End","What type of mahjong competition will we be having during this year\'s festival?","Fun","Competitive","Adventure Channel Fan","It\'s finally the day. I need spoilers. Please tell me if the Treasure Hunt Adventure is being held at the school building or the entire campus?","The school building","The entire campus","Among the countless festival activities, knowledge on safety is always the priority. Should we spend event funds on holding a safety seminar to ensure the festival goes off without a hitch?","It\'s necessary","It isn\'t necessary","The Literary World Needs Me","The festival\'s reading corner is looking a bit like a ghost town. I\'m sure replacing the benches with comfortable sofas will be a much-needed improvement. What is your opinion on this expenditure?","Buy the sofa and pay for knowledge","Keep using the benches","Drama Queen","Supposedly, if you add a mysterious BGM to the psychological horror show, Dealing In 2, which is being performed at night during the school festival, it\'ll induce screams from the entire audience! As a member of the Drama Club, I would like to request a super loud sound system to bring the atmosphere there to its peak!","Make the purchase","Fear engraved in your DNA needs no sound system","Security Personnel","Patrolling the festival is an important job that must be done well. If we\'re provided a standard set of walkie-talkies, we\'ll be able to communicate effectively, and that will give a tremendous boost to our efficiency.","Purchase the walkie-talkies","Refuse","Business Expert","Relax, I\'m not here to apply for funding. I just have a small suggestion for you. You should consider inviting some well-known businesses in One Han City to collaborate with the school festival. Your funding will be endless once the investments come in.","Refuse in order to maintain the festival\'s freedom","Invite them because cash flow is everything","Gamer","The equipment for the gaming competition is too outdated. Could we have them updated to elevate the contestants\' experience?","Upgrade the equipment","They are still usable","Security Personnel","The snack stalls are beyond busy. Should we limit the flow of people toward them?","Limit the flow of people","Business as usual","Member of the Marketing Department","The school newspaper has limited space. Should we focus more on fun and interesting activities or the school festival\'s traditions in this special issue on the school festival?","Traditions","Interesting activities","This year\'s festival is so much fun! The only flaw is that the security personnel are too stern. I\'ll give the festival five stars if they patrol while dressed up as dolls!","Make the security personnel dress up","Tell the security personnel to stay stern","How Did You Know I\'m the Top Student?","Immersion learning is my way of participating in the school festival. Could you assign personnel to stop students from messing around in the library?","Make arrangements for the top student","Our funds don\'t allow it","School Debate Team Member","After an intense debate, we\'ve decided on \"Overcoming Myself is My Victory/My Loss\" as the topic for the school festival\'s Debate Competition. Could you let me know if you consider this a fun or serious topic?","It\'s a fun topic","It\'s a serious topic","My Cards Have Found Their Match","I have a few friends from off-campus that are great at magic! What do you think about inviting them to put on a performance at our school?","Agree","Refuse","Passionate Student","My family owns a restaurant, and we can provide free lunches for busy students during the school festival. However, the quantity isn\'t enough to feed all the students. What would be the best place to send them?","The mahjong club","The gym club","Handicraft Enthusiast","Hi, I would like to open a handicraft stall for the school festival, but the stalls seem to be fully booked. Could you help me figure something out?","Of course, I\'ll make the arrangements","I\'m sorry, it\'s first come first serve","All Last is Just the Beginning","The competition is about to begin. How do I stay calm in a long South Wind round?","It\'s too difficult, I suggest avoiding it","Use All Simples to speed it up","So Hard to Choose","Excuse me, I\'m suffering from decidophobia. What should I do during the school festival? I can\'t decide!","How about staying quiet and doing nothing?","So I\'m not the only one with a phobia for decision-making","Passionate Teacher","The teachers of Asaha High School would like to chip in for the school festival too! How can we help?","Help lighten the atmosphere","Join security","Anonymous Student","Can I do whatever I want during the school festival?","A copy of this application has been forwarded to the student council","I recommend reading the school\'s rules","Security Personnel","We caught a few students causing trouble during the school festival. They admitted their mistakes but said they would do it again. What should we do with them?","Make them clean up the festival area","Hand them over to a Student Council Member","I\'m the Haunted House NPC","How can a school festival go without a haunted house? Our perfect haunted house setup is only lacking a finale. Please help me come up with an unforgettable punishment for those who run away!","Make them be NPCs like you","Make them finish ten test papers","Fire safety is of the utmost importance during the school festival. How do we increase student awareness on the subject?","Conduct a fire drill","Conduct a seminar on fire safety","Fashion Design Club Member","The Fashion Design Club would like to showcase our designs during the school festival. Should we use mannequins as our display models or organize a fashion show on the runway with students?","Mannequins","Fashion show","Is the sale of doujinshi allowed in stalls during the school festivals?","Yes","No","The science and technology exhibition, with its cutting-edge, self-operating mahjong tables, has unexpectedly become the star attraction of our school festival. It has grown so popular that snagging a ticket is now a challenge! Should we allow students to enter the exhibition freely without a reservation?","No","Yes","Fes Budget bonus for proposals and incidents: {0}","Chance to change Failures to Success: {0}%","Level up and spend Fes Budget to procure proposals","The cost of procuring proposals reduced: {0}","Fes Stats bonus for proposals and incidents: {0}","E-","E","E+","D-","D","D+","C-","C","C+","B-","B","B+","A-","A","A+","S","SS","SSS","Empty Bottle","Delicious Shrimp","Decorative Shell","Pepperoni Pizza","Chocolate Waffle","Croissant","Water Gun","Massage Gun","Umbrella","Jewelry Stand","Riichi Bet Choker","Crystal Dinosaur","Ducky Sea-Saw","The island has received gifts from the sea, and shrimp are abundant by the shore. The price of [tag]Delicious Shrimp[/tag] will significantly [tag]decrease[/tag].","Experts say that eating shrimp helps boost immunity, improve sleep quality, and even enhance one\'s luck in mahjong. The price of [tag]Delicious Shrimp[/tag] will significantly [tag]increase[/tag].","Recently produced [tag]Decorative Shell[/tag] have been reported to have quality issues, breaking upon touch. The price of [tag]Decorative Shell[/tag] will significantly [tag]decrease[/tag].","A famous actress\'s shell earrings have become a hot fashion item on the island. The price of [tag]Decorative Shell[/tag] will significantly [tag]increase[/tag].","An anonymous tip revealed that the secret to the bakery\'s delicious bread is the addition of addictive substances. The prices of all products from the [tag]Bakery[/tag] will significantly [tag]decrease[/tag].","The well-known gourmet show \"Taste of the Island\" aired a new episode, \"The Secret of Bread.\" The prices of all products from the [tag]Bakery[/tag] will significantly [tag]increase[/tag].","A student caused an eye infection in others by filling a toy water gun with dirty water, so parents are boycotting it. The price of [tag]Water Gun[/tag] will significantly [tag]decrease[/tag].","Tomorrow\'s high temperatures on the island will make water gun battles a new trend in beach activities. The price of [tag]Water Gun[/tag] will significantly [tag]increase[/tag].","Citizens have complained that using the island\'s fascia massage guns causes bruising, making them feel as if they\'ve been beaten up. The price of [tag]Massage Gun[/tag] will significantly [tag]decrease[/tag].","Experts claim that long-term use of fascia massage guns can shatter kidney stones. The price of [tag]Massage Gun[/tag] will significantly [tag]increase[/tag].","Heavy to torrential rain is expected tomorrow. The price of [tag]Umbrella[/tag] will significantly [tag]increase[/tag].","Tomorrow is a day off for students at the Island School. The prices of all goods at [tag]Island School[/tag] will significantly [tag]decrease[/tag].","The Island School will hold a sports day tomorrow. The prices of all goods at [tag]Island School[/tag] will significantly [tag]increase[/tag].","The mascot performer at Mahjong Zone has been exposed for scandalous behavior. The prices of all goods at [tag]Mahjong Zone[/tag] will significantly [tag]decrease[/tag].","The 36th Island Mahjong Tournament has begun and it brought a surge of tourists to the Mahjong Zone. The prices of all goods at [tag]Mahjong Zone[/tag] will significantly [tag]increase[/tag].","Returning to nature is the new trend on the island, and sleeping outdoors is more popular than in a comfy bed. The prices of all goods at [tag]Holiday Resort[/tag] will significantly [tag]decrease[/tag].","It\'s said that staying at the resort allows one to see red pandas patrolling at dawn, attracting many tourists. The prices of all goods at [tag]Holiday Resort[/tag] will significantly [tag]increase[/tag].","Welcome to \nSAMU Joy Island","Patrolling the Park","HIBI Haunted \nHouse Channel","Royal Theater","Claw Crane Challenge","Waver of Dreams","A Trip Full of \n\"Gourmet Food\"","Summer Fireworks","Adventurous Wonderland","Chance Meeting \nat the Aquarium","Romance in the Park","Looking Forward","SAMU Joy Island","Cynthia Studio","Cynthia","Kana No.1","Hibiki Fan","Is Hibiki Streaming Today?","Hibiki Makes Me Happy","I Love Cynthia","Addicted to Cynthia","Walking With Cynthia","Let Me See Who\'s Unhappy","Fall in Love Early","I Hate Work","Cynthia the Goddess","Nicknames Aren\'t Important","Lucky to Have Cynthia","Kana No.1","A Fan\'s Obsession","Kana Fujita\'s Hairpin","It\'s time to visit the island! Dear tourists, please check in here on this CatChat to commemorate the start of your wonderful SAMU Joy Island adventure!//[tag]#Draw[/tag] The 21-day soft opening of SAMU Joy Island is about to begin. Congratulations to [tag]@Leia, @I\'ll Wash My Head While Doing a Handstand if I\'m Selected, @The Opponent\'s Monkey, @Kaavi[/tag], and other lucky tourists of One Han City for winning the chance to visit the island this time! Check here to see the full list of winners →[tag]Full List of Winners[/tag]","Welcome to SAMU Joy Island! I can\'t wait to explore the amusement park!","Ohhh, my babe! I have a ticket, so I\'m coming to see you![tag]@Cynthia\'s Closet[/tag] It looks like your idol will also be there for work, inside info. No need to thank me.","Haha, I\'m looking forward to it.[tag]@Kaavi @Yuzu [/tag]","Welcome to SAMU Joy Island!","I want to thank the organizers of SAMU Joy Island for inviting me. My livestream will give everyone an immersive experience of all the happiness and joy this island has to offer! The registration entrance is already available, and I\'ll be your guide on this adventure! [tag]Website link[/tag]","Yay! So lucky! The chosen high school student is here to check in!","Hehe, does this count as an outing?[tag]@Ayako Morikawa @Sora Ichinose @Anju Suzumiya [/tag]","Wow! I wonder what natural scenery is waiting for us on a warm island. Hehe, my camera is locked, loaded, and ready for action!","Beep. Jyanshi card.","Welcome, {name}! We hope you\'ll have a great time here on SAMU Joy Island!","Welcome, Mirai! We hope you have a great time here on SAMU Joy Island!","Oh, so the comments are replied automatically.","QAQ No! I reply to all comments manually.","Wow, someone from the official account is actually reading the comments!","I strive to make this the most friendly official account, so please keep interacting with me!","Sunshine, beach, water paradise--here I come!","Master, I\'m fully armed and ready for anything. I\'ll definitely keep you safe during this trip!","Fully armed... What did you bring?","In addition to my kunai, makibishi, and other conventional weapons, I\'ve also brought the small razor-sharp tachi that my father forged from black iron recently.","...Promise me that you\'ll leave all of that at home. The island is really safe, so you don\'t need to bring anything other than yourself.","Destiny will give you a big surprise if you aren\'t careful. These careless tourists have been waiting in line for a long time, completely oblivious to the fact that they are lining up for my fortune-telling stall until they are in front of me... The look of despair on their faces makes me smile.","I knew it. I\'ve been lining up for Kaavi\'s fortune-telling stall all this time, haha.","Um... I\'m actually packing up already. You haven\'t seen [tag]@Yuzu[/tag] today, right? She should be wandering around somewhere around you.","Is that true? [tag]@Yuzu [/tag]","Ehhh! I\'m on patrol, not wandering! I\'m not there anymore. I\'m patrolling in the vicinity of the theater now!","Hmm, I believe a good child like Yuzu won\'t tell lies, right?","Actually, I\'m not quite at the theater yet, but I\'m almost there. I\'m going to start my patrol now...","Sigh, what a shame. I thought I would finally do my duty as your teacher and spend the whole day having fun with you two at the amusement park. I didn\'t think that... Oh well, you two can go ahead and play by yourselves today.","Okay, Master!","Sure thing, Miss Leia!","We\'re here on the island for a vacation, so why are you still telling people\'s fortunes, Kaavi? Aren\'t you going to play on any of the rides?","Rather than saying that I\'m telling people\'s fortunes, it\'s more accurate to say that I\'m waiting for the arrangements of fate.","And what arrangements are those exactly?","Fate is telling me that my identity as a fortune teller is essential if I want to be the happiest I can be on this island.","Are you talking about...","My fortune in making a fortune, of course. The tourists here are all fascinated by fortune-telling, so my business is booming. It\'s making me so happy.","Are you opening tomorrow? I\'ll make sure to line up early.","According to my crystal ball, I won\'t be open for business tomorrow.","But I\'ll be traveling with someone, and that person is you.","[tag]#HIBIHauntedHouseChannel[/tag] Is Hibiki Himekawa\'s SAMU Joy Island livestream leaving you thirsting for more? Worry not! The highlight reel is now available online! [tag]@Hibiki Himekawa[/tag] What interesting things have happened while streaming this thrilling adventure? Check here for the replay →[tag]Website link[/tag] [tag]#SAMUJoyIslandNowOpen[/tag] Check here for the highlight reel →[tag]Website link[/tag]","Meanwhile, we sincerely invite everyone to share your review of the Haunted Dormitory Live! Repost this and leave a comment about your experience for a chance to win SAMU Joy Island merch!","Mmm... I felt like I was there again when I saw the video...[tag]@Hana Ninomiya[/tag] I\'m really sorry, I didn\'t mean to run off like that... It\'s just that the bell of the dormitory sounded exactly the same as the one at school, so I panicked and ran...","I give it a 5 star. It\'s a good place to practice my ninjutsu.","Sadako said she had lots of fun... and met many interesting friends.","Average.","After I shared my review with my new friends there... they said they were sorry and would work harder to bring more happiness to everyone...","{name}, wanna give a another shot? It should be better than last time because everyone has been training really hard...","Amazing.","What a concise evaluation. I\'ve decided to privately sponsor you with a merch. Remember to come and see me tonight!","What\'s wrong with these questions that I need to answer to get the stamps from the Royal Theater? You want me to guess what the lions are saying when they roar in \"A Lion\'s Game of Thrones...\" I bet that none of the three answers are correct, right?[tag]@SAMU Joy Island[/tag]","Hey, thanks for your feedback! We\'re looking into it right away. We really appreciate your help in making our soft opening better.","Maybe you can try to answer the questions for another performance. The questions for the other two performances might be easier... I think.","...So you\'re the person who watched three performances in a row to get the commemorative stamp. No wonder the staff kept encouraging me to stick it out and mentioned someone who watched all three performances... You really are patient...","You don\'t get it. This is the unyielding spirit that drives humans to keep challenging themselves!","Hannah also said something similar when we watched the performance together.","Tsk... no wonder I couldn\'t find you anywhere. So you were watching performances with someone else.","It was just by chance. Really! I also ran into Natsuki, Fuyumi, and Eve.","Geez, you bumped into so many people. How come none of them are me?","How would I know... Wait a minute, do you want to hang out with me?","Huh?! Where did you get that from? Don\'t be ridiculous! I\'m very busy!","Seriously, don\'t read too much into it. When I passed by the roller coaster earlier, I just thought it would be fun to make you get on it to give you a fright.","Got it?","Got it. Let\'s go on the roller coaster together later.","Hmph, just don\'t start crying when you get scared on the ride later.","[tag]@Natsuki Shinomiya[/tag] Brother, this is why the claw cranes disappeared overnight. It\'s got nothing to do with some parallel universe nonsense...//[tag]@SAMU Joy Island[/tag]: Dear tourists, due to a technical issue, all the claw cranes have been sent back to the factory for repairs. Please wait patiently for their grand return! In the meantime, we invite you to enjoy the other awesome video game attractions on the island!","Heh, you\'re too young and too naive. Official announcements are usually used to cover up the truth. Demon King Fuyumi, don\'t trust humans so readily.","You\'re even less trustworthy than humans!","Fuyumi, how about ditching your brother and hanging out with me! [tag]@Fuyumi Shinomiya[/tag]","Although I\'m worried my brother will get into trouble if I leave him alone... let\'s ditch him and have some fun!","I know what you mean. To be honest, I\'m... partially responsible for the creation of this parallel universe. [tag]@Natsuki Shinomiya[/tag]","Oh, my friend, let\'s find a place to discuss this in detail.","What do you think when you see... this?","Wow! Is that a jellyfish from the aquarium? Why did you sneak off there without us?!","I saw an acquaintance when I was passing by, so I went inside to take a look...","Ninomiya, what does it remind you of?","...It just reminded me of just how... invisible and insignificant I am... just drifting along...","Why do you say that?","{name}, I followed you when you went to the aquarium... and... you were chatting so happily with everyone in the aquarium... so I started to look forward to talking to you... but... I stood in front of the jellyfish tank for a long time, and you ignored me like you ignored those jellyfish...","Huh???","These jellyfish look so fresh. They must taste great in a cold dish.","That\'s sure is some... unconventional thinking.","Hmm, maybe I got a bit brainwashed by some of the stuff I heard at the aquarium today.","Me before coming to this island: Vacation is just working in another place.\nMe right now: I take that back.","Wow, Chihori isn\'t working overtime by herself tonight! I sense an unusual vibe.","Filling wine glasses with grape juice is definitely the organizers\' idea, right...","After all, it\'s an amusement park for all ages. Are you seriously fixated on the grape juice instead of the vibe?","You... were too close to me at that time, so I felt embarrassed...","It looks like we need to get to know each other a lot more intimately. We\'ll start with tomorrow\'s new request.","Every short break is usually made possible by a hard worker like me...","It seems that tonight\'s dinner didn\'t satisfy you. Can you give me another shot tomorrow?","Miki looks even more astonishing than usual today! She said she shared the dishes I carefully selected with friends who would be able to appreciate them! So she\'s in a super good mood! Sure enough, elegance comes from within! Sharing generously is a quality of a tasteful and elegant lady! I learned something new today!","So you\'re her accomplice...","Huh? Accomplice... What do you mean?","Your boss is a famous jeweler of Tenhoukaku, not a gourmet chef, so why is she always going on about food?","Miki said that we should do anything but our job when we\'re out to have fun!","But isn\'t she like this in One Han City, too?","Well, everyone likes to slack off while they\'re at work. Don\'t you?","[tag]#BestFireworksSpot[/tag]  After reading your guide, I decided to not watch the fireworks display in the crowded plaza. Instead, I found a slow-moving roller coaster ride nearby. Watching fireworks while riding a roller coaster... How should I describe this experience? I saw the fireworks clearly... it wasn\'t crowded at all... and the night breeze was very comfortable... but why didn\'t anyone tell me that the photos would all end up like this?","Hahahahahaha! Hahahahahahahaha! Hahahahaha!","Hahahahaha! You have unlocked a new achievement!","Lol! I was wondering who was screaming on the roller coaster during the fireworks display--","This photo looks very artistic. It\'s a very unique moment.","Really...? Since you like it so much, do you want to get your own photo during tomorrow night\'s fireworks display?","Why didn\'t you ask me to join you?","Yeah, it\'s a pity... Okay then, I\'ll ask you next time! Don\'t back out at the last minute!","The joyful shooting schedule finally started. Unexpectedly, the first to collapse was not the artist, but me. As I didn\'t get enough sleep the night before, I actually got heatstroke the moment I arrived at the island... Fortunately, there\'s this miracle-working doctor in the medical station on the island. My dizziness and blurry vision all disappeared after I took her medicine! Now that I\'m no longer dizzy, I feel like I\'m ready for ten more shoots with Cynthia! Who knew that within just one hour, she would give the prop balloon we were using for the photo shoot to a stranger while wandering around the amusement park! (She also brought back a normal-looking balloon... but it looks really precious to her...) Anyway, I blacked out suddenly and had to lie down in the medical room again... Fortunately, Cynthia is a natural at doing photo shoots... There were no more suitable balloons for the final video, but she found props that were even more fantastic. Cynthia is as incredible as ever...! I\'ll get to the point now. More videos will be officially announced later, haha. I\'ll show you something from behind the scenes first!","That\'s so much nonsense. If you delay the next day\'s schedule again because you stayed up to play mahjong, I\'ll hang you up in the set like a prop.","QAQ I won\'t do it again! This is the last time!!!","Hang me up too! Please! (Expressing my love rationally behind my twisted and screaming face)","Soooooooo gorgeous!!!","Ahhh! That\'s my idol! All supermodels have their own flair!","I want to see the original image in three seconds. [tag]@Cynthia[/tag]","Stay tuned for the official video! (PS: You must be a new follower, right? Just so you know, the weeds growing on the grave of the last person who dared to @ her like this in a chat are already as tall as her now.)","How lame. Do you want to lose the eyes that witnessed everything firsthand?","???","That balloon was meant to be a prop?!","Why else would I be walking around with a balloon?","Although the tarot cards reminded me to bring more medicinal materials to One Han City, I\'ve ended up using more than I expected... Haha, this just shows how unpredictable fate can be. Just like how I foresaw that a good child would grant one of my wishes... But their identity turned out to be a complete surprise...","I\'ve prepared some medicinal materials in advance. I\'ll take them to your room later.","Kaavi, you really are talented at telling fortunes. Did you already foresee my predicament?","No one can change fate. You did this on purpose... right?","Haha, remember to bring Yuzu with you. It\'s been a long time since the three of us slept together.","Are you satisfied with this accident?","Am I satisfied? Haha, I think it\'s too early to tell... but it\'s always been wonderful to observe the arrangements of fate. Isn\'t that right?","Did you come to One Han City because of this person?","Hmm, yes... or no? I can\'t say for sure at this time because I need to find out if they are a good child first.","Confusion From the Red Queen Actress: This is strange. Did all the tourists go to your side today? [tag]@Ciri[/tag]","No. Only one or two groups. According to the feedback from the staff, most of them should have gone to your side.","But I haven\'t seen any tourists since noon.","So you\'re the Red Queen!","Ehehe, did you only find out now? You foolish mortal! Just so you know, I threw everyone out without a second thought. Only you have received the favor of the gods. Are you moved?","Huh?! You were here on the Red Queen\'s side? I didn\'t see you at all.","There\'s only one truth: Everyone, including me, has been intercepted by a certain rabbit who has been pretending to be the Red Queen...","Sara, are you also an NPC here?!","Yes, it\'s a shame you didn\'t come to my side, or else I would show you the Red Queen\'s dance.","What\'s the Red Queen\'s dance?","Haha, it\'s a dance I came up with while waiting for tourists. If you don\'t mind, I can show you tonight.","[tag]#Lost&FoundSummary[/tag] Dear tourists, please take good care of your personal belongings during your visit to SAMU Joy Island. Please contact us as soon as possible if you lose anything. You can also leave a message on CatChat to see if other tourists can help you.","Someone has lost their deal-in and knock-out record. It\'s been sent to the tourist center.","I\'m looking for my girlfriend who has been missing for 20 years. The fortune teller at the amusement park said she\'s here on the island!","I\'m looking for my hair that ran away from home. The red-haired doctor in the medical station said that I have a chance of regaining them if I stay in a place where I don\'t need to work...","As expected of a harmonious and beautiful island.","It\'s thanks to all our tourists!","Is this a manual reply?","QAQ Please don\'t tease me. I\'m working seriously!","What a beautiful state of mind.","It\'s another happy and joyful day today on the island.","Promise me that this joyful adventure will never end.","There\'s no such thing as a never-ending adventure, but... you are welcome to come back anytime you want.","The wind has carried the urge to play mahjong to this island.","I want to play too. Where should I go?","Huh? Does everyone want to play mahjong?","Wow, the president found a great place. I want to go too.","I\'ve sent you the location. This is a specially developed seaside mahjong area.","I\'m coming now!","There\'s no rush. I\'ll wait for you.","Attractions or mahjong... This is the question.","Well, do you want to play mahjong with me here? The air is fresh, and the scenery is pleasant. I also want to play mahjong with you.","[tag]#TravelToEscapeOrdinaryLife[/tag] [tag]#GoingToAnotherCityMakesYouBraverAndBolder[/tag] The netizens sure are better at summarizing things than me.","That\'s not a reason for you to come to the door of my hotel room at 3 a.m. in the morning with a shovel, waking me up to go dig for clams.","Pfft, the most amazing thing about Nadeshiko is that she\'s the same whether she\'s drunk or not... It\'s a good thing you stopped her... You stopped her, right?","Nah. I whipped out my phone and recorded the whole thing.","...I still plan to return to One Han City, so please don\'t include me in your report.","I feel the same way. It\'s easier to go wild when you are in a new place.","In a new place, it feels like everything you do is part of a closed beta test that will be deleted afterward... unless you have some bad friends who keep records for you.","How did clam digging go?","Sometimes, I\'ll admit that I have no skill at certain things.","On the surface: Island amusement park trip\nTruth: Ten-kilometer outdoor cross-country training","It\'s so good to be young. Your body is filled with energy... Here\'s a like.","Miss Kisaragi!!! You\'re not allowed to sleep in at the hotel tomorrow. The vice president has put aside his work to play with us. You must come and have some fun with us too!","But it\'s outdoors... I\'ll be under the sun... and lining up... I give up. I\'m no longer that happy girl who bravely encouraged her cousin to wear a mermaid costume for Halloween...","No sun, no fun.","That\'s the spirit. I\'ve sent you tomorrow\'s arrangements. We\'ll meet up at 6 a.m.! I\'ll call you! See you there!","Maybe we should take a break","Don\'t worry! Tomorrow will be very relaxing.","Wonderful! Where are we going?","We\'re going to get a massage! But you\'ll be in for both pain and pleasure because I\'ve arranged a fascia blading treatment for you. You\'re welcome!","???","Why does this exclusive set meal in the themed restaurant taste a little familiar?","Are you talking about the mahjong-themed restaurant in the amusement park, nyaa?!","Yeah.","Nyaa! I really want to eat there, but it\'s really hard to get a reservation, nyaa!","You end up paying three times the price for food that tastes the same as a certain fast food chain brand in One Han City. You\'re better off not eating there.","Three times the price... um, I think {name} will end up going bankrupt.","The food doesn\'t taste nice at the restaurant. I\'ve noted that down. We\'ll look into this seriously!","I remember that there really is a chain restaurant on the neighboring island. Considering the location... woof, could the food be directly supplied by the chain store?","Well... business people care more about efficiency and profits, so I can understand.","Do you really think you have the right to say that about others, woof?","It\'s opened in a tourist area, so let\'s not be too harsh on the taste of the food.","Do you think my Luck and Fortune can also...","Stop having such dangerous thoughts!","Thanks for the info. I won\'t go there then.","Oh, you haven\'t eaten there yet? I sent this CatChat message too early. I should have waited until you\'ve also eaten there.","We can enjoy blessings together, but there\'s really no need to endure misfortunes together.","Youngster, you need to experience more hardships to grow up. I\'m doing this for your own good.","Mmm, I\'ve received your postcards from SAMU Joy Island! It seems that everyone is having a really good time there.","Have you received mine yet?","Huh? Did you also send me one? Mmm... maybe it hasn\'t arrived yet.","I didn\'t send you a postcard. I got too many plushies from the claw cranes on the island, and that idiot, {name}, couldn\'t carry all of them, so I gave you some.","You sent me cute plushies? I\'m really looking forward to receiving them. Thanks, Chiori.","They are just some ordinary plushies, so don\'t get your hopes up too high.","Miss Chiori, we just sent it out, so they won\'t reach One Han City until at least the day after tomorrow. Also, the parcel was huge because we stuffed more than ten plushies in it.","Huh?! The commoner\'s delivery service is this slow?","The delivery service on this island really does seem a little slow. Why don\'t we give the remaining plushies to other friends in person after we go back?","Hmph, we\'ll do that then.","Reina, why don\'t we come together when the park opens officially?","But there aren\'t many things that I dare to play at the amusement park... You won\'t have a good time if you go there with me, {name}.","Sometimes it\'s not about what you do at an amusement park but who you go with. I want to go with you, Reina.","Mmm, in that case, please bring me with you next time. I also want to go to the amusement park with you, {name}.","I miss the coffee at Éternité.","Then you must come to Éternité when you get back, {name}. I\'ll make our newest special iced drink for you.","I ordered this so that I wouldn\'t get separated from the children. It works surprisingly well.","If I had known about this earlier, I would have used it with Shaun! Please share the link!","I have the urge to get one for my mom and brother... Does it support air shipping if I order now?","Please share the link.","?","There are more people here than I expected... To ensure Miss Chiori is safe, it\'s better to be safe than sorry!","Hmm? {name}, did you also bring a younger companion with you?","Well, some people are physically young, and some people are mentally young. I have a hunch that this will come in handy on this trip.","Is one enough? If there are lots of people, wouldn\'t you need one for every person you\'re traveling with?","Haha, that\'s why I bought two. After all, {name} is like a child sometimes. I just can\'t stop worrying.","SAMU Joy Island really does bring people joy. An author who announced they would be going on hiatus a few days ago has suddenly resumed updating today... It\'s double the joy with this amusement park and the novel updates.","Oh, I saw that too... That author writes really well... I\'m so happy.","Pfft, did you see her latest status? I never thought something like that would happen.","Yeah... I saw it... Although I feel bad laughing about it... but... I really... couldn\'t hold back...","Tell me too.","The author came to SAMU Joy Island to have fun, but happened to run into her editor at the fairy tale castle. Now she has been locked down inside her hotel room to release updates.","It\'s such a coincidence that both the author and the editor were selected for the soft opening.","Not really. It\'s because SAMU Corporation owns the platform that signed the author, and the editor came here to experience the soft opening as an employee.","That\'s why it\'s even more funny.","Which novel is this?","It\'s called \"After Being Reborn, I Discovered That My Mortal Enemy Was Also Reborn.\" It\'s about the intense tangle of love and desire, with classic scenes of passion emerging from inner turmoil and the tantalizing sounds of bodies entwined.","...The title seems completely unrelated to what you just described.","Simple steps to packing your luggage: Open your suitcase → take out the red pandas → pack your clothes → take out the red pandas → pack your daily necessities → take out the red pandas → pack some snacks → close the suitcase → open the suitcase → take out the red pandas...","If only my herbs would pack themselves like that.","I\'ll help you next time you need to pack your luggage!","I wish I could pack myself into my suitcase too. That way, I\'ll just arrive at my destination when I wake up.","Miss Kisaragi, unattended suitcases are usually sent to the lost and found office instead of their destination.","Wow, I feel like I have gone through the same steps before. Suitcases are so magical!","All I really need to pack is my master (or my master\'s wallet), nyaa!","Hahaha, you\'ve got to bring along that youthful and vibrant energy!","How can you not pack a set of mahjong in your suitcase?","As expected of a famous Jyanshi of One Han City... A just world needs someone like you who stays true to themselves!","My suitcase is still quite empty. Your red pandas can get in my suitcase!","{name}, I don\'t think you\'ve noticed that a member of my Red Panda Squad has been hiding in your suitcase for a long time now...","How can we not take some photos since we\'re at the seaside?","Wow, your meal is extremely healthy today too!","One glance is all I need to tell that this is something only beauties would eat. I can\'t see Cynthia, but she must look absolutely stunning today!","You look so amazing! The sight of a beauty by the sea is unbeatable! (Imagining the scene now)","QAQ When will you share some selfies with us? We miss your dazzling beauty!","What will we do after eating?","Well, we\'re here anyway... so let\'s take a stroll along the beach and walk off our meal.","Alright.","It looks really great, but can we skip the plain healthy meal next time?","You don\'t like it? Of course we can. I\'ll let my assistant know that we\'re not having dinner.","??? That\'s not what I meant!","I bought some beautiful letter paper at the tourist gift shop... I can\'t wait to use them to write letters to my students in One Han City.","You all live in the same city, so why bother sending letters to your students?","Our handwriting often reflects our feelings... It\'s very interesting. You should start developing this habit as well.","I want to receive a letter from you too, Miss Leia.","You\'re a good child. You\'ll receive one when the time is right.","[tag]#KanaFujita\'sTakeawayOrderUserNameIsTheWomanWhoDominatesTheArcade[/tag] What an embarrassing day... Thanks to that dedicated delivery guy, I\'ll definitely pay attention to my text messages and calls next time...","Everyone who saw this trending topic, I\'ll tell you what happened so you can save your data. Kana Fujita was so immersed while playing at the arcade on the island that she didn\'t hear her takeout arrive. The delivery guy stood in the middle of the arcade and shouted her name out loud, lol!","Hahahahahahahaha! I\'m sorry that our idol has embarrassed herself like this. She is really serious about being an idol though!","The woman who dominates the arcade--hahahaha! My dear Kana is really cute!","A moment of gluttony can make someone an introvert for the rest of their life.","You\'re laughing too much! I\'m not bringing you with me the next time I go to the arcade!","What did you order?","Thanks, but don\'t ask. Anyway, my manager already told me off... [Cry] [Cry] [Cry]","Today\'s the last day of our soft opening. Thanks so much for supporting SAMU Joy Island! We can\'t wait to see you again when we open officially! PS: If you have any thoughts or feedback about your experience, we\'d love to hear them!","This was an interesting trip. I\'m looking forward to its official opening.","I\'ll be back as a tourist next time.","One day, the flying duck in the water park broke down and couldn\'t start up. The staff member calmly said that the flying duck was a little tired and would be fine after resting for a while, haha... At that moment, I felt like the rides of the amusement park had come to life! Keep up the good work! I look forward to the official opening!","I can\'t wait to come back!","Thanks for your support! We look forward to your next visit!","Pfft! It\'s this type of official and polite replies that make me think this is an automatic reply.","Keep it up! You can do even better next time!","The survey you submitted will definitely be useful.","Thanks for being so supportive. We\'ll definitely do better next time!","Chapter 1","Chapter 2","Chapter 3","Before starting work, I had the final interview with Fuuka Minami, the boss of Bamboo Cloud. During our conversation, I realized that the job of a temporary secretary is not that easy…","On an auspicious day, deities are invited to the parade.\nThe parade is the most important part of Bamboo Cloud\'s anniversary. However, during the busy preparations, a problem occurred. Shaman A-Yuan\'s ritual failed, and the deities refused the invitation.\nAs the supervisor, it\'s my responsibility to help her. But... who are they?\nIntriguing shaman culture, lively operator successors... Girls on Champion Street took me to investigate the case and unveil the secrets of Fuuka Minami\'s homeland, an ancient and mysterious land.","As promised, I went to my new workplace, the Champion Auction House, to check on the preparations for Bamboo Cloud\'s Annual Charity Auction.\nIncidentally, I witnessed a horrifying scene: a violent robbery was taking place in the auction house!\nAs the only witness, I was entrusted with a heavy responsibility by Fuuka Minami: to solve this case and recover the stolen exhibition piece.\nAfter enduring numerous hardships, we finally found a trace of the culprit.\nLittle did we know, the theft of the priceless jade was just the tip of the iceberg...","Magical Dream, a time-honored teahouse on Champion Street, has been chosen by Fuuka Minami as her new partner in collaboration.\nI arrived at the teahouse to discuss the collaboration details, only to find the boss, Fei Ming, had disappeared, leaving the employee, Yuan Xiao, to handle the provocations from jealous business rivals.\nTo secure the collaboration, I only had to help Magical Dream face its rivals in a tea competition.\nHowever, even though I\'ve seen through Fei Ming\'s tea ceremony, there still seem to be others who covet the trade secret of Bamboo Cloud...","Bamboo Cloud is a gathering of talent. Its boss, Fuuka Minami, is accompanied by the renowned Four Nobles: Plum, Orchid, Bamboo, and Chrysanthemum. As the anniversary celebration draws near, I arrive at the Bamboo Cloud HQ to assist and meet these enigmatic figures. However, strange events begin to occur, seemingly connected to the Four Nobles. What are their true intentions? Will the anniversary celebration proceed as planned?","After all those twists and turns, I managed to keep the preparations for the celebration on track. Now came the day for making progress reports to Fuuka Minami. I arrived at Bamboo Cloud HQ alone and knocked on her office door...","After overcoming numerous obstacles, the Bamboo Cloud anniversary celebration finally takes place smoothly. On this joyous night, I glimpse a different side of Fuuka Minami...","Bamboo Cloud\'s Offer","Overture on the Auspicious Day","Variations on Heart of Divinity","March of Tea Competition","Harmony of the Nobles","Intermezzo of Promise","Hymn to the Year","Minami Ancestral Hall","Champion Auction House","Magical Dream","Bamboo Cloud HQ","You\'re the temporary secretary Ume hired for me? Looks competent.","You\'ll be in charge of supervising the preparations for Bamboo Cloud\'s anniversary celebration.","In other words, you\'ll be a supervisor.","A supervisor... which basically means I\'m a project manager. Now I see. It\'s a job nobody likes.","I agree with you. Why else would we need to hire you at the last minute to replace the previous supervisor who had an \"accident\"?","Why the long face?","Relax! I was just joking. Here at Bamboo Cloud, we won\'t easily let any employees get hurt, since you\'re all precious labor assets to me.","What will I need to do?","Here\'s a list of your tasks. There are four locations you need to go to, and you\'ll need to confirm the progress with the person in charge at each location.","You\'ll need to be both gentle and firm with them.","What do you mean?","It means you\'ll need to push them mercilessly when it looks like they are behind schedule or might not complete their tasks on time.","But at the same time, you\'ll need to be a kind boss who provides timely assistance when they are incapable.","It doesn\'t sound easy...","Management requires both experience and skill. If you want to learn more about it, you can ask our manager Ume.","I understand.","Okay, then you better get to it.","By the way, you should find a chance to meet our accountant Take, who is responsible for handling all your paychecks.","I can\'t wait to see how you\'ll do, my dear new secretary.","Read Chapter 1 in Minami Ancestral Hall to claim it","Read Chapter 3 in Minami Ancestral Hall to claim it","Read Chapter 1 in Champion Auction House to claim it","Read Chapter 3 in Champion Auction House to claim it","Read Chapter 1 in Magical Dream to claim it","Read Chapter 3 in Magical Dream to claim it","Read Chapter 1 in Bamboo Cloud HQ to claim it","Read Chapter 3 in Bamboo Cloud HQ to claim it","Welcome to One Han City","Wherever Your Belief lies, A Stage Will Rise","Pursuing Dream and Original Aspiration","Idols\' Wonderful Adventure","Popularity bonus for the first 2 matches daily: {0}%→{1}%","Popularity bonus for the rank in Ranked Match/Event Match: {0}%→{1}%","Popularity bonus for winning in Ranked Match/Event Match: {0}%→{1}%","Gain a deeper understanding of the trend.","Ensure a cozy space for performance.","Purchase a better wardrobe and dazzling clothing.","Vanity Case","Incense","Fine Tea","Divine Power bonus for wishes and incidents: {0}","Chance to change Failure to Success: {0}%","Fair Stats bonus for wishes and incidents: {0}","E","E+","D","D+","C","C+","B","B+","A","A+","S","S+","SS","SS+","SSS","SSS+","EX","EX+","[Housework Transfer, Nyaa]","Nyaa? I don\'t have to play mahjong to make my wish come true anymore, nyaa? That\'s so convenient, nyaa... In that case, please have Wanjirou and Master take over my shrine cleaning duties this month, nyaa!","Ichihime, look behind you","Ichihime turns to find herself looking into your eyes. In that instant, the air falls into a deadly silence. Snapping back to her senses, she starts to run away, but you\'re too quick for her, successfully catching yourself a temple fair helper! Ichihime ends up running errands for you for the rest of the day. Wanjirou, completely unaware of any of this, sees Ichihime and you working so hard that he volunteers to do all the cleaning work of Mahjong Soul Shrine. Ichihime\'s wish has actually come true!","Ichihime turns to find herself looking into your eyes. In that instant, the air falls into a deadly silence. Snapping back to her senses, she starts to run away. Unfortunately, she slips past you. For the rest of the day, she not only manages to stay out of your sight but also eats a ton of dorayaki to ease her anxiety, carelessly spending lots of your Coppers!","Ichihime, I\'ll spoil you this time","She hasn\'t done anything wrong. You see the heart of the matter and decide not to respond directly to her wish. Instead, you invite Riu Kujou, the cleaning expert, to give advice on how you can optimize the cleaning work of Mahjong Soul Shrine. Ichihime and Wanjirou are really happy with this!","You decide to make Ichihime\'s wish come true, but at the same time, you receive a stern protest from the Wanjirou Conservation Association – why is Wanjirou treated so unfairly? As a result, you juggle managing the temple fair while taking on all the cleaning duties at Mahjong Soul Shrine. By sacrificing yourself and working two jobs, you ensure that Ichihime and Wanjirou enjoy the good life you hoped for.","Fuuka Minami","[Year-End Party Gifts]","To reward the Bamboo Cloud employees for their hard work over the past year, Fuuka Minami has prepared generous year-end gifts. What\'s the best way to distribute them to make the employees happiest?","Give out gift boxes containing various goods","Fuuka Minami\'s year-end gift boxes are a hit! Exquisitely packed and filled with lots of practical goods, they are a delight to the employees. Photos quickly flood CatChat, further elevating Bamboo Cloud\'s reputation as One Han City\'s dream company.","The packaging is so exquisite that the employees are reluctant to throw the gift boxes away, even though they take up a lot of space and serve no other purpose. The boxes just end up gathering dust in the corner, turning this year-end reward into more of a hassle than a perk.","Give out concert tickets","Everyone has their own idol in their heart, but it turns out the employees all admire the same one. At the concert, their singing rises and falls like a massive karaoke session. The idol exclaims, \"Did you pay to come sing for me?\"","When the employees hear they are getting concert tickets, they are unexpectedly thrilled, likely because they can resell these fairly valuable tickets.","[Blind Fortune Teller]","Yuan Feng spotted a blind fortune teller who seemed to be a real guru and had countless supporters at the temple fair. The fortune teller ended up taking a lot of Yuan Feng\'s business, and his supporters even accused Yuan Feng of pretending to be the blind fortune teller to dupe people. What should Yuan Feng do?","Take off the sunglasses","Believing his sunglasses are the problem, Yuan Feng starts serving customers without them, shifting his focus to face and palm readings. Since his services don\'t overlap with the blind fortune teller\'s, and he can also offer advice on getting lucky and avoiding trouble, more and more people are coming to Yuan Feng for their New Year\'s fortunes. As a result, the blind fortune teller\'s supporters have stopped harassing him.","Yuan Feng decides to follow the advice and removes his sunglasses. While this initially appears to help, with his business slowly recovering, his regulars at the temple fair aren\'t convinced. Without his sunglasses, he just doesn\'t have the same vibe...","Test the blind fortune teller","When no one is around, Yuan Feng leaves some Coppers near the blind fortune teller\'s stall. Sure enough, the \"blind\" fortune teller quickly scans his surroundings before grabbing the Coppers at lightning speed and putting them away after a few wipes. Yuan Feng confronts him with the video he recorded, and the fortune teller is sensible enough to leave.","Yuan Feng tries to bait the blind fortune teller, films his every move, and makes faces at him, but he is too cautious. In the end, Yuan Feng fails to confirm his suspicions.","Qi Xi","[Business Cooperation]","With so many tourists here, this is a good opportunity for me to really shine! Qi Xi wants to play matchmaker for the tourists who have come to make wishes at the Snake Palace. Do you agree?","Agree","All kinds of wishes are made during the spring temple fair, many of them related to love and romance. Qi Xi may fulfill a ton of these wishes for Lady Li Yang\'s attendant, strengthening people\'s faith in the Snake Palace\'s ability to grant their wishes.","A piece of advice, \"think twice before making a wish,\" starts spreading through the Snake Palace because people have realized that no matter what wish they make, it always comes true with a romantic twist! After all, having too many love interests can be troublesome too.","Disagree","Knowing that Lady Li Yang wants all the offerings for herself, you figure it\'s safer for Qi Xi to play matchmaker somewhere else and leave the wishes made at the palace to Lady Li Yang. Touched by your thoughtfulness, Qi Xi gives you a charm-filled red envelope. With its blessing, Lady Li Yang\'s attendant now favors you even more.","After being rejected, Qi Xi decides to start a business competition in the simplest way possible – by camping out near the Snake Palace entrance to spot and snatch any potential targets there to make wishes! Qi Xi observes the arrivals gleefully for a long time, only to realize that he\'s so preoccupied with this one location that he has completely neglected all the love wishes being whispered elsewhere.","Hibiki Himekawa","[Special Livestream]","Hibiki Himekawa wants to do a livestreaming event at the Snake Palace during the spring temple fair. Do you agree?","Agree","As a dedicated professional, Hibiki Himekawa meticulously researches everything to ensure her audience has a fantastic experience of the Snake Palace during her livestream. Thanks to the overwhelmingly successful livestream, the Snake Palace has gone viral, leading to a significant increase in offerings. This outcome thoroughly pleases Lady Li Yang\'s attendant, who is delighted with your decision.","Hibiki\'s livestreams have always been very dramatic. To attract more viewers, she interviews Lady Li Yang\'s attendant, grilling her about the Snake Palace\'s splendid achievements in fulfilling wishes for wealth, education, and peace. It isn\'t long before someone reports the livestream for false advertising. Furious, the attendant immediately shuts it down.","Disagree","It\'s the once-a-year spring temple fair, and even hard-working streamers like Hibiki Himekawa deserve a break. You suggest she take some time off work to enjoy the holiday like a regular tourist, and she takes you up on the offer. Even though she\'s not streaming, her fans instantly recognize her, and soon enough, videos of her are popping up online. Turns out, her cute everyday look actually wins over many new fans, making the Snake Palace an even hotter spot for her followers. Now it\'s a win-win for everyone.","After you reject her request, Hibiki Himekawa quickly finds a new location for her special livestream at Mahjong Soul Shrine, thanks to Ichihime\'s consent. With her influence as a popular streamer, the shrine is bustling with visitors once again this year, while the Snake Palace becomes much quieter in comparison...","Anju Suzumiya","[Conflicting Wishes]","Question: If two Jyanshis at the same table both made a wish to Lady Li Yang to make them finish in first place, how will this conflict be resolved?","It depends on whose offering is better","After completing a long, complicated, and difficult calculation, KR-976 decides to give her favorite strawberry milk as the offering for her wish to finish in first place. The pressure of losing the strawberry milk pushes KR-976 to explore the limits of her computing power, making her invincible and securing first place in every game. It seems that her wish came true.","Upon hearing this, KR-976 stares wide-eyed at the strawberry milk in her hands. Warning! A new conflict has emerged! What should she do when the best offering is also her favorite food? KR-976 is embroiled in a new conflict!","Establish detailed and meticulous rules","The most points, the most Dora, the most Riichi, and the most deal-ins... After entering this data in the adjustment program provided by Lady Li Yang, KR-976 discovers the following: The conflict has been resolved. The wishes have been fulfilled and everyone should be happy because each Jyanshi has finished in first place in one way or another.","Detailed rules were established to address everyone\'s concerns, but they ended up exceeding the text input limit. You have to rewrite them using cryptic icons and codes, which causes Lady Li Yang to crash again.","Zechs","[A Hunter\'s Decision]","In the new year, I want to become even stronger, both in swordsmanship and mahjong! Hey! I just realized I haven\'t decided on which aspect I should be focusing on yet!","This year is a good year for focusing on honing your offensive skills","As they say, offense is the best defense, so you suggest that Zechs specialize in attack training. As a result, Zechs manages to learn a new skill – [Super Serious Finisher]! Both his critical hit rate and points won in matches have increased significantly!","Zechs already has powerful attack skills, whereas his defense is now his weakness. For example, others can intercept him when he is setting up a big hand in mahjong... He\'ll be in trouble when he faces an opponent who is good at thinking on their feet...","This year is a good year for focusing on your defense","By going all-in on dodging and patiently waiting, even if your attacks hit like a wet noodle, you will eventually wear down the opponent. This is true both on the battlefield and at the mahjong table, so you suggest that he specialize in defensive training. As a result, Zechs manages to learn a new skill – [Become Untargetable]! His ability to avoid dealing in and his winning speed have increased significantly!","Zechs works hard on his defense but neglects his attack training because he is convinced that he can\'t be defeated. His duels fizzle out, and almost every mahjong game he plays ends in a draw...","[Spring Cleaning]","Riu Kujou always ends up with a lot of old skirts that Miss Chiori no longer wears after finishing spring cleaning. It\'s a waste to throw them away, but also a waste of space to keep them. What should she do with them?","Donate them to people who need them","After discussing this with Chiori Mikami, Riu Kujou donates the old skirts. Although it takes some effort, the thought of being able to help others fills her with happiness, and Miss Chiori also feels proud about it.","Chiori Mikami is sad to hear that Riu Kujou has donated her old skirts because they are mementos of her time with Riu Kujou. Regretting the decision, Riu Kujou decides to never trust Lady Li Yang again. From now on, she will just discuss everything with Miss Chiori.","Keep whatever you can","Riu Kujou decides to keep the old skirts and finds a new place to store them. While going through them, she recalls the times when Chiori Mikami wore these skirts, and she ends up having a wonderful time reliving these beautiful memories.","Riu Kujou keeps the old skirts, but as a perfect maid, she insists on having everything perfectly stored in the house she maintains. So she spends all her time every day sorting clothes, until one day, after dealing with more and more old skirts, she realizes that although the house is big enough for everything, she is but one person. The day will come when she won\'t be able to do everything that needs to be done...","Ju","[Interesting Night]","Ju thinks a normal temple fair is too boring and suggests that you invite him to perform something interesting for Lady Li Yang.","Show me just how interesting it can be","Ju tells you to look forward to tomorrow. Recalling some of his past pranks, you decide to take the initiative and announce in advance that Gemini will be performing for everyone tomorrow. Ju laughs and applauds upon hearing your announcement. On the next day, he keeps his word, delivering a wonderful clown show with his troupe for the tourists. Before leaving, Ju thanks you for making him, a clown who entertains others, feel like he\'s having fun too. He looks forward to interacting with you again.","Ju laughs and applauds because he likes people like you who have the courage to do things differently. He tells you to look forward to tomorrow. On the next day, you are on edge the whole time because anything that happens at the temple fair could be one of Ju\'s pranks. Your heightened alertness makes you appear like an adorable fool who can be teased to Lady Li Yang\'s attendant. When you see her smiling at you, it dawns on you that the interesting thing Ju arranged... is actually you.","Maybe not","Recalling Ju\'s idea of \"interesting\" in the recent Bamboo Cloud celebrations, you reject his suggestion out of rationality. As a result, you spend a seemingly quiet and peaceful night. However, when you go out the next day, you find that all the shops have blacklisted Ju. You have no clue what happened, but Ju seems to be in a much better mood than yesterday on the phone.","Recalling Ju\'s idea of \"interesting\" in the recent Bamboo Cloud celebrations, you reject his suggestion out of rationality. As a result, you spend a seemingly quiet and peaceful night. However, when you go out the next day, you find that all the shops have blacklisted you. You have no clue what happened, but soon find yourself surrounded by shopkeepers. It looks like you\'re in trouble.","Yuan Xiao","[Spring Holiday]","Fei Ming generously gives Yuan Xiao a month off for the Spring Festival, and she and Huo Guo both express their wish to celebrate with you. But since you\'ll be working at the Snake Palace throughout the holiday...","Invite them to have their holiday in the Snake Palace","The mount of an ancient war god actually resides in One Han City? Lady Li Yang\'s attendant is surprisingly respectful of Huo Guo and agrees readily to your suggestion. Huo Guo has a wonderful time at the Snake Palace, eating and playing to its heart\'s content. Meanwhile, Lady Li Yang\'s attendant and Yuan Xiao manage to invent a mahjong solitaire game and enjoy themselves.","More and more people come to make wishes at the Snake Palace, but they seem to all be there to see Huo Guo. Scared by their fervent enthusiasm, Huo Guo uses the skills it learned from Yuan Xiao to climb up the palace walls every day. In the end, you\'re the unlucky one who has to chase after it.","Sorry, we won\'t be able to celebrate the holiday together","After learning why you can\'t celebrate the holiday together, Yuan Xiao feels sorry for you having to work during this time and decides to help you with your tasks at the Snake Palace. Thanks to her, you\'re able to clock out two hours early every day, allowing you to keep your promise of having a feast with Yuan Xiao and Huo Guo.","After regretfully bidding you farewell, Yuan Xiao fills her holiday with shopping trips alongside Hua Yuqing, writing food reviews with A-Yuan, and busily making new friends. Your overtime feels even more torturous as you see the happy, festive photos she keeps posting...","Hannah","[Thoughts and Craftsmanship]","It\'s the Shpring Festival again, and I want to make shome embroideries for my friendsh, but I\'m worried they won\'t look good...","It\'s the thought that counts","Hannah takes your advice. Although her creations aren\'t as good as the handicrafts sold in the market, her friends are overjoyed to receive her uniquely designed gifts.","Her friends are happy about receiving the gifts but are a little confused by the elephant embroidered on them because it\'s clearly the Year of the Snake. Hannah is hit hard by this...","Use some Divine Power to make the embroidery look more exquisite","Hannah\'s endless embroidery inspiration is only limited by her skills. When Lady Li Yang\'s attendant uses her powers to smooth out the embroidery lines, Hannah\'s ideas come to life one after another. Her friends are all blown away by her design talent when they receive their gifts.","Thanks to Lady Li Yang\'s attendant, Hannah\'s embroidery looks too good to be true. So, when her friends get their gifts, they automatically assume she bought them and ask where she got them. This really bums Hannah out because nobody thinks she\'s the one who made them.","[Festival Tea Time]","During the Spring Festival, as people visit family and friends, more customers are coming to Magical Dream for a pleasant tea time. This should have been a good thing, but some customers are saying they can\'t sleep after drinking the tea, and Fei Ming seems very troubled by this.","Serve juice to those who can\'t drink tea","To celebrate the holiday, Magical Dream introduces a family combo that includes both juice and tea, allowing tea drinkers and their friends who don\'t usually drink tea to gather, chat, and enjoy the festival\'s warmth together at the tea house. Magical Dream\'s popularity sees a significant boost afterward.","The juice at Magical Dream surprisingly becomes a big hit, with customers flocking to take photos and post them online. However, as the juice sales soar, tea orders begin to dwindle, leaving the tea house in a bit of an unexpected twist regarding its main offerings.","Add a reminder that drinking tea may cause insomnia","In a thoughtful move, Fei Ming puts up a board clearly marking the insomnia levels of each type of tea available at the tea house to assist customers in their selection. Now, customers don\'t have to worry about being kept awake at night by overly strong tea.","While Yuan Xiao is on holiday, the new part-time staff member marks the insomnia level ten times higher for each tea after consulting the wrong information. For a while, people are deterred from visiting Magical Dream, leading to a significant downturn in business.","Chiori Mikami","[Time Magic]","I\'m only trying this because Riu said it works and insisted on coming. I won\'t blame you if you can\'t make the Spring Festival holiday longer, but if you can... Here, Riu waited in line for hours to get these roast ducks, so make sure you eat every last bit of them!","Extend the time spent together","Out of the blue, a heavy snowstorm hits One Han City, delaying Chiori Mikami\'s parents\' flight so that she can spend two more days with them. They spend the time joyfully, building snowmen, having snowball fights, and visiting the temple fair. Those are wonderful memories for her.","Out of the blue, a heavy snowstorm hits One Han City, delaying Chiori Mikami\'s parents\' flight by two days. Chiori Mikami can tell her parents are stressed because they can\'t get back to work, and she feels bad about the wish she made at the Snake Palace.","Cherish the time spent together","Even if the family reunion cannot be extended, their time together can still be more meaningful. Chiori Mikami is determined to make the most of her time with her parents. They visit the temple fair, take lots of photos to capture these moments, and make a wish at the Snake Palace. Every second they spend together feels significant.","Chiori Mikami goes all out trying to plan the perfect trip for her parents, but she starts stressing too much because it feels like this has to be absolutely flawless. She ends up asking Riu Kujou to handle it. Even though she has a blast on the trip, she still feels a little bad about giving up on the planning.","Sawako Kitami","[Reunion Dinner]","While out shopping for holiday goods, Sawako Kitami\'s child mentions that his friend\'s family will be having their reunion dinner at a restaurant this year. Sawako is a bit hesitant. Should her family have their dinner at a restaurant too?","Reunion dinner should be eaten at home","Sawako Kitami thinks that the reunion dinner is about having all family members gathered around the dining table, chatting about memorable events from the past year, and enjoying a meal filled with love. Sure enough, this year\'s reunion dinner is as delicious as ever.","Just like in previous years, Sawako Kitami and her family enjoy a delicious reunion dinner together, but after the big meal, the kitchen turns into a disaster zone of pots and pans. Once the cleanup is done, she sighs to herself: \"The cooking part isn\'t hard – but the dishwashing part always is!\"","Try having it at a restaurant","The new year is a time for new experiences and surprises. Sawako Kitami creates just such a surprise for her child by taking him to a restaurant for the reunion dinner. He is overjoyed to bump into his friends there! Seeing his happy smile makes her even more excited for the year ahead.","Most restaurants in One Han City are fully booked on that night. When Sawako Kitami finally finds one with availability, she discovers that all the dishes are precooked and far inferior to what she can make herself. This experience quickly dampens her family\'s holiday enthusiasm.","Fu Ji","[Customer Promotion]","With the holiday approaching, Fu Ji plans to launch a promotion at Luck and Fortune. However, she\'s unsure about what kind of events to organize.","Discounts for lucky new customers","The discount promotion, with its generous offers, proves a hit as happy regulars eagerly bring in new customers. The new customers are exceptionally lucky, winning with big hands like Blessing of Heaven and Blessing of Earth. Business at Luck and Fortune is thriving, and Fu Ji also shares this blessing with the Snake Palace.","The discount promotion, with its generous offers, proves a hit as happy regulars eagerly bring in new customers. However, Luck and Fortune has also received some negative reviews. Some Jyanshis have complained that the promotion ads are everywhere, causing them to miss information about the Happy Friday discounts.","Entrance fee exemption for those who win with a big hand","Any Jyanshi who wins with a Haneman or bigger hand in Luck and Fortune will have their fee waived! This is an unprecedented promotion in the history of Luck and Fortune, and the business is so brisk that it\'s bursting at the seams!","Any Jyanshi who wins with a Haneman or bigger hand in Luck and Fortune will have their fee waived! This is an unprecedented promotion in the history of Luck and Fortune! However, the smile on Fu Ji\'s face sends shivers down the customers\' spines, as if they might pay a terrible price for taking advantage of her offer... As a result, despite this incredible deal, Luck and Fortune is nearly dead quiet during the holiday.","Hua Yuqing","[Rock Opera]","Hua Yuqing plans to surprise the audience by combining traditional opera and rock music in Thunderclap\'s Spring Festival performance. She has prepared two different versions. Which one should she use?","Opera complemented by rock music","Hua Yuqing sings valiantly and moves with agility in the costume of a female warrior, earning enthusiastic applause from the audience. As the song reaches its climax, she electrifies the atmosphere with rock music, causing the audience to dance while shedding tears and shouting: \"A new era has come! Rock and roll will never die!\"","Hua Yuqing sings valiantly and moves with agility in the costume of a female warrior, but the audience starts to look at each other, wondering if they\'ve gone to the wrong concert as they thought they had come to listen to rock music.","Rock music complemented by opera","Singing classic rock hits, Hua Yuqing has the crowd headbanging in unison. Right after the chorus, caught up in the moment, she delivers her best solo opera performance. The fans are enthralled; this blend of the traditional and the contemporary is so ON FIRE!","Singing classic rock hits, Hua Yuqing has the crowd headbanging in unison. Right after the chorus, caught up in the moment, she performs one of her favorite opera pieces. The fans exchange confused glances as the atmosphere dies down.","Hua Yubai","[Way of Management]","Hua Yubai has always been strict with the members of Floating Dreams, but it\'s understandable that they would want to relax for a few days during the Spring Festival. Does Lady Li Yang have any management advice for her?","Train on the hottest days during summer and the coldest days in winter","A few minutes of glory on stage often comes from more than ten years of hard work behind the scenes. Even during the holiday, Hua Yubai insists that Floating Dreams remain committed to their training. When one dedicated member shares a short video of their intense practice on CatChat, it unexpectedly goes viral, sparking interest and giving many a newfound appreciation for the dedication behind opera.","A few minutes of glory on stage often comes from more than ten years of hard work behind the scenes. Even during the holiday, Hua Yubai insists that Floating Dreams remain committed to their training. However, even the strictest rules can restrain a heart that yearns for freedom, so their training isn\'t very effective.","Having a good balance between work and rest is the way to go","Hua Yubai believes that the troupe\'s management philosophy should evolve with the times. The members of Floating Dreams have worked hard for a year, so they should relax during the Spring Festival. Sure enough, the troupe members come back with more energy and spirit after the holiday.","Hua Yubai believes that the troupe\'s management philosophy should evolve with the times. The members of Floating Dreams have worked hard for a year, so they should relax during the Spring Festival. However, it\'s quite obvious to everyone, even including the audience, that many of them have gotten rusty after their time off.","???","[Farewell at the Snake Palace]","Time sure flies. This year\'s temple fair is near the end. You have received your reward, I trust? Though the local customs here are indeed special and unique, it is time for me to leave and explore other corners of this vast world.","Farewell. I\'ll never forget about you","On your last night together, it suddenly hits you – you\'re both so busy preparing for the ritual that you haven\'t had a chance to just experience the temple fair yourselves. Now, walking through the bustling fair and seeing her genuine enjoyment of the food you recommend, you can\'t help but think how much she has changed. She\'s definitely no longer the proud and unapproachable person you first met... Her pace picks up, and as you hurry to keep up, it seems like her figure is changing a little...","Come back and visit when you miss us","Respected Village Chief","For the past few years, a severe drought has plagued the land every spring, cracking the land and making it impossible to plant our crops. We desperately need your help, Lady Li Yang!","Bless them with a heavy rain when spring starts","Bestow them with drought-resistant seeds","How Did You Know My Child Is the Top Student?","Sigh... If only my child\'s mahjong skills could be as good as his grades.","You can\'t have your cake and eat it too","Learning Skill PT -2","I\'m Already a Mature Elementary School Student","I don\'t really have any wishes to fulfill, but... if I have to make a wish, then can your attendant play with us at the spring temple fair tomorrow night?","She is very busy","Who can say no to a fun time","I Love Money","It\'s been absolutely freezing lately, and with the end of the year coming, I\'m so broke that I can\'t even afford warm clothes or a mahjong set. Could you spare a thought for me?","Bestow some winter clothes","Bestow a mahjong set","Mahjong Forever","The Snake Cup Mahjong Competition is starting soon. I sincerely invite Lady Li Yang to join us and witness the best of the best battle it out!","Increase the prize pool","Just check it out","I Love My Family","Please bless my family with peace and good health in the new year! By the way, what kind of offering should I prepare?","Your sincere heart is all that\'s needed","This roast chicken will do","Blessings of Heaven and Earth, Let Me Win Big","I\'m competing in the mahjong competition soon. Please send some extra good luck my way while I\'m playing!","Okay, but remember luck has to come from somewhere","No, dealing into others is just another form of charity","Coach, I Want to Play Games","Lady Li Yang! Please grant me a swift fortune! A modest 100,000 Coppers is all I need to finally get that new game console I\'ve been dreaming of!","Okay, I\'ll give you 200,000 Coppers","No, earn that money yourself","Weak, Pitiful, and Powerless","I hope I can stop finishing in fourth place in the new year...","Try playing three-player mahjong","Have some roast duck","Time to Get Some Fries from the Pier","I\'ve made many mistakes in my life... Please, Lady Li Yang, can you tell me what I should do? What is the meaning of life?","Do more good deeds in the future","You should do what your nickname suggests","Money\'s All I Have","I\'m thinking of investing in several industries. Do you have any recommendations?","Local cuisine","A mahjong-themed culture street","Don\'t Hit a Smiling Face","O great and powerful Lady Li Yang, long have I heard of your incredible, boundless, and omnipotent powers...","I won\'t hesitate to hit a smiling face talking in riddles","Keep the praising going for ten more minutes – I\'d like to hear more","I\'ll Protect the Snake Palace","I\'ve found a thief who had the gall to steal the offerings to Lady Li Yang! What should I do with the thief?","Make sure the thief pays tenfold","Ask the thief why they did it","Your Lady Is Gracious and Kind","I\'m here to thank Lady Li Yang for making my wish come true! What can I do for you?","Offer me roast duck","Offer me milk tea","Normal Passerby Working at Bamboo Cloud","The year-end party is almost here, and I heard Ms. Minami has prepared abundant prizes for us. I\'ve always had terrible luck... Please make me win the grand prize!","Let everyone choose their own prize instead of having a prize draw","Luck +2","Keep the Promotions ON","I\'ve opened a new mahjong dojo that has good transport connections and reasonable prices. Please help me promote it!","Okay, but it won\'t be for free","Unsubscribe","Guardian of the Snake Palace","It won\'t be safe when we set off firecrackers because they\'ll fill the palace with smoke. What should we do?","A slight use of Divine Power will suffice","To be on the safe side, let\'s not light any firecrackers","Make a Wish under the Wishing Tree","The wishing trees in the palace are already filled with wishes. There\'s no room to hang new ones...","Use the Divine Power to make the tree grow taller","Trees\' lives matter too. Hang wishes in the corridor from now on","Master Chef","Lady Li Yang, your attendant will also be attending tomorrow\'s feast. What dishes should we make?","Dishes that she likes","Dishes that everyone likes","Ten Games, Nine Deal-Ins","I\'ve always felt inferior to others since I was a child because I suck at playing mahjong. Please give me some advice...","Play with people at the same level as you","Dealing in helps you grow up","Under the Tutelage of the One and Only Miki","I don\'t know why my snacks never sell. Please, Lady Li Yang, help my business thrive!","Maybe you should find a new teacher...","Exhaust the Divine Power to make them taste good","I\'m Not Three Anymore","I\'m Fu Fu, and it\'s my birthday today. Can you wish me a happy birthday?","Happy fourth birthday to you!","Happy birthday, Fu Fu!","Drawing Is All about Luck","In the new year, I hope for an Ippatsu every time I call Riichi, Ura Doras in abundance, and to only deal into small hands! Please give me your blessing, Lady Li Yang!","Okay, but the blessing will work on your mahjong buddies too","No, relying on luck in mahjong isn\'t going to get you anywhere","Please Give Your Servant Clear Guidance","The reception is already packed with people, but expanding it will infringe on your dining space...","Lady Li Yang takes priority","Expand the reception","Please give us your blessing, Lady Li Yang! Please make our village a wonderful hotspot of mahjong talent!",