 kick this ship into high gear, woof! Full speed ahead!","You hear the roar of those waves? My fighting spirit is rising right along with them.","I\'ll handle everyone\'s safety. There\'s nothing this cannon can\'t solve.","Suspicious target spotted in the distance... Taking aim... Fire!","Sailing the high seas just isn\'t right without a good beer... wait, no. Is it supposed to be rum?","It doesn\'t matter how rough the sea gets. I guarantee I\'ll hit my mark.","Vitamin C is critical at sea... so I\'m making this grilled fish with orange sauce.","Staring at a fixed object alleviates seasickness. You\'re my reference point, senpai.","The view is nice... and you look... Hmm. It\'s interesting, watching you try to keep your balance.","...It would be really fascinating if we got to see a waterspout out here. They\'re supposed to be super rare.","Knowing your direction is crucial on the ocean. The first step is always to find the position of the sun and the stars...","Hehe. Not bad. It seems my offering is nearly within reach.","I am growing weary. Come, accompany me to my cabin for a brief rest.","While I could simply walk upon the waves with my divine power, this leisurely cruise is... not without its charms.","Is that... the scent of grilled fish? Well, present my offering at once.","To discern a distant object with the naked eye upon the open sea... it is rather difficult, I must admit.","Anyone ready for an adventure?","Setting sail now? Are you on the hunt for that legendary treasure?","Wow! Treasure?! Is there gonna be a treasure hunt squad? Raising hand violently!!!","Yup, rumor has it... Someone found a treasure map near Mahjong Soul Shrine, and according to that map, the legendary treasure is buried in the waters near One Han City.","I want to see the view from the tippy-top of the mast, nyaa! Signing up RIGHT NYAA!!!","LOL, shorty and shouty? How eager.","Just keep throwing shade, you floppy ears. And enjoy your zero treasure, nyaa.","Hold up – a treasure map that just POPS up? That\'s WAY too coincidental... Smells like a prank OR trap! [tag]#DetectiveModeActivated[/tag]","IDC if it\'s a trap, just imagine the loot!! Sign me up! If we bag a big one, we\'re set for life!","Zero details? Crew size? Requirements? PAY?! This poster\'s a joke!","Shouldn\'t you be handling such trifles for me?","We\'re setting sail today, and you\'re only just starting to recruit the crew?!","That\'s right. Tick-tock, you better help me pick my crew extra fast!","Ready to go.","Yui, don\'t forget to test my Explosive Antimatter Fishing Machine. I\'m counting on you for all the data for my thesis next semester.","Please, please, please!","Okay.","Umm... is this really safe? The name alone sounds kinda dangerous...","DAWN OF ANOTHER WORLD, SHINE BEFORE MY FLAWLESS PREPARATIONS!","If the ship hits light speed, then there\'s a chance theoretically.","Fuyumi didn\'t show up to roast her big bro today.","Guess she finally gave up.","So many suitcases! Let me help you out.","Carrying it together drastically cuts energy consumption... Clever as always.","What do you have in these suitcases?","That\'s... classified, for now.","Super special shiny summer smasher 5S fried noodles, slow-braised beef tongue tacos with tomato sauce, crispy crunchy fried chicken, mushroom & braised pork calzones, caramel cinnamon apple tarts... I\'ll buy you all once I get the treasure, nyaa!","Where\'s the \"soaring into the heavens\" dango? You were totally hyped for that last time.","Ugh, nyaa... I\'m officially DONE with your food recommendations, nyaa...","Mai will take good care of Mahjong Soul Shrine. You can count on me!","Awesome, nyaa! Then I\'ll leave everything except for that stupid rabbit to you, nyaa!","Yeesh, we haven\'t even left yet, and Ichihime\'s already got the treasure all spent in her head, woof...","Gotta plan how to use the treasure first for MAX motivation, nyaa!","Noooo, anything but MUSHROOM...","I\'ve never been out to sea before... already feeling the jitters, NGL... BUT! For the sake of becoming a true elegant lady, I\'ll do my best to hunt that treasure down!","Not 100% sure we\'ll find the treasure yet...","Nyaa, nyaa, nyaa?! Don\'t crush my grand buffet fantasy, nyaa!","Forget the treasure. I can get these for you right now.","Nope, nyaa! I\'m gonna find the treasure so I can spoil BOTH of us, nyaa!","Terrific weapon.","Only the finest offerings for me.","THIS is an offering, nyaa?","Paws crossed it will never be used, woof...","Yes.","WHY is there something this dangerous on the ship?!","Our route passes through a few pirate-infested waters... y\'know, just in case.","PIRATES?! Can I still jump ship?!","I hereby declare Nadeshiko the new Pirate Queen!","Guess I gotta level up... or I can\'t protect you when it counts.","This is the most insanely detailed gun replica I\'ve ever seen.","And {name} is the most innocent Jyanshi I\'ve ever met.","Sweet red bean as base and yuzu zest for fragrance, finished with a sprinkle of gold leaf to evoke a starlit night sky...","Behold – the voyage-limited mocktail! GENIUS! This is straight-up art! Now all it needs is a killer name! [tag]#MixilogyArt[/tag]","Need a name? How about Diesel R35?","Red Bean Yuzu Juice!","Keep it simple – just call it Sweet Red Wine.","Haha... I appreciate the passion, everyone! But I\'ve got a spicy candidate – how about Obsidian Impact?!","My hunter instincts are protesting that a red bean drink shouldn\'t have a goth name...!","Constructive input, Ein! Then the drink shall now be named Scarlet Impact!","What about Bloody Velvet?","Exquisite & romantic, love it! Want to be the first brave soul to taste-test?","Its name shall be... Fallen Angel\'s Scarlet Sigil: EXTREME!","Now THAT\'S a name! Didn\'t expect you to have this level of taste! Future R&D is all yours now!","Anyone know how to fix the ship\'s wheel? Super urgent! [tag]#SOS[/tag]","The wheel is – DEAD – NYAAA!","Ahem so... my ninjutsu training may have caused a slight Kunai vs Wheel collision. And by \"slight,\" I mean this little disaster.","Island ahead! Fix the wheel ASAP, or there\'s gonna be another COLLISION, nyaa!!","Call the repair guy.","I was thinking the same thing, but... what repair guy?","Kunai?! HOW did you even pass security?!","Let\'s... just focus on the emergency.","NOOOO! I don\'t want to sink like a stone!!!","Just chill, Master. I packed two sets of water-walking ninja gear in my luggage – ZERO drowning allowed!","Worry not, nothing bad will happen while I\'m here. Though... your panicked face looks pretty appetizing.","Who\'s up for some swimming with me?","Cool as a cucumber mid-crisis – as expected of my Master!","Pro tip: Eating ramen mid-storm = bad life choice. I almost became HOT DOG, woof.","Looks pretty risky... I suggest switching from ramen to grilled fish instead.","Breakfast: Sashimi + Takoyaki + Marinated Fish. Lunch: Salt-Grilled Fish + Braised Fish + Sweet&Sour Fish. Dinner: Steamed Fish + Boiled Fish + Fish Head Stew... Even my dog soul is fish-ified now, woof. [tag]#FishOverdose[/tag]","Ramen, nyaa! Any left in the kitchen? My stomach is still roaring, nyaa.","You care more about RAMEN than your almost-scalded comrade, woof?!","Nyaa... So... is the ramen that almost scalded you still there?","Genius move: Fried rice over ramen!","But fried rice and ramen have totally different charms, woof.","Not a good idea to eat on stormy seas...","A steaming fresh bowl of ramen is biologically impossible to resist, woof!","Yellow Tea seems a bit low on energy today.","Is Yellow Tea okay...? Don\'t worry! Kind soul told me there\'s a school nurse sailing with us!","[tag]@Ayane Kisaragi[/tag] We\'re counting on you, Ms. Kisaragi!","While the idea might seem similar, leave pet care to the pros. I can hook Qing Luan up with a reliable pet doc.","Thanks, but Yellow Tea will be fine – it\'s just feeling a bit seasick.","Birds get seasick too? Uh-oh... the deck really is wobbling... Gotta check on Huo Guo!","Pretty sure Yellow Tea\'s just dizzy from that swirly cabin flooring. Who approved these hypnotic spiral tiles?","Swirly tiles? This ship\'s flooring is 100% straight lines...","Perhaps you could use some rest too.","And you? Feeling alright?","Thanks for your concern, I\'m doing well.","If you\'re not feeling well at any point, please don\'t hesitate to let me know. I\'d be glad to help in any way I can.","I heard that acupuncture can help with seasickness...","The moment I took out the needles, Yellow Tea immediately flew off. Could this folk remedy actually work?","Mmm... Why does every catch turn out to be so weird? Guess fishing like this isn\'t my jam... I\'m gonna dive in and grab them barehanded!","So the conclusion is, direct flesh-to-fin contact is non-negotiable.","As expected of a well-read lady... Your words are next-level profound!","Not bad for a newbie... At least there\'s something in your basket. Maybe upgrade your bait?","Bait? What is that? You mean I can\'t just yeet the line and wait for the fish?","I\'ll join you for some barehanded fishing next time.","Thanks! With paw-powered smackdowns, no fish stands a chance before us!","No fish caught, but you just deep-cleaned the ocean!","Oh... OH?! Is that so? Time to double down on the effort...!","It\'s confirmed! I\'ve tried it myself (many, many times), and lychee with wasabi and soy sauce actually tastes like salmon. Don\'t knock it \'til you try it!","Oh, big reminder! DO NOT mix milk & grapes! Trust me, a surprise tummy ache at the worst moment is NOT what you want!","How did you find out?","Just basic hunter knowledge! Totally unrelated to that tiny little mishap at my workplace, promise! Lol...","Hohoho... Watch out for food combos! Harmless foods can become TOXIC when combined. [tag]#ClassicMO[/tag]","Hyped to try!","Knew you\'d say that. Got everything ready for you.","Maybe, but nothing beats the taste of real salmon...","Oops, the sample for comparison just vanished into my stomach! No biggie though, I\'ll go catch another one ASAP!","Lost in a sunny haze... nearly missed something important.","Sunbathing feels purr-fect, nyaa... I\'m signing off for a catnap, nyaa...","Hehe, snooze on the crow\'s nest and wave goodbye to that treasure!","Can\'t have that! Gotta get my game face on, nyaa!","...UV radiation can penetrate your eyelids and damage eye structures such as cornea, lens, and retina.","But Lady Li Yang\'s eyesight can\'t possibly get any worse... right?","Still able to read CatChat replies.","\"Something important\"... You mean having lunch?","To be precise, having lunch with you, {name}.","Feeling a bit drowsy too...","Hehe... A snake would never pass up unwary prey...","It might deserve a spot in One Han City\'s top 3 desserts... might.","So good that someone forgot to wipe their messy face!","No need to be so indirect. Just come over here and wipe it for me – I\'m not going to stop you.","You\'re actually sharing your preferences?","I don\'t even know where to start with you. Now guess why you\'re the only one replying to this.","[tag]#2025WINMidsummerTour[/tag] The W.I.N concert presale starts TONIGHT!\nGet ready to test your speed and luck, everyone!\nStars Align, City Rocks. Join us for an unforgettable night of music and make this summer\'s most amazing memories!\nAll ticket info & the official link here→\n[tag]2025 W.I.N Midsummer Tour Official Website[/tag]","OMG, One Han City\'s e-rations finally got approved!!! I practically levitated out of bed.","WORK CAN WAIT – TICKET DROP EMERGENCY! (screeches) (twists into an unnatural shape) (thrashes on the floor) (growls demonically) (regresses to ape form) (snatches a banana) (swings from a vine) (unleashes a primal roar)","[tag]#2025WINMidsummerTour[/tag] Go W.I.N! May your spotlight never fade. Keep shining bright and bringing us joy! →[tag]2025 W.I.N Midsummer Tour Official Website[/tag]","Have a good think about why you failed to snag the top comment!","Is there a surprise song segment this time?! I\'m dying to hear \"Rainbow Light\" again! Like & forward to get me seen, fam!","Please... just this once... Let me win the ticket war...","OMG IT\'S YOU! The ultimate ticket warrior who never wins but never quits!","Daily self-reflection: Why am I OBSESSED with Kana? Why is Mia so PERFECT? And how did Akane steal my SOUL?!","Am I the only one who can\'t open the link...","Please let the ship drift into somewhere with a good signal when tickets drop...","I\'m rooting for you all! May the ticket gods bless everyone with the seats of their dreams!","Just so you know, there\'s more than one way to get tickets. Smart cookies are already sliding into Mia\'s DMs with their best travel selfies!","You can do it.","WHO among you mortals got the holy TRIPLE REPLY from my girls... Jealousy.exe has been initialized. [tag]#GreenWithEnvy[/tag]","Relax, you\'ll definitely get a ticket! I just know it!","Petition to have W.I.N host their next concert on a cruise ship!","Genius idea, I love it! I\'m sending this to our manager right now!","Confess, are you really interested in the concert, or is this just an excuse to spend more time with Mia?","Proposal accepted.","There you are again! The chosen one who gets all the replies every single time!!!","[tag]@W.I.N Studio[/tag] Y\'all got the next concert\'s theme & venue – now MAKE IT HAPPEN!","[tag]@W.I.N Studio[/tag] SECONDED!","[tag]@W.I.N Studio[/tag] 1000% AGREED!","O Lady of the Snake Palace, bless this poor soul – ward off my cosmic bad luck and manifest that GOD-TIER pull in Sky-High Ambition!\nP.S. Only managed to scrape together enough for a small fruit offering, plz don\'t judge! [tag]#BrokeButDevoted[/tag]","No words, just this DM\'d screenshot of Universal Pull+.","No words, just this DM\'d screenshot of Ling - Galaxy Hacker+.","No words, just this DM\'d screenshot of Kaavi - The Enchanter+.","No words, just this DM\'d screenshot of Moonlight Aegis+.","Let\'s throw down! Loser shaves their tail clean.","Hmph...","So people actually wish for stuff like that...","Because this BAD LUCK is CRUSHING ME!","No words, just this DM\'d screenshot of Ransei - Shadow Clone+.","Even YOU?! Is it just ME who can\'t pull it?","After the passion... only emptiness remains.","Felt that in my soul... The butterflies fade, texts get shorter... Guess that\'s the \"meh\" phase of a relationship.","...I\'m talking about the emptiness that hits halfway through the voyage.","I remember you brought a library aboard, finished them all already?","Yup. Got one book you\'ll love – I\'ll drop it off when we dock in One Han City.","Algorithms know me too well. Slide into my DMs if you\'re bored!","So much to do on a long voyage! You can go fishing, belt out some tunes, surf in the pool (if your ship has one), feast like royalty, and just live for those golden sunsets...","Ughhh... *crying in cram class* Could\'ve been sailing with y\'all!","Thanks for the tips, but been there and done that many times already.","You\'re literally living in my dream!!","Up for a game of Sky-High Ambition?","Is that the new board game? Since it\'s my first time... I\'m putting myself in your hands, {name}.","Same here, been zoning out hard.","Omw to share the void with you. Two is better than one, after all.","1 root Ginseng, 5g Grouper Roe, 10g Mullet Gizzard\n3 tbsp Channelled Wrack Powder, 5 Shiitake Mushrooms, 6 Goji Berries\n1 packet Dried Chili Peppers, Licorice to taste, Turmeric to taste\nJujube Seeds to taste, 2 Bell Peppers, 10g Chives","...Oh no. Didn\'t mean to post this.","Alright detectives, let\'s decode Yui\'s cryptic recipe together.","100% black magic potion.","A lot of these ingredients are pretty obscure. Is this some kind of traditional medicine or something?","Shouldn\'t medicine be precise? All this \"to taste\" is making me nervous, woof.","This is my recipe for homemade curry.","...Huh?","So where\'s the actual curry powder in this \"curry\" recipe?","LOL, Yui\'s wild creativity strikes again. With all 