y next big adventure? It\'s that call of the wild, that freedom just inherent in a man\'s spirit, you know! [tag]#BrotherhoodOfTheWild[/tag]","I\'d love some stargazing too.","No problem, I\'ll come pick you up. Evening breeze is a bit chilly, so remember to bring a jacket, alright?","Careful, being creative this late can easily lead to insomnia.","Oh, thanks for the concern. But an opportunity to just relax and admire the night sky with a sea breeze is quite rare and valuable to me. Care to come along?","My journey is drawing to a close, while yours is just about to begin again.","I heard the seagulls were hurt before... Is their journey very dangerous?","It is. Migratory birds like seagulls have to travel with the seasons to find suitable habitats, and they can face all sorts of threats along the way.","Good news: The poaching ring has been completely busted! One Han City is safe for them now.","I heard you put in a lot of effort. I\'d like to say thank you on behalf of the little ones.","It\'s Zephyr and Snowii... Let\'s go see them tomorrow!","Okay. Breezy\'s there with them too, and its wing seems to have healed completely.","Phew, glad you\'re not migratory! Means we can keep seeing each other.","Should a moment arrive where I must depart, rest assured, I\'ll be asking you to join me on the journey.","How do you even identify every single bird?!","It\'s hardly challenging. The distinctions among these little ones are quite apparent.","CODE RED: I can\'t sleep, nyaa! Maybe the shrine\'s too quiet without ocean sounds? Trying wave ASMR, nyaa!","Won\'t work. Save you effort, woof.","How\'d you know that, nyaa?","Wouldn\'t be replying to you at 3 AM if it worked, woof.","MUST LISTEN: Deep Sleep - Healing Ocean Waves (Binaural Beats). This track is no joke – I was sleepy in 3 minutes. Tap the link to try it >> [fake.link]","I read every, single, word, only to find a... FAKE LINK! Claws unsheathed, nyaa!","You\'re missing the point. The real issue is that Mahjong So